INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (148, 76, 'zh-CN', '简单易实操的币市绝对收益策略——中低频网格套利', '<p class=\"has-custom-size\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">套利交易简介</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">套利交易，又叫对冲交易，遵循“市场中性”原则，即同时进行两笔行情相关、方向相反、数量相当、盈亏相抵的交易。最常见的套利交易发生在满足条件一对标的上，交易时，买入认为被低估的标的，同时卖出被高估的标的，当差价恢复时，平仓出场。本质上，套利交易是交易者选择两个标的，构建投资组合，并以组合内两个标的的差价，作为交易对象，如投资者认为价差较低时，买入/开多价差，价差上涨后平仓获利。投资者关心的是组合内标价格的相互关系，而不是其绝对价格水平，通过其差价的波动来获利，同时避免了价格直接波动的影响。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">套利交易的基本方法</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当我们选择A,B两个产品组成交易对时，我们定义组合的差价 diff = price_A - price_B。当认为diff处于低位时，我们开多diff，diff上涨到合适位置平仓。开多diff，即开多A，同时开空B；平多，即平多A，同时平多B。开空平空同理。下面我们具体举例说明。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如我们选择STAI的BTC永续合约和BTC季度合约分别作为A和B，diff = 永续价格 - 季度价格。永续和季度合约各1个BTC保证金。</p>', '目前产生利润的比特币比例高达89％。这意味着，如果他们在市场上出售其BTC，比特币供应量中将仅有11％亏损');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (149, 76, 'en', 'DEXs Ride the DeFi Wave: Liquidity, Security and the Road to Mass Adoption', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Decentralized finance, or DeFi, has recently been the focus of interest and discussion in the broader crypto community. The total value in USD locked in the DeFi market&nbsp;<a href=\"https://defipulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">surpassed</a>&nbsp;$2 billion for the first time in July. The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cointelegraph.com/news/users-surge-but-just-five-defi-projects-account-for-94-of-locked-funds\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">number of users</a>&nbsp;in the DeFi market also witnessed considerable growth, reaching almost 240,000 as of July 6.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The recent explosive growth of the DeFi niche is believed to be driven by one lending protocol in particular, Compound, which began to gain popularity starting with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.okex.com/academy/en/the-rise-of-compound-hype-driven-bubble-or-indicator-of-defis-strength\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">distribution</a>&nbsp;of its governance token COMP in mid-June. Compound quickly overtook fellow Ethereum-based lending protocol, Maker, as the leading DeFi project, reaching&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.okex.com/academy/en/introducing-defis-top-5-projects-in-terms-of-total-value-locked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">almost $700 million</a>&nbsp;in assets locked on the protocol as of July 9.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The hype around DeFi appears to have also benefited decentralized exchanges, commonly referred to as DEXs. Data from Ethereum analytics service Dune Analytics&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/decentralized-exchange-volumes-up-70-in-june-pass-1-5-billion\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">indicates</a>&nbsp;that trading volumes on DEXs set an all-time high of $1.52 billion in June — a 70% increase from May. In particular, DEX platforms Uniswap and Curve dominated the market, with $446 million and $350 million volume traded, respectively.</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (150, 77, 'zh-CN', '比特币BTC减半套利策略：交易“减半”', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">第三次BTC减半预计将在2020年5月12日发生。有相当多的用户认为BTC价格会因为产量减半，供不应求而上涨。本文，我们利用历史数据回测，探究如何从事件套利的角度交易“减半”。</p><h4 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #222a3c; line-height: 29px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #222a3c; line-height: 29px;\"><span class=\"tadv-background-color\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; background-color: #8ed1fc;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; background-color: #8ed1fc;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">历史数据</span></span></h4><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">2020 年 4 月，BCH 和 BSV 分别于8日和10日发生了减半，两者对BTC 的价格如图所示。对BTC价格可以有效地消除市场波动影响</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/06/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873-16-1.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"比特币BTC减半套利策略：交易“减半”\" width=\"804\" height=\"255\" data-mce-style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium;\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\" data-mce-src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/06/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873-16-1.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\"></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">图1  BCH 减半期间百度搜索指数</em></figcaption></figure><h4 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #222a3c; line-height: 29px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #222a3c; line-height: 29px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"><span class=\"tadv-background-color\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; background-color: #8ed1fc;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; background-color: #8ed1fc;\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/04/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874-10.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" width=\"807\" height=\"256\" data-mce-src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/04/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874-10.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\"></span></span></h4><p><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: #222a3c;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: #222a3c;\"></p><h4 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #222a3c; line-height: 29px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #222a3c; line-height: 29px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"><span class=\"tadv-background-color\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; background-color: #8ed1fc;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; background-color: #8ed1fc;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">图2 BSV减半期间百度搜索指数</em>简单多空策略回测</span></span></h4><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">如上图所示，百度搜索率通常从减半发生的3天前开始上涨，并在减半日达到峰值，之后开始下降。利用 LTC（2019 年 8 月 5 日发生减半）、BCH 和 BSV的历史数据，我们提出了一个简单的交易策略，即减半前买入做多，在减半日做空达到反向头寸，并在 3 天后平仓。我们将交易以BTC报价的币对以消除市场波动噪音。如例一所示，这三个简单的交易：提前3天买入~1BTC的减半币种，在减半日当日双倍做空，得到~1BTC空仓，减半3天后平仓，给我们带来了共约33.84%， 平均约11.28%的收益。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\"># 例一: </em></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/academyokex.wpcomstaging.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_15876503713220.png?fit=268%2C240&ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-44248\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: auto;\" data-mce-src=\"https://i1.wp.com/academyokex.wpcomstaging.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_15876503713220.png?fit=268%2C240&ssl=1\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"> 总收益约为 0.3384BTC，即33.84%，均值约为11.28%</p><h4 class=\"has-very-dark-gray-color has-text-color\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #222a3c; line-height: 29px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #222a3c; line-height: 29px;\"><span class=\"tadv-background-color\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; background-color: #8ed1fc;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; background-color: #8ed1fc;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">如何应用于即将到来的 BTC</span> <span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">减半</span></span></h4><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">上述回测显示，在低市值币种市场，“就谣言而入，就新闻而沽(Buy on Rumours, Sell on News)”是一种可用的alpha。但是，将这种策略移植到 BTC 会稍有不同，因为对冲市场波动不是件易事。在上面的例子中，本质上delta为0，因为我们总是在以BTC进行买卖。为了进行类似的BTC减半交易，我们可以选择以USD交易或以USDT进行交易，亦可选择用ETH对冲。用户可以自行选择最佳方式。当然，如果没有现货持仓，用户可以在STAI杠杆交易平台借币完成上述操作，或者可以选择交易USDT永续合约。</p><h4 class=\"has-very-dark-gray-color has-text-color\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #222a3c; line-height: 29px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #222a3c; line-height: 29px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"><span class=\"tadv-background-color\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; background-color: #8ed1fc;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; background-color: #8ed1fc;\">结论</span></span></h4><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">本文我们研究了一种事件驱动套利交易，我们在一个币种减半前做多，减半时做空。我们推测，由于减半新闻盛行，市场需求随着减半的到来逐渐增加，但减半后，买入压力逐渐消失，导致价格开始下跌。我们利用以BTC报价的币对进行了delta中性的回测，最后讨论了如何将这个逻辑应用于即将到来的2020年5月BTC的减半。</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/04/%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_15876407614602.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-44204\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: auto;\" data-mce-src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/04/%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_15876407614602.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: auto;\"></figure>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (151, 78, 'zh-CN', '如何购买比特币', '<p>비트 코 인 을 구 매 하기 전에 다음 과 같은 작업 을 완성 해 야 합 니 다.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>1. 반드시 핸드폰 번 호 를 연결 해 야 합 니 다.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>2. 적어도 KYC 1 인증 완료</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>만약 에 귀하 가 동전 을 팔 아서 조작 을 해 야 한다 면 상기 두 가지 조건 을 만족 시 키 는 토대 에서 본인 의 실명 인증 을 받 은 은행 카드 를 연결 해 야 합 니 다.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>법정 화 폐 는 세 가지 거래 유형 을 포함 하 는데 그것 이 바로 빠 른 거래, C2C 거래 와 대형 거래 이다.</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (152, 78, 'en', 'How to buy Bitcoin', '<p>Before you can buy bitcoin, you need to do the following:</p><p>1. The mobile phone number must be bound (the registered user of the mobile phone number is the bound user);</p><p>2. At least complete KYC1 certification</p><p>If you still need to sell COINS, you need to bind a bank card with your real name authentication on the basis of meeting the above two conditions.</p><p>There are three types of transactions in legal tender, namely, quick transaction, C2C transaction and bulk transaction.</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (153, 78, 'zh-TW', '如何購買比特幣', '<p>在購買比特幣前，您需要完成以下操作：</p><p>1.必須綁定手機號（手機號注冊的用戶即已綁定用戶）；</p><p>2.至少完成KYC1認證 </p><p>若您還需要賣幣操作，在滿足以上兩個條件基礎上還需要綁定一張本人實名認證的銀行卡。</p><p>法幣包含三種交易類型，分別是快捷買賣、C2C交易和大宗交易。</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (154, 79, 'zh-TW', '繁体', NULL, NULL);
