INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (156, 79, 'en', '引文', NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (157, 77, 'en', 'Bitcoin BTC Halve Arbitrage Strategy: Trading \"halve\"', '<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/05/NoW-1.jpg?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"News of the Week image\" class=\"wp-image-50174\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">While a lack of institutional interest is reportedly causing the first crypto hedge fund in the United Kingdom to shut its doors, banks in the United States may soon start offering custodial services for digital assets. Meanwhile, PayPal is reportedly set to offer direct cryptocurrency sales to its users. These and more topics are examined in this week’s edition of STAI Insight’s Crypto News of the Week.</p><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">U.S. banks permitted to provide custody for cryptocurrencies</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Nationally chartered banks in the United States will be allowed to provide custody services for unique cryptographic keys tied to cryptocurrency wallets, according to <a href=\"https://www.occ.treas.gov/news-issuances/news-releases/2020/nr-occ-2020-98.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">a public letter</a> from the Office of the Comptroller of the Currency’s Jonathan Gould, the independent bureau of Treasury Department’s senior deputy comptroller and chief counsel.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The letter also clarifies that banks may provide both fiduciary and non-fiduciary custodian services.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">As a side note, the OCC is currently being led by former Coinbase’s chief legal officer, <a href=\"https://www.occ.treas.gov/about/who-we-are/comptroller/bio-brian-brooks.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">Brian Brooks</a>.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">Key takeaways:</span></p><ul style=\"padding: 0px 10px; margin: 0px 12px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); line-height: 22px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Though Bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies have long allowed users to “be their own banks,” individuals uncomfortable with the idea may soon allow traditional banks to secure their digital assets.</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">The ability to provide cryptocurrency custody services — which has primarily been limited to select regulated entities — may now become greatly expanded and diversified.</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">The OCC clearly recognizes the need to adapt and keep pace with the speed of financial innovation, which has largely been accelerated by BTC and blockchain technology.</li></ul><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PayPal is reportedly partnering with Paxos for cryptocurrency services</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PayPal is reportedly planning on partnering with Paxos to offer direct cryptocurrency sales and trading. The news comes via <a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/paypal-picks-paxos-to-supply-crypto-for-new-service-sources-say\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">CoinDesk</a>, which claims to have spoken to two individuals familiar with the prospective arrangement.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Paxos is based out of New York and recently launched its own crypto brokerage service, Paxos Crypto Brokerage, which will provide services to Revolut US.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">Key takeaways:</span></p><ul style=\"padding: 0px 10px; margin: 0px 12px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); line-height: 22px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Should the reports be true, Bitcoin will see one of its most mainstream forms of adoption yet — given the sheer size and scope of PayPal’s user base, which numbers upward of 325 million.</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">The fintech giant, which also owns Venmo, would join publicly traded competitors Square and Robinhood in offering digital-asset purchases.</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/fed1da6da79ca8f0cba2aa0c88e14d9e5f217ce19d8dc.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"445\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></li></ul><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">First U.K. crypto hedge fund closing due to lack of demand</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The United Kingdom’s first cryptocurrency hedge fund, Prime Factor Capital, is shutting down — citing a lack of demand from institutional investors. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">According to a Financial News report cited by <a href=\"https://www.theblockcrypto.com/linked/72638/uk-crypto-hedge-fund-closing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">The Block</a>, the hedge fund “struggled to get traction in terms of raising assets,” per a direct quote from Prime Factor Capital CEO Nic Niedermowwe.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The cryptocurrency hedge fund was notably the first to get a green light from the Financial Conduct Authority, the nation’s independently operating financial regulatory body.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">Key takeaway:</span></p><ul style=\"padding: 0px 10px; margin: 0px 12px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); line-height: 22px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">The lack of institutional demand cited as the reason for Prime Factor Capital’s winding down stands in stark contrast to <a href=\"https://www.okex.com/academy/en/bitcoin-bandwagoning-an-examination-of-institutional-investment-in-crypto\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">the dramatic increase in institutional investment</a> seen elsewhere in the cryptocurrency space.</li></ul><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Fintech giant Ant Group launches blockchain brand AntChain</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Alibaba Group’s fintech branch, Ant Group, <a href=\"https://www.theblockcrypto.com/linked/72715/chinese-fintech-giant-ant-group-launches-new-blockchain-brand-antchain\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">launched its own blockchain brand</a> this week. Named “AntChain,” the brand will cover blockchain-based solutions, while claiming to be able to process 1 billion daily transactions and support upward of 1 billion user accounts.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ant Group is the parent company of Alipay, a China-based online and mobile payments giant that is very closely affiliated with China’s official digital currency.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">Key takeaway:</span></p><ul style=\"padding: 0px 10px; margin: 0px 12px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); line-height: 22px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">While the term “blockchain” has been used liberally as a buzzword in recent years, the launch of a tangible blockchain brand from Ant Group represents a major push for the technology into mainstream fintech.</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/fed1da6da79ca8f0cba2aa0c88e14d9e5f217d045adf3.jpg\" width=\"808\" height=\"449\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></li></ul><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Mastercard signs deal with Wirex for cryptocurrency cards </h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Mastercard has <a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/07/20/mastercard-strikes-cryptocurrency-card-deal-with-uk-start-up-wirex.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">signed a deal</a> with cryptocurrency startup Wirex after opening up its cryptocurrency-related program, Mastercard Accelerate, which now allows crypto companies to create their own payment cards. As such, Wirex will now be able to issue its own Mastercard-backed cards.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Wirex previously saw its debit cards issued by Wirecard, a now-defunct German payment processor that was recently unable to account for $2 billion.</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (158, 77, 'zh-TW', '比特幣BTC減半套利策略：交易“減半”', '<div class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/academyokex.wpcomstaging.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/%E7%94%BB%E6%9D%BF-381.png?fit=427%2C240&ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-44384\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure></div><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">第三次BTC減半預計將在2020年5月12日發生。有相當多的用戶認為BTC價格會因為產量減半，供不應求而上漲。本文，我們利用歷史數據回測，探究如何從事件套利的角度交易“減半”。</font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><br></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">歷史數據</font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">2020 年 4 月，BCH 和 BSV 分別於8日和10日發生了減半，兩者對BTC 的價格如圖所示。對BTC價格可以有效地消除市場波動影響。</font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">我們可以看到，價格高峰發生在減半當天。作為一名量化交易者，我相信短期價格是受供求關係驅動的。從基本面角度分析，通貨膨脹率降低導致價格上漲，這種影響在短期內是可以忽略的。不難想像，減半新聞鋪天蓋地，人們情緒高漲時，價格會上升至最高點。從百度指數和谷歌指數均可看出，BCH和BSV的搜索率在減半時達到頂峰，這意味著減半時需求也達到最高。我推測我們可以使用所謂的就謠言而入，就新聞而沽(Buy on Rumours, Sell on News)策略。</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/06/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873-16-1.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"比特币BTC减半套利策略：交易“减半”\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\"><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">圖1 BCH 減半期間百度搜索指數</em></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/04/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874-10.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-44201\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\"><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">圖2 BSV減半期間百度搜索指數</em></figcaption></figure><h4 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"><span class=\"tadv-background-color\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; background-color: rgb(142, 209, 252);\">簡單多空策略回測</span></span></h4><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">如上圖所示，百度搜索率通常從減半發生的3天前開始上漲，並在減半日達到峰值，之後開始下降。利用LTC（2019 年8 月5 日發生減半）、BCH 和BSV的歷史數據，我們提出了一個簡單的交易策略，即減半前買入做多，在減半日做空達到反向頭寸，並在3 天后平倉。我們將交易以BTC報價的幣對以消除市場波動噪音。如例一所示，這三個簡單的交易：提前3天買入~1BTC的減半幣種，在減半日當日雙倍做空，得到~1BTC空倉，減半3天后平倉，給我們帶來了共約33.84%， 平均約11.28%的收益。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"># 例一:</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/academyokex.wpcomstaging.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_15876503713220.png?fit=268%2C240&ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-44248\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">總收益約為 0.3384BTC，即33.84%，均值約為11.28%</font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><br></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">如何應用於即將到來的 BTC 減半</font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">上述回測顯示，在低市值幣種市場，“就謠言而入，就新聞而沽(Buy on Rumours, Sell on News)”是一種可用的alpha。但是，將這種策略移植到 BTC 會稍有不同，因為對沖市場波動不是件易事。在上面的例子中，本質上delta為0，因為我們總是在以BTC進行買賣。為了進行類似的BTC減半交易，我們可以選擇以USD交易或以USDT進行交易，亦可選擇用ETH對沖。用戶可以自行選擇最佳方式。當然，如果沒有現貨持倉，用戶可以在OKEx槓桿交易平台借幣完成上述操作，或者可以選擇交易USDT永續合約。</font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><br></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">結論</font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">本文我們研究了一種事件驅動套利交易，我們在一個幣種減半前做多，減半時做空。我們推測，由於減半新聞盛行，市場需求隨著減半的到來逐漸增加，但減半後，買入壓力逐漸消失，導致價格開始下跌。我們利用以BTC報價的幣對進行了delta中性的回測，最後討論瞭如何將這個邏輯應用於即將到來的2020年5月BTC的減半。</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/04/%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_15876407614602.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-44204\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (159, 80, 'en', 'Ant Group’s IPO Plan, Beijing’s Blockchain Blueprint and CSRC’s Approval of Equity Trading Pilot — China Market Watch', '<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/07/China_Market_Watch.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-70550\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The stock market in China and Hong Kong saw a mild recovery this week. The Shanghai SE Composite and CSI 300 currently <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://tradingeconomics.com/stocks\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">run</a> at 3,325 and 4,712, with rebounds of 3.86% and 4.34% respectively over the week. The <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://tradingeconomics.com/hong-kong/stock-market\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">Hang Seng Index</a> also posted a weekly value rise of 3.58%, currently standing at 25,203.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The Hang Seng Index received an early boost this week due to the <a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3093949/hong-kong-stock-exchange-get-new-tech-index-tracking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">announcement</a> of the Hang Seng Tech Index, which will debut on July 27, and will track the 30 largest technology companies listed in Hong Kong. Some of these big names include Alibaba, Tencent Holdings, Meituan Dianping, Xiaomi and Sunny Optical. The announcement of a concurrent IPO plan by Ant Group on July 20 also serves as another boost for both the Hong Kong and China stock market.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">On the contrary, the diplomatic tension between China and the U.S. rose again this week. The U.S <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-53497193\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">ordered</a> China to close its consulate in Houston on July 22, reportedly in a bid to protect the intellectual property and private information of Americans. China condemned this and believed the move to be aimed at “political provocation.\" In return, the country accused the U.S. of posting <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://twitter.com/SpokespersonCHN/status/1285970001199915008\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">death threats</a> to the Chinese embassy. These ongoing tensions led to a daily drop of 0.24% and 0.22% for Shanghai SE Composite and CSI 300, respectively.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Meanwhile, the SZSE Blockchain 50 index currently stands at 4,064, a weekly rise of 3.68%. Among the 50 stocks included in the index, Jiangsu Akcome Solar Science & Technology (002610.SZ) is the daily top gainer, with a 10.16% increase, while the Client Service International (300663.SZ) is the top loser, with a weekly value of -5.38%.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/853b031a43495200d111d6f5239398a35f217df043132.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"425\" alt=\"\"><br><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">Performance of Chinese market indexes. Source: Trading Economics, Investing.com</em></figcaption></figure><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">News of the Week</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">From Ant Group’s concurrent initial public offering plan to Beijing’s blockchain blueprint and China Security Regulatory Commission’s approval of a blockchain pilot in equity trading,  Insights takes a look at this week’s top three crypto news stories from China and Hong Kong.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ant Group plans a concurrent IPO in Hong Kong and Shanghai</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ant Group, an affiliate of e-commerce giant Alibaba, is <a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ant-financial-ipo/alibabas-ant-group-starts-concurrent-ipo-process-in-shanghai-hong-kong-idUSKCN24L0ZO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">reportedly</a> planning to conduct a concurrent IPO on the <a href=\"https://www.hkex.com.hk/?sc_lang=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">Hong Kong Stock Exchange</a> and the <a href=\"https://www.ciis.com.hk/hongkong/en/scitech/index.shtml#:~:text=Science%20and%20Technology%20Innovation%20Board,tech%20and%20strategically%20emerging%20sectors.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">STAR Board</a> of Shanghai’s stock exchange. Known for its <a href=\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/226152/largest-ipos-in-the-united-states-by-issue-volume/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">landmark New York IPO</a> of $21.77 billion in 2014, Alibaba conducted its second IPO in Hong Kong with $12.9 billion raised. To better reflect the firm’s business model, Ant Financial <a href=\"https://www.spglobal.com/marketintelligence/en/news-insights/latest-news-headlines/ant-financial-to-change-name-59168730#:~:text=Zhejiang%20Ant%20Financial%20Services%20Group,a%20spokesman%20for%20the%20company.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">rebranded</a> to Ant Group in June.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Apart from owning Alipay — one of the most popular digital payment apps in China, with over 900 million users — Ant Group <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/07/21/alibaba-ant-group-ipo-hong-kong-shanghai-explained.html#:~:text=IPO%20details&text=Ant%20Group\'s%20last%20major%20fundraising,was%20valued%20at%20%24150%20billion.\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">offers</a> other digital financial services in wealth management, loans and insurance, etc. As of the end of the fiscal year on March 31, these digital financial services accounted for more than 50% of Ant Group’s overall revenue.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Alipay has been an <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20180625005561/en/AlipayHK-GCash-Launch-Cross-Border-Remittance-Service-Powered\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">early mover</a> in blockchain technology since 2015. Its parent company, Alibaba, is active in the space and <a href=\"http://www.chinabankingnews.com/2020/04/26/chinese-tech-giants-take-top-three-spots-for-blockchain-patent-applications-in-2019/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">topped</a> the global blockchain patent applications ranking in 2019.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Built on the aforementioned expertise and R&D in blockchain technology, the Hangzhou-based group launched its blockchain-as-a-service platform, OpenChain, in April, which enables small and medium-sized enterprises to build decentralized applications, otherwise known as DApps. The fixed asset registration center of Zhuhai could be the latest user of OpenChain, as it recently <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.jinse.com/blockchain/763500.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">signed</a> an agreement with Ant Group to streamline mortgage applications using blockchain.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">Key takeaways</span></p><ul style=\"padding: 0px 10px; margin: 0px 12px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); line-height: 22px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Ant Group, rebranded from Ant Financial in June, is seeking a concurrent IPO in Hong Kong and Shanghai.</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Ant Group is an affiliate of tech giant Alibaba and is the <a href=\"https://www.alipayhk.com/en/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">parent company</a> of Alipay.</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Ant Group is also active in the blockchain space, with its own BaaS platform OpenChain launched in April.</li></ul><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Beijing released its first blockchain application blueprint</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">On July 16, the Beijing government <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202007/15/WS5f0efda2e4b00aba04d26963.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">released</a> its first <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.chainnews.com/articles/973651558972.htm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">blockchain blueprint</a> on government services — according to which, 140 government services applications in China are using blockchain to save costs around an average of 40%.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The blueprint highlights three categories of applications: data sharing and exchange, business collaborative processing, and storage of electronic certificates.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">For the last category, the blueprint illustrates the case of fixed assets registration. Due to the use of blockchain technology, the relevant information is transparent and traceable by government authorities, such as the municipal planning commission, the tax bureau and the public security bureau.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The blockchain blueprint is consistent with Beijing’s continuous blockchain push, following the “Beijing Municipal Blockchain Innovation Development Action Plan (2020–2022)” <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2020-07/02/content_5523574.htm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">released</a> on July 2. The Beijing government identified four pillars in blockchain to support economic growth: innovation in blockchain technology, industrial development, blockchain use cases, and talent cultivation.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">Key takeaways</span></p><ul style=\"padding: 0px 10px; margin: 0px 12px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); line-height: 22px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">The Beijing government released its first blockchain blueprint in government services.</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">On average, blockchain use cases in government services result in 40% cost savings.</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">There are three featured categories in the blueprint: data sharing and exchange, business collaborative processing, and storage of electronic certificates.</li></ul><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">CSRC approved five equity trading centers for a blockchain pilot</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">On July 7, the China Security Regulatory Commission issued a statement approving blockchain pilots of five regional equity trading centers. The five regions are Beijing, Shanghai, Jiangsu, Zhejiang and Shenzhen. This announcement was first <a href=\"http://jrj.beijing.gov.cn/jrgzdt/202007/t20200721_1954394.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">made public</a> by the Beijing Local Financial Supervision and Administration on July 21.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">As stated in the announcement, Beijing’s equity trading center has reportedly built a \"relatively perfect\" infrastructure for equity registration, custody and transaction transfer. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Beijing’s equity trading center has been an early explorer in blockchain technology since 2017. The center <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://cointelegraph.com/news/china-considers-implementing-blockchain-tech-in-equity-trading-centers/amp\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">partnered</a> with the Shenzhen Stock Exchange to launch a blockchain to track the credit reference of equity market intermediaries. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In addition, Beijing’s equity trading center will be collaborating with the China Securities Depository and Clearing Corporation for the pilot launch of backend infrastructure.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">As of June 30, Beijing’s equity trading center held a total of 21.07 billion RMB ($3 billion) in custody. The center serves nine commercial banks and more than 1,000 unlisted joint-stock companies.</p>', 'Ant Group’s IPO Plan, Beijing’s Blockchain Blueprint and CSRC’s Approval of Equity Trading Pilot — China Market Watch');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (160, 80, 'zh-CN', '区块链如何改变商业价值？唯有颠覆！', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2018年，区块链市场泡沫破裂后，区块链技术本身却获得了政府，公共服务组织和一些私营企业的青睐。目前或许是我们关注区块链技术的最佳时机。区块链技术能否为企业和消费者带来价值变化？区块链可以产生多大商业价值？区块链是否可以创造出比现有业务更具竞争性的商业模式？这里，让我们从价值，价格和成本三个方面来详细讨论区块链技术可能带来的商业价值。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">成本：谁在买单？</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">首先，我们不要忘记一些基本原则：价格和成本决定了公司的利润，而价格和价值则产生消费者剩余（consumer’s surplus）。</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2019/12/7.1.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4438\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">价值，价格和成本框架</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从服务商的角度来看，降低成本或（和）提高价格会增加其利润。许多人认为区块链技术降低了经营企业的成本，但这种说法存在争议。与运行中心化数据服务器或网络的成本相比，区块链技术确实可以节省这些成本。然而，要做到让参与区块链网络的节点提供稳定的服务质量，可能会产生意想不到的成本。众所周知，跟中心化网络相比，区块链没有效率优势。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们从很多项目中都可以看出，随着业务的增长，“低效成本（inefficiency cost）” 甚至会高于使用区块链技术所节省的成本。正如以太坊创始人Vitalik Buterin所言：“亚马逊EC2云服务的中等规模计算成本为每小时0.04美元，而在以太坊执行相同任务的成本约为每200毫秒13.40美元，比亚马逊高出140万倍。”这表明区块链行业在效率层面还有很大的提升空间。</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/academyokex.wpcomstaging.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/27201.png?fit=1024%2C576&ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7725\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">随着业务的发展，区块链的扩展局限和低效率成本问题会变得更加严重。因此，我们不能简单地认为经营区块链业务的总成本将比以前大幅减少。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然而，有趣的是，区块链业务中往往是消费者为成本买单。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">与区块链商业模式不同，在传统的商业模式中，公司搭建和维护能够处理大量用户请求的中心化网络服务器。公司先承担运行此类网络的成本，后从服务用户中获取利润。然而，在区块链商业模式中，公司不负责处理用户请求，而由“自愿参与的节点”承担，用户支付节点奖励费用。例如，当用户使用以太坊网络上的DAPP时，需要支付节点一定的费用来处理请求。费用可以是DAPP上的通证，也可以是ETH。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">价格：从看不见到看得见</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">价格包括成本和公司的利润。让我们来想一想每天使用IT服务支付了多少钱。令人惊讶的是，“付费使用服务”的做法在现有的IT业务中已经很少见了。一旦连接到互联网，用户每次向Google发送电子邮件时都不需要再支付一分钱，除非要充值高级会员来跳过广告或扩展云存储，大多数IT公司都不会向用户索取费用。</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/academyokex.wpcomstaging.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/27202.png?fit=1024%2C576&ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7726\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但这并不意味着这些服务是完全免费的。作为回报，用户需要将其数据控制权交给服务商和广告商，而这是公司业务的主要收入来源。我们所在的世界充满着欢迎各类 “免费注册并使用我们的服务”，而这实际上都是一种“无形的价格标签”。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是，在基于区块链的服务中，价格标签变得更加明显。在区块链网络中，服务商不再管理、掌握用户数据，用户自己掌握其数据的所有权。一些区块链企业允许其用户“出售”数据来赚取通证，或者支付使用服务的费用。这就是区块链的商业价值。问题是，用户习惯了看似免费的服务，当基于区块链的服务明码标价的时候，用户是否会认为标价合理呢？</p><h4 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </h4><h4 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">价值：理念超过实用性？</h4><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“价值”是区块链业务中最棘手的部分。企业的价值通常被定义为利润，而对消费者而言，这一单词的含义更加复杂。简单来说，价值就是“消费者愿意购买产品或服务的原因”。如区块链公司的广告词强调“隐私”和“透明”，而传统广告强调速度，价格优势或便利性。这又会产生一系列新的问题：消费者是否愿意牺牲效率和响应及时的客户服务而去使用区块链服务？区块链业务所传递的价值，如隐私和抗审查，是否足以吸引大量消费者群体？</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/06/27203.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"区块链如何改变商业价值？唯有颠覆\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">俗话说，没有恶就没有善。在区块链行业中，有些概念一开始就非常明确，如去中心化是好的，而中心化是不好的。很多区块链项目被指责“不够去中心化”、“伪区块链”。我们已经见证了太多区块链商业模式失败，它们盲目强调好的愿景而忽视了消费者的其他需求。理念本身并不能推动行业的长远发展。有人认为区块链商业模式中通证经济和去中心化的理念具有魔力，可以吸引消费者来这个生态追求经济回报。但是，这种说法并没有现实案例来支撑。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们必须承认，大多数通证经济都是服务投资者而非消费者的。人可以轻易的失去对理念的信仰，但却不会轻易放弃好的实际体验。只有当区块链商业公司重视用户体验时，理念才能被消费者所接受。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">超越竞争对手</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果未来区块链业务可以击败强大的竞争对手，理想情况将会如下图所示：成本和价格降低，消费者剩余增加，最终产生的总价值超过其竞争对手。没有人能够确定这种理想情况是否会变为现实。或许区块链业务的盈利率会低于竞争对手。注：下图中成本，价格和价值的占有比例可能会因公司而异。</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2019/12/7.5.jpg?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/I54nSo4IS0X8vBfbU8f8ufBiaictS18ptVHeAdaJVoPF9EPahcWA3oWCicOgXcTL1oE8bTKiarYoRDicTrxxwd8u4NQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" class=\"wp-image-4442\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">理想中的区块链业务框架与其竞争对手的业务框架</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">目前看来，区块链公司在价值，价格和成本三个方面都不存在优势。低效成本太高，消费者习惯于使用“免费”服务，区块链商业模式的理念能否吸引大众消费者仍是个疑问。当然不确定性中存在着积极意义。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根据“创新者的窘境（Innovator’ Dilemma）”理论，新技术会颠覆现有的市场，甚至导致一些巨头破产。这一理论认为 “颠覆性技术”往往改变了市场的基本价值主张，导致了急剧的范式转移，使得巨头企业无法适应。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“创新者的窘境”理论认为颠覆性技术最初的性能表现较差，容量低于现有的解决方案。虽然目前的价值，价格和成本框架无法说明区块链产业具有光明的前景，但或许区块链会创造一种全新的范例。区块链技术已经改变了部分人的思考方式，让他们意识到中心化机构和中介所带来的问题。即使区块链技术无法解决这些问题并最终消失，遗留下来的东西也会持续下去，促进下一个颠覆性技术的出现。</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2019/12/7.6.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4443\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">区块链技术的商业模式或许无法创造出人类历史上最赚钱的业务，但它有可能打破目前中心化公司将追求利益最大化作为准则的商业运作理念----而创造一种新的常态。让我们在行业最艰难的时候依然心存希望。</p>', '区块链如何改变商业价值？唯有颠覆！');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (161, 80, 'zh-TW', NULL, '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">2018年，區塊鏈市場泡沫破裂後，區塊鏈技術本身卻獲得了政府，公共服務組織和一些私營企業的青睞。目前或許是我們關注區塊鏈技術的最佳時機。區塊鏈技術能否為企業和消費者帶來價值變化？區塊鏈可以產生多大商業價值？區塊鍊是否可以創造出比現有業務更具競爭性的商業模式？這裡，讓我們從價值，價格和成本三個方面來詳細討論區塊鏈技術可能帶來的商業價值。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">成本：誰在買單？</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">首先，我們不要忘記一些基本原則：價格和成本決定了公司的利潤，而價格和價值則產生消費者剩餘（consumer’s surplus）</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2019/12/7.1.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4438\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">價值，價格和成本框架</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">從服務商的角度來看，降低成本或（和）提高價格會增加其利潤。許多人認為區塊鏈技術降低了經營企業的成本，但這種說法存在爭議。與運行中心化數據服務器或網絡的成本相比，區塊鏈技術確實可以節省這些成本。然而，要做到讓參與區塊鍊網絡的節點提供穩定的服務質量，可能會產生意想不到的成本。眾所周知，跟中心化網絡相比，區塊鏈沒有效率優勢。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">我們從很多項目中都可以看出，隨著業務的增長，“低效成本（inefficiency cost）” 甚至會高於使用區塊鏈技術所節省的成本。正如以太坊創始人Vitalik Buterin所言：“亞馬遜EC2雲服務的中等規模計算成本為每小時0.04美元，而在以太坊執行相同任務的成本約為每200毫秒13.40美元，比亞馬遜高出140萬倍。”這表明區塊鏈行業在效率層面還有很大的提升空間。</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/academyokex.wpcomstaging.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/27201.png?fit=1024%2C576&ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7725\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">隨著業務的發展，區塊鏈的擴展局限和低效率成本問題會變得更加嚴重。因此，我們不能簡單地認為經營區塊鏈業務的總成本將比以前大幅減少。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">然而，有趣的是，區塊鏈業務中往往是消費者為成本買單。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">與區塊鏈商業模式不同，在傳統的商業模式中，公司搭建和維護能夠處理大量用戶請求的中心化網絡服務器。公司先承擔運行此類網絡的成本，後從服務用戶中獲取利潤。然而，在區塊鏈商業模式中，公司不負責處理用戶請求，而由“自願參與的節點”承擔，用戶支付節點獎勵費用。例如，當用戶使用以太坊網絡上的DAPP時，需要支付節點一定的費用來處理請求。費用可以是DAPP上的通證，也可以是ETH。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">價格：從看不見到看得見</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">價格包括成本和公司的利潤。讓我們來想一想每天使用IT服務支付了多少錢。令人驚訝的是，“付費使用服務”的做法在現有的IT業務中已經很少見了。一旦連接到互聯網，用戶每次向Google發送電子郵件時都不需要再支付一分錢，除非要充值高級會員來跳過廣告或擴展雲存儲，大多數IT公司都不會向用戶索取費用。</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/academyokex.wpcomstaging.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/27202.png?fit=1024%2C576&ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7726\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">但這並不意味著這些服務是完全免費的。作為回報，用戶需要將其數據控制權交給服務商和廣告商，而這是公司業務的主要收入來源。我們所在的世界充滿著歡迎各類 “免費註冊並使用我們的服務”，而這實際上都是一種“無形的價格標籤”。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">但是，在基於區塊鏈的服務中，價格標籤變得更加明顯。在區塊鍊網絡中，服務商不再管理、掌握用戶數據，用戶自己掌握其數據的所有權。一些區塊鏈企業允許其用戶“出售”數據來賺取通證，或者支付使用服務的費用。這就是區塊鏈的商業價值。問題是，用戶習慣了看似免費的服務，當基於區塊鏈的服務明碼標價的時候，用戶是否會認為標價合理呢？</font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">價值：理念超過實用性？</font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">“價值”是區塊鏈業務中最棘手的部分。企業的價值通常被定義為利潤，而對消費者而言，這一單詞的含義更加複雜。簡單來說，價值就是“消費者願意購買產品或服務的原因”。如區塊鏈公司的廣告詞強調“隱私”和“透明”，而傳統廣告強調速度，價格優勢或便利性。這又會產生一系列新的問題：消費者是否願意犧牲效率和響應及時的客戶服務而去使用區塊鏈服務？區塊鏈業務所傳遞的價值，如隱私和抗審查，是否足以吸引大量消費者群體？</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/06/27203.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"区块链如何改变商业价值？唯有颠覆\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">俗話說，沒有惡就沒有善。在區塊鏈行業中，有些概念一開始就非常明確，如去中心化是好的，而中心化是不好的。很多區塊鏈項目被指責“不夠去中心化”、“偽區塊鏈”。我們已經見證了太多區塊鏈商業模式失敗，它們盲目強調好的願景而忽視了消費者的其他需求。理念本身並不能推動行業的長遠發展。有人認為區塊鏈商業模式中通證經濟和去中心化的理念具有魔力，可以吸引消費者來這個生態追求經濟回報。但是，這種說法並沒有現實案例來支撐。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">我們必須承認，大多數通證經濟都是服務投資者而非消費者的。人可以輕易的失去對理念的信仰，但卻不會輕易放棄好的實際體驗。只有當區塊鏈商業公司重視用戶體驗時，理念才能被消費者所接受。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">超越競爭對手</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">如果未來區塊鏈業務可以擊敗強大的競爭對手，理想情況將會如下圖所示：成本和價格降低，消費者剩餘增加，最終產生的總價值超過其競爭對手。沒有人能夠確定這種理想情況是否會變為現實。或許區塊鏈業務的盈利率會低於競爭對手。注：下圖中成本，價格和價值的佔有比例可能會因公司而異。</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2019/12/7.5.jpg?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/I54nSo4IS0X8vBfbU8f8ufBiaictS18ptVHeAdaJVoPF9EPahcWA3oWCicOgXcTL1oE8bTKiarYoRDicTrxxwd8u4NQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" class=\"wp-image-4442\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">理想中的區塊鏈業務框架與其競爭對手的業務框架</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">目前看來，區塊鏈公司在價值，價格和成本三個方面都不存在優勢。低效成本太高，消費者習慣於使用“免費”服務，區塊鏈商業模式的理念能否吸引大眾消費者仍是個疑問。當然不確定性中存在著積極意義。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">根據“創新者的窘境（Innovator’ Dilemma）”理論，新技術會顛覆現有的市場，甚至導致一些巨頭破產。這一理論認為 “顛覆性技術”往往改變了市場的基本價值主張，導致了急劇的範式轉移，使得巨頭企業無法適應。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">“創新者的窘境”理論認為顛覆性技術最初的性能表現較差，容量低於現有的解決方案。雖然目前的價值，價格和成本框架無法說明區塊鏈產業具有光明的前景，但或許區塊鏈會創造一種全新的範例。區塊鏈技術已經改變了部分人的思考方式，讓他們意識到中心化機構和中介所帶來的問題。即使區塊鏈技術無法解決這些問題並最終消失，遺留下來的東西也會持續下去，促進下一個顛覆性技術的出現。</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2019/12/7.6.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4443\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">區塊鏈技術的商業模式或許無法創造出人類歷史上最賺錢的業務，但它有可能打破目前中心化公司將追求利益最大化作為準則的商業運作理念----而創造一種新的常態。讓我們在行業最艱難的時候依然心存希望。</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (162, 81, 'en', 'What is blockchain?', '<p>What is blockchain? Essentially, blockchain is a distributed, decentralized network database system that makes a difference in how data is stored, updated, maintained and operated.</p><p>The blockchain we are going to talk about today has four essential core technologies: distributed storage, consensus mechanism, principles of cryptography, and intelligent contract.</p><p>So we are going to talk about today, compared with traditional data processing, what is the difference between the blockchain, to help you understand what the blockchain is, let you have a general understanding of the blockchain.</p><p>1. Data storage in block chain: Block chain data structure</p><p>In terms of data storage, block chain technology USES \"block chain data structure\" to verify and store data. What does block chain mean? You\'ve all seen the chain, the link within the link, in fact, each link we can think of as a block, a lot of links linked together to form a block chain.</p><p>Blocks store data, but the difference is that on a blockchain, the data in the latter block contains the data in the previous block.<img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/1e20f4048e6555a9c7ba7ef34fc157ad5f217db29bdcc.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"435\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/1e20f4048e6555a9c7ba7ef34fc157ad5f217db29bdcc.jpg\"></p><p>Take reading for example: when we read a book, we read the first page, then the second page, the third page... What about in the blockchain? If you give each block a page number, the second page contains the first page, and the third page contains the first and second pages... Page 10 contains the contents of the first nine pages, such a nested chain. In this way, you can trace back to the source of the data, which is the traceability of the blockchain.</p><p>2. Data update in blockchain: Distributed node consensus algorithm</p><p>In terms of data update, block chain technology USES \"distributed node consensus algorithm\" to generate and update data.</p><p>Every time a new block is generated (that is, when the data is updated), it needs an algorithm to obtain the approval of more than 51% of the nodes in the whole network to form a new block. In other words, it is a vote, and more than half of the people agree that it can be generated. This makes the data on the blockchain untamable.</p><p>Let\'s use a metaphor to explain this: We liken the blockchain to a ledger, because it\'s all about recording data. In the traditional world, the right to keep accounts lies in Mr. Bookkeeping, Mr. Bookkeeping belongs to a person; In the blockchain, everyone has this account book, we keep accounts together, if you want to update the account, you have to vote, more than half of the people agree to update the account data.<img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/c9270c12cde8baa422bcc6a4a1266ab95f217e6befa6f.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"606\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/c9270c12cde8baa422bcc6a4a1266ab95f217e6befa6f.jpg\"></p><p>In this process, we will refer to the following terms: distributed, node, consensus algorithm:</p><p>Everybody keeps books (that is, everybody owns the books, and the books are spread out in everybody\'s hands). This is called \"distributed\"; The bookkeeping method that everyone discusses, votes and agrees on is the so-called \"consensus algorithm\". The nodes are much simpler, and everyone involved in the bookkeeping can be seen as a node.</p><p>3. Data maintenance in block chain: Cryptography</p><p>When it comes to data maintenance, blockchains differ in that they use cryptography to secure data transmission and access.<img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/298062ac48bdaaf030a5adb158015f125f217f22a8d33.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"536\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/298062ac48bdaaf030a5adb158015f125f217f22a8d33.jpg\"></p><p>Then, the cryptography principles applied in block chain mainly include the following: hash algorithm, Merkle hash tree, elliptic curve algorithm and Base58. These principles, in fact, are based on a series of complex calculations and transformations to ensure the security of data on the blockchain.</p><p>Iv. Data operation in blockchain: Intelligent contract</p><p>Finally, we come to the data manipulation phase, which we then refer to as the \"smart contract\".</p><p>A smart contract is a promise agreement defined by a computer program and automatically executed. To put it simply, it is a set of trading rules executed in code, similar to the automatic payment function of credit CARDS. With this function on, you don\'t have to care about anything yourself, and the bank will automatically deduct the money you owe when it is due.</p><p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/0d7b616cb7195b3ba551d839b71d45a45f21806026f46.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/0d7b616cb7195b3ba551d839b71d45a45f21806026f46.jpg\"></p><p>The outstanding advantage of smart contracts is that they largely avoid a range of issues that arise from trust. Many of us have been stuck with a loan: a friend who is strapped for cash asks for $2,000, promises to pay back his paycheck the next month, and then finds another excuse not to do so. I don\'t have much money, but I\'m still a friend, and if you\'re depressed, that\'s all right.</p><p>Then, with the smart contract, he can\'t default, because in the smart contract, once the clause in the contract is triggered, the code is automatically executed and he has to pay you back whether he wants to or not when he gets paid and has money in his account.</p><p>Finally, to summarize today\'s content, today we mainly through the data storage operation of such a process, introduced the basic situation of blockchain. To sum up, we can find that there are four indispensable core technologies in blockchain, namely: distributed storage, consensus mechanism, cryptography principle, and intelligent contract.</p><p>Then, we can understand it as follows: distributed storage corresponds to the stage of data storage; consensus mechanism corresponds to the stage of data processing and update; cryptography corresponds to data security; and intelligent contract corresponds to data operation.</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (163, 81, 'zh-CN', '什么是区块链？', '<p>什么是区块链呢，本质上讲，区块链是一种分布式、去中心化的网络数据库系统，这个系统会让数据的存储、更新、维护、操作变得不同。</p><p>我们今天要讲的区块链呢，它有四项不可缺的核心技术，分别是：分布式存储、共识机制、密码学原理、智能合约。</p><p>那么我们今天就讲一讲，与传统数据处理相比，区块链到底有什么不同，帮助大家了解区块链是什么，让大家对区块链有一个总的认知。</p><p>一、区块链中的数据存储：块链式数据结构</p><p>在数据存储方面，区块链技术利用的是“块链式数据结构”来验证与存储数据的。块链式结构是什么意思呢？铁链子大家都见过吧，一环套一环那种，其实，每一环我们可以看作是一个区块，很多环节扣在一起就形成了区块链。</p><p>区块里存储的是数据，和普通存储数据的不同之处在于：在区块链上，后一个区块里的数据是包含前一个区块里的数据的。</p><p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/1e20f4048e6555a9c7ba7ef34fc157ad5f2185f5864a1.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"435\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p>以读书为例：我们平时看书，看完第一页，接着读第二页、第三页......那在区块链里面呢，如果给每个区块标注上页码，那么第二页的内容是包含第一页的内容的，第三页的内容包含第一页和第二页的内容......第十页包含了前九页的内容，就是这样一个层层嵌套的链条。这样一来，就可以追溯到最本源的数据了，这就是区块链的可追溯性。</p><p>二、区块链中的数据更新：分布式节点共识算法</p><p>在数据更新方面，区块链技术是利用“分布式节点共识算法”来生成和更新数据。</p><p>每每生成新的区块（也就是更新数据的时候），都需要通过一种算法获得全网51%以上节点的认可才能构成新的区块，说白了就是投票，超过半数人同意就可以生成。这就使得区块链上的数据不容篡改。</p><p>我们还是打一个比喻来解释：我们把区块链比作一个账本，因为都是记录数据的嘛。传统世界里，记账权在于记账先生，账本属于记账先生一个人的；在区块链里面，每一个人都拥有这个账本，大家一起来记账，想要更新账目呢，就要投票，半数人以上赞成才可以去更新账目数据。</p><p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/c9270c12cde8baa422bcc6a4a1266ab95f218622dbb5e.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"606\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p>在这个过程中，我们会涉及到这么几个名词：分布式、节点、共识算法：</p><p>每个人都记账（也就是人人拥有账本，账本分散在每个人手里）这就是所谓的“分布式”；大家讨论、投票产生的、一致赞同的记账办法，就是所谓的“共识算法”；节点就更简单了，参与记账的每一个人就可以看做是一个节点。</p><p>三、 区块链中的数据维护：密码学</p><p>接下来到了数据维护阶段，区块链的不同之处就在于：它利用密码学的方式来保证数据传输和访问的安全。</p><p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/298062ac48bdaaf030a5adb158015f125f21864758d6d.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"536\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p>那么，区块链中所应用的密码学原理主要有以下这么几个：哈希算法、Merkle哈希树、椭圆曲线算法、Base58。这些原理，其实呢，他们都是通过一系列复杂的运算以及换算，来保证区块链上数据安全。</p><p>四、 区块链中的数据操作：智能合约</p><p>最后就进入到了数据的操作阶段，也就是我们接着要说的“智能合约”。</p><p>智能合约，是由计算机程序定义并自动执行的承诺协议，说白了，就是用代码执行的一套交易准则，类似于现在的信用卡自动还款功能，开启这个功能，您自己什么都不用管，到期银行会自动扣除您欠的钱。</p><p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/0d7b616cb7195b3ba551d839b71d45a45f21866a53716.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p>智能合约的突出优势就是，很大程度上避免了由信任产生的一系列问题。我们很多人，都遇到过被借钱的事情：朋友手头紧了跟你借2000块钱，承诺下个月发了工资还钱，到了下个月他又找别的借口不还，拖来托去这事儿就没谱了。本来没多少钱，还是朋友，虽然你很郁闷，这事也就算了。</p><p>那么，有了智能合约以后，他就不能赖账了，因为在智能合约上，一旦触发合约中的条款，代码就会自动执行，不管他愿不愿意，只要他发了工资、账户上有了钱，他就得还你。</p><p>最后总结一下今天的内容，今天呢我们主要通过数据存储操作的这么一个流程，介绍了区块链的基本情况。我们对此做一个总结，可以发现区块链中有四项不可缺的核心技术，分别是：分布式存储、共识机制、密码学原理、智能合约。</p><p>那么，我们可以这样理解：分布式存储对应的是数据存储这个阶段，共识机制对应的是数据的处理更新这个阶段，密码学对应的是数据安全，智能合约对应的是数据的操作问题。</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (164, 81, 'zh-TW', '什麽是區塊鏈？', '<p>什麽是區塊鏈呢，本質上講，區塊鏈是一種分布式、去中心化的網絡數據庫系統，這個系統會讓數據的存儲、更新、維護、操作變得不同。</p><p>我們今天要講的區塊鏈呢，它有四項不可缺的核心技術，分別是：分布式存儲、共識機制、密碼學原理、智能合約。</p><p>那麽我們今天就講一講，與傳統數據處理相比，區塊鏈到底有什麽不同，幫助大家了解區塊鏈是什麽，讓大家對區塊鏈有一個總的認知。</p><p>一、區塊鏈中的數據存儲：塊鏈式數據結構</p><p>在數據存儲方面，區塊鏈技術利用的是“塊鏈式數據結構”來驗證與存儲數據的。塊鏈式結構是什麽意思呢？鐵鏈子大家都見過吧，一環套一環那種，其實，每一環我們可以看作是一個區塊，很多環節扣在一起就形成了區塊鏈。</p><p>區塊裏存儲的是數據，和普通存儲數據的不同之處在于：在區塊鏈上，後一個區塊裏的數據是包含前一個區塊裏的數據的。</p><p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/1e20f4048e6555a9c7ba7ef34fc157ad5f2186e9a7c4d.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"435\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p>以讀書爲例：我們平時看書，看完第一頁，接著讀第二頁、第三頁......那在區塊鏈裏面呢，如果給每個區塊標注上頁碼，那麽第二頁的內容是包含第一頁的內容的，第三頁的內容包含第一頁和第二頁的內容......第十頁包含了前九頁的內容，就是這樣一個層層嵌套的鏈條。這樣一來，就可以追溯到最本源的數據了，這就是區塊鏈的可追溯性。</p><p>二、區塊鏈中的數據更新：分布式節點共識算法</p><p>在數據更新方面，區塊鏈技術是利用“分布式節點共識算法”來生成和更新數據。</p><p>每每生成新的區塊（也就是更新數據的時候），都需要通過一種算法獲得全網51%以上節點的認可才能構成新的區塊，說白了就是投票，超過半數人同意就可以生成。這就使得區塊鏈上的數據不容篡改。</p><p>我們還是打一個比喻來解釋：我們把區塊鏈比作一個賬本，因爲都是記錄數據的嘛。傳統世界裏，記賬權在于記賬先生，賬本屬于記賬先生一個人的；在區塊鏈裏面，每一個人都擁有這個賬本，大家一起來記賬，想要更新賬目呢，就要投票，半數人以上贊成才可以去更新賬目數據。</p><p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/c9270c12cde8baa422bcc6a4a1266ab95f218705ec982.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"606\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p>在這個過程中，我們會涉及到這麽幾個名詞：分布式、節點、共識算法：</p><p>每個人都記賬（也就是人人擁有賬本，賬本分散在每個人手裏）這就是所謂的“分布式”；大家討論、投票産生的、一致贊同的記賬辦法，就是所謂的“共識算法”；節點就更簡單了，參與記賬的每一個人就可以看做是一個節點。</p><p>三、 區塊鏈中的數據維護：密碼學</p><p>接下來到了數據維護階段，區塊鏈的不同之處就在于：它利用密碼學的方式來保證數據傳輸和訪問的安全。</p><p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/298062ac48bdaaf030a5adb158015f125f21872258b98.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"536\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p>那麽，區塊鏈中所應用的密碼學原理主要有以下這麽幾個：哈希算法、Merkle哈希樹、橢圓曲線算法、Base58。這些原理，其實呢，他們都是通過一系列複雜的運算以及換算，來保證區塊鏈上數據安全。</p><p>四、 區塊鏈中的數據操作：智能合約</p><p>最後就進入到了數據的操作階段，也就是我們接著要說的“智能合約”。</p><p>智能合約，是由計算機程序定義並自動執行的承諾協議，說白了，就是用代碼執行的一套交易准則，類似于現在的信用卡自動還款功能，開啓這個功能，您自己什麽都不用管，到期銀行會自動扣除您欠的錢。</p><p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/0d7b616cb7195b3ba551d839b71d45a45f218737f3bf8.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p>智能合約的突出優勢就是，很大程度上避免了由信任産生的一系列問題。我們很多人，都遇到過被借錢的事情：朋友手頭緊了跟你借2000塊錢，承諾下個月發了工資還錢，到了下個月他又找別的借口不還，拖來托去這事兒就沒譜了。本來沒多少錢，還是朋友，雖然你很郁悶，這事也就算了。</p><p>那麽，有了智能合約以後，他就不能賴賬了，因爲在智能合約上，一旦觸發合約中的條款，代碼就會自動執行，不管他願不願意，只要他發了工資、賬戶上有了錢，他就得還你。</p><p>最後總結一下今天的內容，今天呢我們主要通過數據存儲操作的這麽一個流程，介紹了區塊鏈的基本情況。我們對此做一個總結，可以發現區塊鏈中有四項不可缺的核心技術，分別是：分布式存儲、共識機制、密碼學原理、智能合約。</p><p>那麽，我們可以這樣理解：分布式存儲對應的是數據存儲這個階段，共識機制對應的是數據的處理更新這個階段，密碼學對應的是數據安全，智能合約對應的是數據的操作問題。</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (165, 82, 'en', 'The DeFi Regulation Void: Decentralization Vs. Investor Protection', '<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/07/Artboard_1.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-71517\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Decentralized finance, commonly referred to as DeFi, has seen significant growth in the second quarter of 2020. Daily transaction volumes hit an all-time high of <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.dapp.com/article/q2-2020-dapp-market-report\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">$608 million</a> on June 21. The total USD value locked in DeFi <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://defipulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">reached</a> $1.95 billion in Q2 2020 — a quarterly growth of 311%. And since July, that value has surged to $2.83 billion.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">While much of the DeFi-related focus has been placed on <a href=\"https://www.okex.com/academy/en/the-rise-of-compound-hype-driven-bubble-or-indicator-of-defis-strength\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">the rise of Compound</a> and <a href=\"https://www.okex.com/academy/en/dex-and-the-defi-wave-liquidity-security-and-the-road-to-mass-adoption\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">the surging volumes on decentralized exchanges</a>, not a lot has been said about the development of regulatory frameworks for the emerging industry niche. With that in mind, stai Insights examines the regulatory environment for crypto-lending platforms and decentralized exchanges. </p><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The key differences between centralized and decentralized crypto-lending platforms</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Loan transactions in the crypto-lending market <a href=\"https://reports.credmark.com/TheCryptoCreditReport-q4-2019.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">reached $8 billion</a> in Q4 2019, up 700% from 2018. The sum, however, remains infantile when compared to the traditional lending market, which boasts an <a href=\"https://www.statista.com/outlook/338/100/marketplace-lending--consumer-/worldwide\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">annual transaction volume</a> of $85 billion. Still, the crypto-lending market is rapidly gaining traction — and both centralized and decentralized lending platforms are the key players in the nascent industry.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Centralized crypto-lending platforms, such as BlockFi and Celsius Network, are similar to traditional financial service companies, in so much as they <a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/leeorshimron/2020/05/26/exploding-past-10b-interest-income-and-lending-are-bitcoins-first-killer-apps/#76b854533320\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">retain full control</a> when matching and executing loan requests between borrowers and lenders. The activities of centralized crypto-lending platforms include safekeeping clients’ assets and determining the interest rates of crypto assets. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Conversely, decentralized crypto-lending platforms make use of smart contracts to remove the need for centralized third parties to act as middlemen. Smart contracts are used for executing loan transactions, determining interest rates for crypto assets and storing the collateral for both lenders and borrowers. Compound and Maker are two examples of decentralized crypto-lending platforms.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">There are four key differences between centralized and decentralized crypto-lending platforms: </p><ul style=\"padding: 0px 10px; margin: 0px 12px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); line-height: 22px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Custody</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Governance</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Compliance</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Profit model</li></ul><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Centralized platforms are custodial</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Centralized crypto-lending platforms are custodial, which means that users’ collateral is kept by the lending platform or a third-party custodian. From the lender\'s perspective, it is the platform’s responsibility to mitigate counterparty risk. Lenders assume that the platform can safeguard their assets and ensure the borrower repays the loan on time.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">BlockFi is one notable example among custodial crypto-lending platforms, as client assets are <a href=\"https://blockfi.com/securely-stored-assets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">deposited</a> with a third-party custodian. When users send their collateral to BlockFi, it is then transferred to a cold storage system provided by Gemini, a regulated cryptocurrency exchange, wallet and custodian. Borrowers cannot access the collateral until they have paid off their loans.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A regulated, centralized crypto custodian provides additional investor protections for users. In the case of BlockFi, Gemini (i.e., the custodian) <a href=\"https://www.dfs.ny.gov/reports_and_publications/press_releases/pr1805141\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">obtained a trust license</a> from the New York State Department of Financial Services — a requirement to be compliant with specific capital reserve needs and banking compliance standards under §100 of the New York Banking Law. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Decentralized platforms are non-custodial</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">On the other side of the spectrum, decentralized lending platforms are non-custodial, meaning they don’t have direct access to user funds. Borrowers and lenders in DeFi lending platforms rely on smart contracts to minimize counterparty risk — they trust that said smart contracts can execute loan transactions without any technical glitches or exploitable loopholes. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The current leader in decentralized finance, Compound, is an example of a non-custodial lending platform. Users supply collateral to borrow other crypto assets. The collateral is represented by a smart contract called cToken — which is <a href=\"https://compound.finance/docs/ctokens\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">stored and managed</a> by Compound users themselves rather than by the Compound team or third-party custodians.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Who governs a decentralized lending platform?</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The difference in the approach to governance between centralized and decentralized lending platforms can be reflected by the purpose of the platforms’ native tokens.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The governance of centralized lending platforms is, generally speaking, controlled by the core development team. The platform’s native tokens are awarded to users primarily for transactional purposes. In the case of Celsius Network, its native token, CEL, <a href=\"https://celsius.network/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/celsius_whitepaper-march21.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">allows</a> users to issue loans, collect interest and lend cryptocurrencies. Payment platform Crypto.com’s native token, CRO, also <a href=\"https://cryptobriefing.com/what-is-monaco-introduction-crypto-com-mco-token/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">serves</a> as a means of payment and settlement on the company’s native blockchain. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The native tokens of decentralized lending platforms, on the other hand, allow users to participate in the governance process of the platforms. The primary example would be Compound, which allows users to vote on governance proposals using the protocol’s native token, COMP. For example, token-holders recently <a href=\"https://compound.finance/governance/proposals/16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">voted</a> to increase the collateral factor of WBTC from 0% to 40% — allowing users to loan WBTC while using 40% of its value as collateral.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Centralized crypto-lending platforms are more compliant</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">When it comes to compliance, centralized crypto-lending protocols have stricter requirements — particularly to comply with existing Know Your Customer and Anti-Money Laundering regulations in jurisdictions where they operate — than decentralized lending protocols. For example, to abide by KYC/AML procedures when applying for a loan, BlockFi users must <a href=\"https://blockfi.com/privacy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">disclose</a> their personal information — including their social security number, wallet public keys and bank information.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Conversely, KYC/AML procedures are typically not required for users on decentralized crypto-lending platforms. Kristi Swartz, managing partner at Swartz, Binnersley & Associates, uses Compound as an example to express her concerns about the lack of investor protection for users of decentralized lending platforms. She told stai Insights: </p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“One disadvantage of decentralization is that investor protection becomes much harder as traditional tools, such as circuit breakers, are not available. Compound, which automatically sets interest rates based on supply and demand, is partially able to achieve stability. However, it may not be enough. By analogy, the central banks do not and cannot rely on interest rates alone to achieve financial/monetary stability.”</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">She also commented on the possibility for some compliance measures for investor protections to be written into the protocol’s smart contracts:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“As human intervention is minimal in DeFi — or, at least, it is supposed to be — any measures must be coded into the protocol itself. Examples could include more stringent risk management policies or requirements to take into account the lack of credit scoring and lower level of human supervision.”</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">How do crypto-lending platforms make profits?</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">When comparing centralized and decentralized crypto-lending platforms, an obvious question that arises is that of profit models.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Similar to traditional lending platforms, centralized crypto-lending platforms primarily use a profit model that is based on the interest-rate spread — i.e., the difference between the interest rate received from borrowers and the interest rate paid to lenders. A higher interest-rate spread indicates higher profitability.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Additionally, traditional financial institutions are emerging clientele for centralized lending platforms. For example, BlockFi <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://blockfi.com/blockfi-news/blockfi-introduces-institutional-services/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">offers</a> services to institutional lending desks and provides liquidity to institutional borrowers. Celsius Network is also seeing increased institutional demand. Alex Mashinsky, the company’s CEO, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://cointelegraph.com/news/celsius-network-is-profitable-and-resisting-market-downturn-claims-ceo\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">said</a> in an interview in March that on the Celsius Network, “close to 100% of the borrowers are institutions.”</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">On the other hand, decentralized lending platforms are not profit-generating by nature. However, those who hold the platform’s governance token, in theory, will profit from the platform’s use. Maker, the second-largest decentralized lending platform, <a href=\"https://makerdao.com/en/whitepaper/#use-of-the-mkr-token-in-maker-governance\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">earns revenue</a> from stability fees and liquidation penalty fees. The revenue is then redistributed to holders of the Maker token, MKR, which is used to build <a href=\"https://github.com/compound-finance/compound-oracle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">price oracle infrastructure</a> and support collateral risk management research.</p><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Centralized and decentralized cryptocurrency exchange regulation</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Apart from crypto-lending platforms, the regulation of decentralized cryptocurrency exchanges — commonly referred to as DEXs — is another important indicator of the sustainable development of DeFi.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">While there is no global consensus when it comes to the regulation of cryptocurrency exchanges in general, the United States has proven to be one of the more inflexible regulators and active enforcers in the space. In a sense, U.S. regulations can serve as a bellwether for many other nations to follow. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">How the United States views centralized and decentralized exchanges</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, as the regulator of securities-trading in the country, <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/litigation/investreport/34-81207.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">first applied crypto-related rules</a> pertaining to the hack of a decentralized autonomous organization called The Dao in June 2016, in which <a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/understanding-dao-hack-journalists\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">3.6 million ether</a> (about $44.6 million at the time) was stolen from the platform. According to the agency’s <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/litigation/investreport/34-81207.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">report</a> on July 25, 2017, the SEC stated that if a trading platform is operated as an exchange and offers digital assets that are securities, it needs to register with the SEC as a national securities exchange (or meet the requirements to be exempt from registration) in order to comply with federal securities law. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Jay Clayton, the chairman of the SEC since 2017, noted in a <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/news/public-statement/statement-clayton-2017-12-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">statement</a> from November 2017 that market participants, including exchanges, should not undermine AML or KYC obligations for any cryptocurrency activities conducted. He stressed that exchanges should treat payments and transactions in cryptocurrencies the same way as cash transactions.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Clayton then released <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/news/testimony/testimony-virtual-currencies-oversight-role-us-securities-and-exchange-commission#_ftn14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">testimony</a> in February 2018 that expressed his concerns regarding cryptocurrencies. The SEC chairman noted that trading platforms listing tokens sold in initial coin offerings did not provide appropriate investor protections in line with transacting through broker-dealers on registered exchanges or alternative trading systems. These investor protections include best execution, short-sale restrictions, prohibitions on front running, and custody and capital requirements.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The SEC then released a <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/news/public-statement/enforcement-tm-statement-potentially-unlawful-online-platforms-trading\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">statement</a> in March 2018 regarding exchanges that trade digital assets — reminding them that they do not have the same standards of integrity as a registered national securities exchange. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">EtherDelta: The landmark ruling on decentralized exchanges</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Decentralized exchanges, for their part, first came under the regulatory spotlight with the SEC’s <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/news/press-release/2018-258\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">ruling on EtherDelta</a> — a landmark decision in the history of DEX regulation.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">EtherDelta is a decentralized exchange offering ether and ERC-20 token trading. After two years of operation, founder Zachary Coburn was charged by the SEC with operating an unregistered exchange — the first case of such enforcement against decentralized exchanges. Coburn consented to the order and agreed to pay $300,000 in disgorgement, $13,000 in prejudgment interest, and a penalty of $75,000. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The key question in this ruling revolved around whether or not EtherDelta offered securities trading and, as a result, needed to register with the SEC to serve U.S. users.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">EtherDelta offered securities trading</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In the SEC’s aforementioned report on The DAO, the regulatory body referred to the Howey Test to <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/corpfin/framework-investment-contract-analysis-digital-assets\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">determine</a> whether digital tokens — or any asset for that matter — are securities. The Howey Test lists three key criteria:</p><ol style=\"padding: 0px 20px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: decimal; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">The investment of money</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: decimal; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Common enterprise</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: decimal; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Reasonable expectation of profits derived from the effort of others</li></ol><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In the EtherDelta ruling, the SEC first identified the time frame during which Coburn founded and operated the exchange as the relevant period — from July 12, 2016 to Dec. 15, 2017. During the relevant period, the regulator concluded that there were more than 3.6 million buy and sell orders of ERC-20 tokens. Approximately 92% were traded during the period after the SEC released The DAO report.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In regard to the ERC-20 tokens offered by EtherDelta, the SEC <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/litigation/admin/2018/34-84553.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">ruled</a> that users purchased certain ERC-20 tokens with a reasonable expectation of profiting. Such expectations came from the operational effort by Coburn, where users expected an increase in the value of their investment in secondary trading. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">For instance, Coburn provided frequent updates to EtherDelta’s users via Twitter and Reddit, which users may have utilized in an effort to make more informed decisions when trading ERC-20 tokens on EtherDelta. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This expectation of profit from EtherDelta’s users is consistent with the third requirement under the Howey Test. However, the SEC did not specify which ERC-20 tokens offered in EtherDelta met the definition of securities.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">EtherDelta met the definition of an exchange</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The SEC <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/litigation/admin/2018/34-84553.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">concluded</a> that EtherDelta met the definition of an exchange — plus, at least some of the tokens traded on it could be considered securities. As such, EtherDelta was required to register as a national securities exchange, pursuant to <a href=\"https://www.nyse.com/publicdocs/nyse/regulation/nyse/sea34.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">Section 5 of the Exchange Act</a>. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">To assess whether EtherDelta met the definition of an exchange, the SEC used a functional test under <a href=\"https://www.law.cornell.edu/cfr/text/17/240.3b-16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">Rule 3b-16(a) of the Exchange Act</a>. In the application of the test, the SEC found that EtherDelta used its order book to gather trading orders of multiple buyers and sellers. Furthermore, the platform leveraged its website, order book and pre-programmed trading protocols as established and nondiscretionary methods for users to trade during the relevant period. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">As such, EtherDelta met the two criteria set in the functional test and, therefore, met the requirements to be considered an exchange under <a href=\"https://www.law.cornell.edu/cfr/text/17/240.3a1-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">Section 3(a)(1) of the Exchange Act</a>.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">Coburn’s action on EtherDelta led to violation of the Exchange Act</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Though EtherDelta was required to register as a national securities exchange to stay compliant, Coburn did not do so during the relevant period. According to the SEC, this led to a violation of Section 5 of the Exchange Act. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">As the founder of EtherDelta, Coburn was responsible for writing and deploying the platform’s smart contract on the Ethereum blockchain. As Coburn had complete and sole control over EtherDelta’s operations, the SEC stated that he should have known the failure to register as a national securities exchange would lead to the violation.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Smart contract regulation remains limited</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">While the EtherDelta ruling serves as a landmark and potentially precedential court decision for approaching decentralized exchanges, existing regulation has limited applicability to protect investors from smart contract vulnerabilities. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In her conversation with stai Insights, Kristi Swartz explained the key obstacles to regulating smart contracts — and specifically, potential implications for the developers behind them. She stated:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“At the heart of a smart contract, there is, by legal definition, a contract — even though it appears to be wearing a new outfit. The terms of the smart contract form the legal agreement between the two parties. That being said, consideration should be made as to whether the developer of the smart contract should also be liable.” </p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">According to Swartz, determining liability when it comes to smart contracts is a complicated matter. Whereas a law firm may be sued for the negligent drafting of a traditional contract, it isn’t entirely clear who assumes the risk for a potentially exploitable smart contract.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Furthermore, determining which regulatory body should have authority over smart contracts is another issue entirely. Swartz explained:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“Similarly, consideration should be given as to governance — which regulator may be involved, which governing law does the contract rely on? Regulations may only have limited protection for smart contract vulnerabilities. Parties will still need to do their own due diligence on the smart contract in order to determine that it is fit for purposes. As the Latin phrase goes, ‘caveat emptor’ — buyer, beware!”</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 20px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The FATF’s recommendation on cryptocurrency exchanges</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Apart from the United States, other countries and organizations are actively exploring the regulation of cryptocurrency exchanges. One notable example is the intergovernmental body the Financial Action Task Force.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In June 2019, the FATF <a href=\"https://www.fatf-gafi.org/media/fatf/documents/recommendations/pdfs/FATF%20Recommendations%202012.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">released</a> an updated recommendation on international standards to combat money laundering and terrorist financing. In particular, it <a href=\"https://www.fatf-gafi.org/publications/fatfrecommendations/documents/public-statement-virtual-assets.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">issued</a> an “Interpretive Note to Recommendation 15 on New Technologies” to further clarify how the FATF requirements should apply to virtual asset service providers, such as cryptocurrency exchanges. As defined by the regulator, VASPs include fiat-to-crypto exchanges and crypto-to-crypto exchanges. Whether the exchange is centralized or decentralized is, evidently, outside the scope of the FATF’s recommendations.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The core piece of regulation extended to cryptocurrency exchanges related to the FATF is Recommendation 16 — commonly known as the “travel rule.” As originally applied to traditional banks, the travel rule now requires cryptocurrency exchanges to collect and share customer data pertaining to cryptocurrency transactions. The data <a href=\"https://www.pwc.com/gx/en/industries/financial-services/assets/pwc-crypto-client-update-fatf-vasp-guidance-august-2019.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">includes</a> the name and wallet address of the originator and beneficiary, as well as the sender’s address and proof of identity. Cryptocurrency exchanges need to ensure that the information of the sender and receiver in each transaction is recorded and made available upon request to relevant regulatory authorities.</p><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">What’s missing in DeFi regulation?</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Despite the recent popularity of Compound and decentralized exchanges, the DeFi sphere is still in its infancy — particularly in regard to regulatory compliance. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">One of the reasons DeFi currently has so few specific regulations applied to it is simply due to the fact that regulators have a limited understanding of the DeFi ecosystem. Swartz told stai Insights that she believes regulators are taking a reactive approach to DeFi regulation rather than a proactive one. She explained:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“By its very nature, DeFi is designed to be permissionless and, currently, operates within the ‘grey’ area of the financial industry — which, as we know, is a highly-regulated market. Currently, DeFi operators seem to have an unspoken ‘code of conduct’ in which they are good players in the space. Regulators are clearly watching the space carefully and, as we know, are reactive in approach rather than proactive. One transaction could topple the apple cart, so to speak.” </p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Swartz then identified the missing pieces in the DeFi regulation puzzle — namely, the scale of the oversight and the treatment of both DEXs and stablecoins. She explained to stai Insights:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“With respect to regulation as a whole, in my opinion, this needs to be considered with a broad brush and the first step is to identify whether the space should have local or global oversight. The question is, then, which prudential authority should regulate which aspect of DeFi — which will, in turn, require consensus on the framework. For instance, should a DEX be regulated by a securities and futures regulator? Should stablecoins be regulated by the central bank?”</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">For Swartz, there needs to be a correct balance between innovation-stifling over-regulation and high-risk under-regulation. “There needs to be sophisticated legislation brought into play to provide ample consumer protection, governance and guiding principles to operators who wish to leverage this space honestly,” she said.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Jake Chervinsky, general counsel of Compound, shared a similar sentiment when he told stai Insights that regulators should allow ample room for DeFi to grow. “It\'s too early to say whether any new regulations are needed to address DeFi protocols or tokens,” he explained. “DeFi has just barely started to emerge as an exciting use case for digital assets. It would be a mistake to rush new regulations before the space has time to develop.\"</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">Disclaimer: This material should not be taken as the basis for making investment decisions, nor be construed as a recommendation to engage in investment transactions. Trading digital assets involve significant risk and can result in the loss of your invested capital. You should ensure that you fully understand the risk involved and take into consideration your level of experience, investment objectives and seek independent financial advice if necessary.</em></p>', 'The DeFi Regulation Void: Decentralization Vs. Investor Protection');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (166, 82, 'zh-CN', '莱特币（LTC）现状调查研究', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">（LTC）简介</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">1）莱特币（LTC）的前世今生</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">莱特币（Litecoin），简写LTC，货币符号Ł，创始者李启威（Charlie Lee），LTC代表着轻量级，是对比<a href=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/zh\" class=\"seo-words\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; user-select: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105) !important;\">比特币</a>来讲更为轻量级的数字货币。它与比特币（BTC）在技术上具有相同的实现原理，其创造和转让基于一种开源的加密协议，不受到任何中央机构的管理。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">历史大事记：</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2011年10月7日莱特币通过Github上面的开源客户端进行发布。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2015年8月26日，莱特币首次减半，每个区块产出量由50降至25个莱特币。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2016年7月3日，莱特币内核开发团队和莱特币协会发布了“莱特币官方2016年开发路线图”，宣称将发布带有“隔离见证”、“闪电网络”、“智能合约”等功能的新版本。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2017年5月11日，隔离见证在莱特币第1201536个区块正式激活，莱特币用户可使用隔离见证这种新的交易方式。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2017年6月21日，莱特币创始人正式宣布莱特币闪电网络上线。闪电网络本质上是使用了哈希时间锁定智能合约来安全地进行0确认交易的一种机制。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">莱特币拥有完整的产业链和充分的流动性，全球莱特币ATM的数量仅次于比特币，矿工和算力、交易平台、开发者、接受支付的商家和粉丝持续增长。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">2）莱特币的机制</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">莱特币被称为是“数字白银”，是第一个基于Scrypt算法的网络数字货币，与比特币相比，莱特币具有三个显著差异：</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（1）莱特币网络每2.5分钟（而不是10分钟）就可以处理一个块，提供更快的交易确认。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（2）莱特币网络预期产出8400万个莱特币，是比特币发行货币量的四倍。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（3）莱特币在工作量证明算法中使用了由Colin Percival首次提出的Scrypt加密算法，相比于比特币使用的SHA256算法，Scrypt算法对挖掘处理能力要求不高，只需要高速访问内存，更容易在普通计算机上挖矿。Scrpyt算法由于其内存依赖的设计特别符合对抗专业矿机的设计，成为数字货币算法发展的一个主要应用方向。Scrpyt算法提醒了人们对于算力中心化的认识，开启了人们对于hash计算去中心化安全的探索，促进了区块链系统向更好的方向发展。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">3）莱特币减产</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">每4年，莱特币将进行减产，每个区块挖出的莱特币减半，上一次减半发生在2015年8月26日，莱特币的区块奖励由50个减半到25个。产量减半从理论上来说会导致供需不平衡，价格上涨，但实际情况却有很多影响因素，15年莱特币减半从其价格表现上可以看出，减半后并没有发生价格上涨，反而有些跌幅。从今天的视角看过去，有几个原因可以作为解释。</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-cd8e64b89b9411fdb6db2818fb2e548b_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">2015年LTC减半前后两个月的走势</figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一是在这之前，LTC已经进行了充分的上涨，7月10日曾达到当时最高点8.967美金，市场预期已经得到了充分的体现。二是当时整个数字货币的体量还十分小，应用场景也很有限，过度的炒作使其价格过多偏离价值，实际需求占比很小，减半影响甚微。第三，当价格没有上涨的情况下，减半致使矿工立减一半，高成本的矿工将入不敷出，只得选择关机。而实际上，LTC算力在减半后有一定幅度的下降，价格受此影响反而持续走低。因此8月27日，莱特币已经迎来了减半之后的第一次难度调整，降低7.61%。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这是发生在2015年的历史，历史不代表未来，现在整个加密货币市场已经不能同日而语，LTC也是如此，接下来stai Research将就LTC目前的状况做全面的研究和分析。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">2. 莱特币（LTC）的现状</span></p><div class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-3e53fccac28b5563c5dd7deeec17073f_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">LTC目前基本情况</figcaption></figure></div><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">LTC总供给量8400万个，目前已经挖出6100多万个，现价60美金一个，总市值36.7亿美金，排名第四。</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-418b0d859e519eaf5e18bd6d5933c668_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">LTC历史价格走势</figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">链上交易情况</span></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-fcfc60d9625909a3f684924b6b72ec13_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">LTC等币种链上交易数据对比</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6eb29744cf7606be7c773afed5b7e628_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">近3个月LTC平均手续费</figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">LTC链上交易数与交易额相较于BTC、ETH还有不少差距，但考虑到其市值和用户群体规模，以及24小时交易额能够占到总市值的5.51%，并有55822个活跃地址，LTC的链上交易可以说还是相当活跃的，尤其近三个月，从其交易手续费的走势可以看出，链上交易在逐渐活跃并保持着增长。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">LTC分布情况</span></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-3e3cecfb8e1472c7ecbe669a6d0c7e61_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">LTC分配情况</figcaption></figure><div class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4cf58f15e253157b9c6cd1a619c31a9c_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">前10、100、1000地址持币占比</figcaption></figure></div><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">LTC的分配情况显示出目前加密货币领域的通病，大量的筹码集中在少数头部的地址当中，前500位地址占据LTC近60%的量，但相较于其他小币种，LTC地址的分配情况已经较为分散，跟大部分主流币的情况差不多，并且这其中包涵了中心化交易所的地址。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">LTC矿池</span></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-c5e1dacb4a58fda780041037e6930509_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">LTC矿池份额</figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">LTC矿池份额占比基本都比较均有，最高的F2Pool占比20.45%，前几大矿池的占比都比较接近，这有利于维护币种的安全和矿工的利益，而全网总共269.77TH/s的算力，相较于BTC 47.31 EH/s和BCH 1.6EH/s还是有一定的差距。 </p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4e9c82fa65f3e03247a533d1381afdac_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">LTC最后100个区块的哈希分配</figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">Github代码更新频率</span></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2154\" data-permalink=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/zh/litecoin-the-silver-to-bitcoins-gold-i-cn/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd\" data-orig-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"720,386\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}\" data-image-title=\"v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd-300x161.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd.jpg\" src=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd.jpg\" alt=\"preview\" class=\"wp-image-2154\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">LTC在Github代码更新频率一直保持不错的情况，最近三个月有所减缓。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">谷歌指数</span></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c5da5ccebaab0cad04de6e34ce2d281f_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">谷歌趋势</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2156\" data-permalink=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/zh/litecoin-the-silver-to-bitcoins-gold-i-cn/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd\" data-orig-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"720,243\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}\" data-image-title=\"v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd-300x101.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd.jpg\" src=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2156\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">谷歌趋势分布</figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从谷歌趋势可以看出，LTC近一年的热度在主流币当中都是处于较高的位置，而关注LTC的地区主要集中在美洲和欧洲，尤其在美国、加拿大和维瑞内拉。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">结论</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从以上数据基本可以一览LTC整个项目目前的基本情况，从其链活跃程度、分配情况、矿池份额、算力、代码更新、谷歌趋势可以看出，LTC整条链保持良好的运行情况，作为市值排名第四的加密货币，其链上活跃程度、去中心化程度以及谷歌趋势相较于其他主流币种也有不错的表现，但同样，加密货币的通病在其身上也有充分的体现。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不过，这仅仅是一些表面数据的罗列和展现，下篇我们将会对LTC的通证循环、挖矿机制、支付生态及其落地模块进展做详细的分析和讨论</p>', '莱特币（LTC）现状调查研究');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (167, 82, 'zh-TW', '萊特幣（LTC）現狀調查研究', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">（LTC）簡介</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">1）萊特幣（LTC）的前世今生</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">萊特幣（Litecoin），簡寫LTC，貨幣符號Ł，創始者李啟威（Charlie Lee），LTC代表著輕量級，是對比比特幣來講更為輕量級的數字貨幣。它與比特幣（BTC）在技術上具有相同的實現原理，其創造和轉讓基於一種開源的加密協議，不受到任何中央機構的管理。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">歷史大事記：</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">2011年10月7日萊特幣通過Github上面的開源客戶端進行發布。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">2015年8月26日，萊特幣首次減半，每個區塊產出量由50降至25個萊特幣。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">2016年7月3日，萊特幣內核開發團隊和萊特幣協會發布了“萊特幣官方2016年開發路線圖”，宣稱將發布帶有“隔離見證”、“閃電網絡”、“智能合約”等功能的新版本。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">2017年5月11日，隔離見證在萊特幣第1201536個區塊正式激活，萊特幣用戶可使用隔離見證這種新的交易方式。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">2017年6月21日，萊特幣創始人正式宣布萊特幣閃電網絡上線。閃電網絡本質上是使用了哈希時間鎖定智能合約來安全地進行0確認交易的一種機制。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">萊特幣擁有完整的產業鍊和充分的流動性，全球萊特幣ATM的數量僅次於比特幣，礦工和算力、交易平台、開發者、接受支付的商家和粉絲持續增長。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">2）萊特幣的機制</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">萊特幣被稱為是“數字白銀”，是第一個基於Scrypt算法的網絡數字貨幣，與比特幣相比，萊特幣具有三個顯著差異：</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">（1）萊特幣網絡每2.5分鐘（而不是10分鐘）就可以處理一個塊，提供更快的交易確認。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">（2）萊特幣網絡預期產出8400萬個萊特幣，是比特幣發行貨幣量的四倍。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">（3）萊特幣在工作量證明算法中使用了由Colin Percival首次提出的Scrypt加密算法，相比於比特幣使用的SHA256算法，Scrypt算法對挖掘處理能力要求不高，只需要高速訪問內存，更容易在普通計算機上挖礦。 Scrpyt算法由於其內存依賴的設計特別符合對抗專業礦機的設計，成為數字貨幣算法發展的一個主要應用方向。 Scrpyt算法提醒了人們對於算力中心化的認識，開啟了人們對於hash計算去中心化安全的探索，促進了區塊鏈系統向更好的方向發展。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">3）萊特幣減產</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">每4年，萊特幣將進行減產，每個區塊挖出的萊特幣減半，上一次減半發生在2015年8月26日，萊特幣的區塊獎勵由50個減半到25個。產量減半從理論上來說會導致供需不平衡，價格上漲，但實際情況卻有很多影響因素，15年萊特幣減半從其價格表現上可以看出，減半後並沒有發生價格上漲，反而有些跌幅。從今天的視角看過去，有幾個原因可以作為解釋。</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#1f2236\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto;\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-cd8e64b89b9411fdb6db2818fb2e548b_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></span></font><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2015年LTC減半前後兩個月的走勢</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">一是在這之前，LTC已經進行了充分的上漲，7月10日曾達到當時最高點8.967美金，市場預期已經得到了充分的體現。二是當時整個數字貨幣的體量還十分小，應用場景也很有限，過度的炒作使其價格過多偏離價值，實際需求佔比很小，減半影響甚微。第三，當價格沒有上漲的情況下，減半致使礦工立減一半，高成本的礦工將入不敷出，只得選擇關機。而實際上，LTC算力在減半後有一定幅度的下降，價格受此影響反而持續走低。因此8月27日，萊特幣已經迎來了減半之後的第一次難度調整，降低7.61%。</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">這是發生在2015年的歷史，歷史不代表未來，現在整個加密貨幣市場已經不能同日而語，LTC也是如此，接下來OKEx Research將就LTC目前的狀況做全面的研究和分析。</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">2. 萊特幣（LTC）的現狀</span><br></figcaption></figcaption></figure><div class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><font color=\"#1f2236\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto;\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-3e53fccac28b5563c5dd7deeec17073f_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></span></font><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">LTC目前基本情況</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">LTC總供給量8400萬個，目前已經挖出6100多萬個，現價60美金一個，總市值36.7億美金，排名第四。</span></font></figcaption></figcaption></figure></div><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-418b0d859e519eaf5e18bd6d5933c668_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">LTC历史价格走势</figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">链上交易情况</span><br></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-fcfc60d9625909a3f684924b6b72ec13_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">TC等幣種鏈上交易數據對比</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#1f2236\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto;\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6eb29744cf7606be7c773afed5b7e628_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></span></font><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">近3個月LTC平均手續費</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">LTC鏈上交易數與交易額相較於BTC、ETH還有不少差距，但考慮到其市值和用戶群體規模，以及24小時交易額能夠占到總市值的5.51%，並有55822個活躍地址，LTC的鏈上交易可以說還是相當活躍的，尤其近三個月，從其交易手續費的走勢可以看出，鏈上交易在逐漸活躍並保持著增長。</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">LTC分佈情況</span></font></figcaption></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-3e3cecfb8e1472c7ecbe669a6d0c7e61_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">LTC分配情況</figcaption></figure><div class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><font color=\"#1f2236\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto;\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4cf58f15e253157b9c6cd1a619c31a9c_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></span></font><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">前10、100、1000地址持幣佔比</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">LTC的分配情況顯示出目前加密貨幣領域的通病，大量的籌碼集中在少數頭部的地址當中，前500位地址佔據LTC近60%的量，但相較於其他小幣種，LTC地址的分配情況已經較為分散，跟大部分主流幣的情況差不多，並且這其中包涵了中心化交易所的地址。</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">LTC礦池</span></font></figcaption></figcaption></figure></div><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#1f2236\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto;\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-c5e1dacb4a58fda780041037e6930509_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></span></font><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">LTC礦池份額</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">LTC礦池份額佔比基本都比較均有，最高的F2Pool佔比20.45%，前幾大礦池的佔比都比較接近，這有利於維護幣種的安全和礦工的利益，而全網總共269.77 TH/s的算力，相較於BTC 47.31 EH/s和BCH 1.6EH/s還是有一定的差距。</span></font></figcaption></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#1f2236\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto;\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4e9c82fa65f3e03247a533d1381afdac_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></span></font><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">LTC最後100個區塊的哈希分配</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Github代碼更新頻率</span></font><font face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2154\" data-permalink=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/zh/litecoin-the-silver-to-bitcoins-gold-i-cn/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd\" data-orig-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"720,386\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}\" data-image-title=\"v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd-300x161.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd.jpg\" src=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd.jpg\" alt=\"preview\" class=\"wp-image-2154\" style=\"color: rgb(31, 34, 54); padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></span></font><br></figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">LTC在Github代碼更新頻率一直保持不錯的情況，最近三個月有所減緩。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">谷歌指數</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c5da5ccebaab0cad04de6e34ce2d281f_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\">谷歌趋势</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#1f2236\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2156\" data-permalink=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/zh/litecoin-the-silver-to-bitcoins-gold-i-cn/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd\" data-orig-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"720,243\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}\" data-image-title=\"v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd-300x101.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd.jpg\" src=\"https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2156\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></span></font><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">谷歌趨勢分佈</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">從谷歌趨勢可以看出，LTC近一年的熱度在主流幣當中都是處於較高的位置，而關注LTC的地區主要集中在美洲和歐洲，尤其在美國、加拿大和維瑞內拉。</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">結論</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">從以上數據基本可以一覽LTC整個項目目前的基本情況，從其鏈活躍程度、分配情況、礦池份額、算力、代碼更新、谷歌趨勢可以看出，LTC整條鏈保持良好的運行情況，作為市值排名第四的加密貨幣，其鏈上活躍程度、去中心化程度以及谷歌趨勢相較於其他主流幣種也有不錯的表現，但同樣，加密貨幣的通病在其身上也有充分的體現。</span></font></figcaption><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; line-height: 20px;\"><font color=\"#222a3c\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">不過，這僅僅是一些表面數據的羅列和展現，下篇我們將會對LTC的通證循環、挖礦機制、支付生態及其落地模塊進展做詳細的分析和討論</span></font></figcaption></figcaption></figure>', '萊特幣（LTC）現狀調查研究');
