INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (171, 84, 'en', 'DEXs Ride the DeFi Wave: Liquidity, Security and the Road to Mass Adoption', '<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/06/dex.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"DEX image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Decentralized finance, or DeFi, has recently been the focus of interest and discussion in the broader crypto community. The total value in USD locked in the DeFi market&nbsp;<a href=\"https://defipulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">surpassed</a>&nbsp;$2 billion for the first time in July. The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cointelegraph.com/news/users-surge-but-just-five-defi-projects-account-for-94-of-locked-funds\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">number of users</a>&nbsp;in the DeFi market also witnessed considerable growth, reaching almost 240,000 as of July 6.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The recent explosive growth of the DeFi niche is believed to be driven by one lending protocol in particular, Compound, which began to gain popularity starting with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.okex.com/academy/en/the-rise-of-compound-hype-driven-bubble-or-indicator-of-defis-strength\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">distribution</a>&nbsp;of its governance token COMP in mid-June. Compound quickly overtook fellow Ethereum-based lending protocol, Maker, as the leading DeFi project, reaching&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.okex.com/academy/en/introducing-defis-top-5-projects-in-terms-of-total-value-locked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">almost $700 million</a>&nbsp;in assets locked on the protocol as of July 9.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The hype around DeFi appears to have also benefited decentralized exchanges, commonly referred to as DEXs. Data from Ethereum analytics service Dune Analytics&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/decentralized-exchange-volumes-up-70-in-june-pass-1-5-billion\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">indicates</a>&nbsp;that trading volumes on DEXs set an all-time high of $1.52 billion in June — a 70% increase from May. In particular, DEX platforms Uniswap and Curve dominated the market, with $446 million and $350 million volume traded, respectively.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/fed1da6da79ca8f0cba2aa0c88e14d9e5f2181c9600aa.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"447\" alt=\"\"><br></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">OKEx Insights examines the reasons behind decentralized exchanges’ recent surge in popularity — as well as the current state of liquidity, security and user experiences DEXs offer.</p><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Centralized vs. decentralized exchanges</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Most crypto exchanges are centralized. Exchanges like OKEx have long been the primary locations for cryptocurrency trading, among other offerings. In the case of these custodial exchanges, users’ funds are kept by a trusted middleman — usually the operator of the exchange. This essentially creates a system with a single point of failure, as the exchange usually has full control of users’ assets.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This has made centralized exchanges prime targets for hackers, who are able to steal millions by exploiting vulnerabilities. For instance, the $500 million&nbsp;<a href=\"https://fortune.com/2018/01/31/coincheck-hack-how/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">Coincheck hack</a>&nbsp;in January 2018 raised widespread concerns about whether centralized cryptocurrency exchanges can safeguard users’ assets in a transparent manner.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">After a series of major cryptocurrency exchange hacks in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/daveywinder/2018/12/31/how-hackers-stole-1b-from-cryptocurrency-exchanges-in-2018/#160f9f1f4d87\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">2018</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cointelegraph.com/news/most-significant-hacks-of-2019-new-record-of-twelve-in-one-year\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">2019</a>, users began to consider decentralized exchanges. On a DEX, trading is executed through smart contracts on a blockchain. This implies that there is no third party involved in the transaction and that users have full control over their own cryptocurrencies.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Compared to centralized cryptocurrency exchanges, DEXs have no single point of failure as users have full control over their own funds. This makes it more difficult for hackers to steal huge sums of cryptocurrencies, as the time and cost required for hacking is much higher than that on centralized cryptocurrency exchanges.</p><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Decentralized exchanges are finally seeing volume</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Decentralized exchanges gained short-term traction in 2018 with their non-custodial nature and alleged enhanced security. However, the hype surrounding DEXs largely faded due to low trading volumes when compared to centralized exchanges.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">For instance, IDEX&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/decentralized-exchange-crypto-dex\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">saw</a>&nbsp;69,339 swaps in two weeks in July 2018, while Bitfinex facilitated 92,024 swap contracts in just two days. Following the peak of $1.5 billion traded on DEXs in May 2018, Diar research&nbsp;<a href=\"https://diar.co/volume-3-issue-3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">reported</a>&nbsp;that DEX trading volume hit a monthly low of $49 million in January 2019.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">DEXs have begun to gain traction once again in 2020 following the rise of Compound and the larger DeFi space. For example, total trading volume on decentralized exchange Curve&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curve.fi/dailystats\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">grew</a>&nbsp;almost 500% from around $7.1 million at the start of COMP distribution on June 16 to its record peak of over $42 million on June 21.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">With DeFi mania reaching a fever pitch, will DEXs finally gain widespread adoption?</p><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Liquidity remains a key concern</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Liquidity is arguably the key driver for the adoption and user growth of cryptocurrency exchanges. Liquidity refers to the ease at which an asset is converted into cash without affecting the price of said asset. In a trade order, a&nbsp;<em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">bid</em>&nbsp;refers to an order to buy, and an&nbsp;<em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">ask</em>&nbsp;refers to an order to sell. The spread refers to the difference between the highest bid and lowest ask. A lower spread indicates a more liquid market, while a higher spread indicates a more illiquid market.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">There are two key components to assess liquidity:</p><ol style=\"padding: 0px 20px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: decimal; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Ease, which is the speed and effort required to convert the asset.</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: decimal; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 19px;\">Price slippage, which is the difference between the expected price and execution price on a larger order.</li></ol><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In a liquid market, assets can be easily converted into cash with minimal slippage.&nbsp; Decentralized exchanges can be divided into two types of liquidity models: order book peer-to-peer exchanges and exchanges based on automated market makers.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">An order book peer-to-peer exchange uses a bid/ask system to fulfill trades. The trade is only&nbsp;<a href=\"https://medium.com/@cesar.schneider/defi-ecosystem-liquidity-pools-be9c9d66af6b\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">executed</a>&nbsp;by the exchange’s matching engine when a trader’s buy/sell order is matched by the opposite order at a chosen price. The order book exchange model is optimal for centralized exchanges with high trading volumes, as this indicates high liquidity and leads to a tight spread. Therefore, traders can place large orders with minimal slippage.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">However, the order book exchange model does not work well with DeFi coins and tokens. As most of the decentralized finance protocols are in their early stages, their assets are not actively traded and there are not enough buyers and sellers in the market. The relative illiquidity of the tokens makes them susceptible to price fluctuations caused by large individual transactions. Huge price fluctuations, in turn, lead to a wide spread. Additionally, assets with high price volatility are less likely to be listed by order book exchanges.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Because DeFi tokens are not widely traded in order book exchanges, platforms based on automated market makers serve as an alternative. An AMM-based exchange&nbsp;<a href=\"https://thecontrol.co/a-comparison-of-decentralized-exchange-designs-1deef249f56a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">uses</a>&nbsp;a set of deterministic algorithms that set parameters to pool liquidity from traders and make markets. Instead of using a traditional order book for buy and sell orders, the funds for both buyers and sellers in AMM-based exchanges are stored in on-chain liquidity pools.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In the context of DeFi, AMM systems are designed to create a large liquidity pool that allows for the swapping of assets, as opposed to having set trading pairs. Compared to a traditional order book exchange, traders’ orders do not need to be matched with other traders’ in the liquidity pools. Instead, these pools ensure constant liquidity when traders deposit their assets into it. Additionally, the pricing of tokens in the liquidity pool is determined by an algorithm set in smart contracts, instead of aggregating pricing information across exchanges.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Liquidity pools are beneficial to both the teams behind these DeFi coins and tokens and the assets’ investors. For project teams, liquidity pools&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/decentralized-liquidity-is-the-backbone-of-defi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">remove</a>&nbsp;the needs to bootstrap a liquidity-providing network before the project delivers real utility. For investors, liquidity pools enable them to withdraw coins and tokens when they are not actively traded.&nbsp;</p><h4 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 24px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 29px; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Liquidity mining and yield farming</h4><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.okex.com/academy/en/the-rise-of-compound-hype-driven-bubble-or-indicator-of-defis-strength\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">dramatic rise of Compound</a>&nbsp;has encouraged “yield farming” — the act of using one or multiple DeFi protocols to generate as many returns as possible. Yield farming has become even more popular with the rise of so-called “liquidity mining,” or earning a protocol’s newly minted native token in addition to regular returns.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/defi-yield-farming-comp-token-explained\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">Liquidity mining</a>&nbsp;refers to a situation when a yield farmer participates in market making to contribute needed liquidity to a specific coin or token and, in doing so, earns the rate of return, plus an extra unit of the protocol’s token.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">When Compound distributed its governance token, COMP, its liquidity mining mechanism led to a massive yield farming push as investors attempted to maximize their returns and earn COMP — which will be distributed to users via liquidity mining for the next four years.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The success of Compound has been similarly seen with other DeFi protocols — such as Balancer, a DEX protocol that offers multi-asset pools and allows everyone to become a liquidity provider on the platform. As of late June, there were two sources of income for liquidity providers in Balancer, trading fees and rewards in newly minted BAL — the protocol’s governance token — distributed for liquidity mining.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">BAL is meant to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cryptobriefing.com/project-spotlight-balancer-labs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">serve</a>&nbsp;as the incentive for traders and liquidity providers to participate in the protocol’s governance and decision-making. The recent distribution of BAL provides an extra source of revenue for liquidity providers in Balancer, which drives up the demand to earn BAL. This led to a over 300% increase in total value locked (USD) in Balancer since the start of the token’s distribution on June 23.&nbsp;</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The sustainability of liquidity mining, however, is still up for debate. Bobby Ong, co-founder of crypto analytics firm CoinGecko, told OKEx Insights that things are looking good early on. He explained:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“The liquidity mining model is a form of protocol incentive similar to the proof-of-work block rewards system. The inflationary model is baked into the protocol and the monetary model is known to everyone.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">The sustainability of the liquidity mining model will depend on how much usage the protocol will manage to gather during the incentive period. The idea is that enough users will use the protocols after the incentive is reduced or removed so it becomes a self-sustainable ecosystem where the governance tokens are in demand to vote on governance issues. At this point in time, it will still be too early to say anything — but the early signs are quite positive.”</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The liquidity mining model adopted by certain DEXs has led to a short-term increase in their market shares by trading volume. For example, since Balancer’s announced distribution of its governance token, its market share in trading volume rose from 1.66% to 13.53% during the week of June 22.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Fredrik Haga, co-founder at Dune Analytics, told OKEx Insights that he feels confident that the trading volume of DEXs can keep its positive momentum in July. He explained:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“It seemed in June that the trading volume was driven by yield farming to a large extent. However, about 1/4 of July has passed and we\'ve seen ~$420M traded in DEXs. If that trend continues, July will land at about the same volume as June (~$1.5B traded).”</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">While total trading volumes on DEXs in July have already surpassed those of last year, looking ahead to Q3 2020, Haga highlighted a few DEXs to keep an eye on:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“From the reference of Balancer and Curve, it\'s getting obvious that automated market makers can drive volume pretty quickly. Now it is going to be interesting to see how new models like the Gnosis Protocol — which launched in May — perform and if they are able to attract liquidity. In addition, with rising gas prices, layer 2 solutions like Loopring and Diversifi are going to be interesting to follow.”</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/fed1da6da79ca8f0cba2aa0c88e14d9e5f2181ef7be92.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"447\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p></blockquote><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">DEXs still have a long way to go to mass adoption</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Despite the surging volumes on decentralized exchanges in June, it is still too early for DEXs to be compared to centralized crypto exchanges —&nbsp;which very much boast the lion’s share of users and trading volumes. As indicated by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://image.tokeninsight.com/upload/levelPdf/2020-Q1-Cryptocurrency-Spot-Exchange-Industry-Report.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">research</a>&nbsp;from TokenInsight, as of Q1 2020, trading volume on DEXs only accounted for 2.68% of total spot trading across the whole crypto market.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In terms of USD, trading volumes on DEXs reached $180 billion USD in Q1 2020 — compared to the $6.6 trillion traded across the entire crypto spot market. Though the proportion is still small, this was actually the first time that DEX volumes made up more than&nbsp; 0.01% of total spot volume, TokenInsight reports.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Security concerns also remain an obstacle for the widespread adoption of decentralized exchanges, as reflected by the recent $500,000 exploit of Balancer. On June 29, CoinDesk&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/hacker-drains-defi-liquidity-balancer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">reported</a>&nbsp;that an attacker had exploited a loophole in the protocol by borrowing $23 million worth of WETH tokens. They reportedly then continuously traded WETH against Statera (STA) with increasing quantities — draining the liquidity pool of STA. The identity of the hacker remains a mystery and the Statera team announced that they are not able to refund the victims of the hack.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Jay Zhou, chief operating officer of DEX protocol Loopring, told OKEx Insights that the limitation of Ethereum throughputs also sheds light on the security issues that DEXs face. He explained:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“My concern is the technology limitation regarding the throughputs of Ethereum. The ‘black swan’ event on March 12 has evaporated the value of the DeFi market by 50% in a single day. This means the current blockchain cannot support the needs of DeFi users if the price changes dramatically in a short period of time. While some of the leading DeFi protocols like MakerDAO and dYdX are using layer-1 scaling solutions on blockchain, we will see more and more dapps adopting layer-2 scaling solutions in the coming year.”</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Poor user interfaces on decentralized exchanges, compared to popular centralized exchanges, are also hampering user adoption. CoinGecko’s Ong told OKEx Insights that the complexity of using DEXs hinders the user experience and, thus, remains an obstacle preventing DeFi from going mainstream. He elaborated:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“It is hard for anyone to understand the concept of how to make high yields available. It is hard to explain the concept of automated market makers, liquidity pools, etc. to anyone, even to participants in the crypto industry. For a person with average crypto knowledge to use these, they have to be familiar with Metamask, get ahold of ETH and/or stablecoins&nbsp; — not to mention the various stablecoins available, like DAI, USDT, USDC, etc. — or use a dashboard like Instadapp to perform yield farming properly.”&nbsp;</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ong also pointed out that, at the moment — with high fees on Ethereum among other considerations — for yield farming on DeFi protocols to be effective, it requires users to put down a large sum of money to start, “a minimum of $10,000 to see some real profits.” He added:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“What this means is that DeFi yield farming is now essentially a game played by large whales who are willing to take on the risk of smart contracts to get high yield.”</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Apart from the above stated obstacles, Jon Jordan, director of communications at decentralized application data company DappRadar, shared with OKEx Insights his belief that the inertia of using centralized exchanges makes DEXs “far from mainstream.” He explained:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“I think the main reason DEXs haven\'t become mainstream is the historical issue that when crypto first boomed, the only way to access these new assets was using centralized exchanges. Once someone has signed up and started getting comfortable using such a product, it\'s very hard to get them to switch to anything else.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">More specifically, however, the problem with DEXs has always been (and continues to be) that they are slower, more expensive to use and offer less liquidity than the top centralized exchanges. This is coupled with plenty of security issues. For these reasons, I don\'t see DEXs becoming mainstream products.”</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">While Jordan believes that DEXs are not going mainstream in the short term, he does think that they offer two clear advantages for users:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“The first advantage of DEX is no KYC/AML restrictions, which is important to some users. The main advantage is what we\'re currently experiencing, which is the way DEXs are being integrated into the wider DeFi explosion. This has seen the rise of products such as Uniswap, Kyber, 1inch, Curve etc, which can be accessed in novel ways as part of a complex DeFi transaction, which may involve multiple actions.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">Another advantage offered by DEX is the phenomenon of yield farming. Users are maximizing their ability to farm Compound\'s new COMP token by depositing collateral, taking out loans and exchanging tokens simultaneously. This is resulting in an enormous explosion in DeFi and DEX volumes, although the number of users remains very low compared to centralized exchanges.”</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In his conversation with OKEx Insights, DappRadar’s Jordan also noted his belief that DEXs will be fully integrated into the DeFi ecosystem:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“I expect that we\'ll see a transformation of DEXs as they become fully integrated with the DeFi ecosystem. And at some point we\'ll probably stop even talking about DEXs as a separate product type.”</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">While decentralized exchanges —&nbsp;and DeFi as a whole — are still in their early stages and effectively remain available to a limited user base, CoinGecko’s Ong believes that DeFi still presents enormous opportunities to democratize financial services to everyone:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">“I am generally optimistic of the future of DeFi. This is the beginning of a multi-decade growth trajectory and DeFi promises us a lot of potential in decentralizing financial services.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5;\">Although there are many problems mentioned above, over time, as Ethereum scales and DeFi developers get more sophisticated, these things will improve and the user experience will become much better such that anyone can participate in it. When that happens, complex financial services with higher returns on investment will be democratised to everyone and not just restricted to the rich.”</p></blockquote>', 'DEXs Ride the DeFi Wave: Liquidity, Security and the Road to Mass Adoption');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (172, 84, 'zh-CN', '简单易实操的币市绝对收益策略——中低频网格套利', '<p class=\"has-custom-size\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 17px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/fed1da6da79ca8f0cba2aa0c88e14d9e5f21828c2a13b.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"447\" alt=\"\">套利交易简介</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">套利交易，又叫对冲交易，遵循“市场中性”原则，即同时进行两笔行情相关、方向相反、数量相当、盈亏相抵的交易。最常见的套利交易发生在满足条件一对标的上，交易时，买入认为被低估的标的，同时卖出被高估的标的，当差价恢复时，平仓出场。本质上，套利交易是交易者选择两个标的，构建投资组合，并以组合内两个标的的差价，作为交易对象，如投资者认为价差较低时，买入/开多价差，价差上涨后平仓获利。投资者关心的是组合内标价格的相互关系，而不是其绝对价格水平，通过其差价的波动来获利，同时避免了价格直接波动的影响。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">套利交易的基本方法</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当我们选择A,B两个产品组成交易对时，我们定义组合的差价 diff = price_A - price_B。当认为diff处于低位时，我们开多diff，diff上涨到合适位置平仓。开多diff，即开多A，同时开空B；平多，即平多A，同时平多B。开空平空同理。下面我们具体举例说明。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如我们选择stai的BTC永续合约和BTC季度合约分别作为A和B，diff = 永续价格 - 季度价格。永续和季度合约各1个BTC保证金。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">操作：</span></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/02/27171.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7669\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">盈亏情况：</span></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/02/27172.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7671\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\"><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">经过上述开仓平仓操作，我们利用50USD的差价变化，赚取了价值约50USD的BTC。抽象来说，即我们在diff = -100USD/BTC时开多1BTC，在diff = -50USD/BTC时平仓，差价上涨了50USD/BTC，共通过做多差价赚取了diff上涨的50USD利润。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">标的选择</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">套利交易资产组合选择的首要因素是，两交易对价格的强相关性，如我们可以选择OKEx不同期的合约，合约与现货，或OKEx合约与OKCoin现货等。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">另外需要考虑差价的波动范围和平台手续费，一次完整的开仓和平仓，需要进行4笔交易，差价的波动需要足够大以保证足够大的利润空间。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">还有，我们需要观察差价的波动周期，确保交割周期内，差价客户收敛，避免因为在差价回归之前交割，造成亏损。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根据这些要求，OKEx的BTC永续合约和BTC季度合约是一个很好的套利组合。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">网格交易法</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">所谓网格交易法（grid trading method），也称鱼网交易网，秉持的原则是“仓位策略比择时策略更重要 \" 。其基本操作方式就是以某点为基点，每上涨或下跌一定点数挂一定数量空单或多单，设定盈利目标，但不设止损，当价格朝期望方向进展时获利平仓，并在原点位挂同样的买单或卖单。这样布下的这些交易单形成了一张像鱼网样的阵列，在震荡的市场中来回获利。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"><br>中低频网格套利策略</span>从上面简单的原理描述中我们不难看出，网格交易法盈利的核心是“均值回归”，在震荡行情中，网格策略会有非常好的表现。而套利交易目标交易对的差价，天然具有“必然回归”的属性，比如交割合约的价格最终必然回归于现货，永续合约与交割合约的价格同样“必然回归”。因此，网格交易法天然适合用于币市的套利。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们以OKEx BTC永续合约和BTC季度合约为例，我们定义diff = 永续价格 - 季度价格，下图为diff在2019.7.27-2019.8.27一个月的波动情况，可以看出，diff从+1%左右至-3%左右区间中震荡，中间几次穿过0轴。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"><br>网格的设置和执行：</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">因为差价存在必然回归到0值的基本假设，因此，差价小于0时，我们执行做多网格，差价大于0时，我们执行做空网格。且基于差价归0假设，开仓后，我们不必做止损，等待价格回归平仓即可。随着价格下跌，每跌至一个格子的价格，我们开一份多仓。随着价格的下跌，我们依次开了买1，买2，买3三份多仓（即在图中买1买2买3三个位置，分别在永续合约开多约30张，并在季度合约开等量空仓）；然后随着价格的回升，我们依次平掉买3，买2，买1三部分仓位（即在图中平买1平买2平买3三个位置，分别平掉永续约所开的30张多仓，并同时平掉季度合约当时所开张数空仓），获利为三个格子的仓位*一个格子差价对应的利润。做空网格同理。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">风险分析</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">理论上，在中低频范畴内使用网格策略进行套利交易属于一种绝对收益模型，中长期看来，可以保证本金完全无风险。但实际操作中，我们仍然需要考虑所选标的特点等实际问题带来的潜在风险。<img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/fed1da6da79ca8f0cba2aa0c88e14d9e5f2182733769c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"447\" alt=\"\"></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">单边爆仓风险</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">套利交易每笔操作正常为对冲操作，持有等量多空仓位对冲价格波动，但仍可能出现由于价格巨幅波动造成的一边仓位爆仓，爆仓后，另一边持仓失去对冲的保护，会造成策略不可控的价格波动带来的巨大风险。因此，首先要控制总杠杆倍数为相对低的程度，另外，一方亏损较大时，即使划转保证金保护其仓位安全。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">手续费和资金费率</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由于套利交易是通过差价波动来盈利，因此单笔盈利较薄，我们通过中低频操作，较大的格子，来保证每笔盈利足以覆盖交易手续费和永续合约资金费率可能带来的损失。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">合约交割问题</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">另外，合约交割时，可能出现差价不回归的问题，因此临近合约交割，我们只平仓不开仓，交割前，主动平掉两边所有仓位。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">总结</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">总的来说，网格套利整体风险极低，逻辑简单明了，可以做到无视币价涨跌稳定盈利。同时，选择中低频大网格操作，相对高频而言，手续费不敏感，对没有程序化实现能力的朋友，手动操作亦可执行。</p>', '简单易实操的币市绝对收益策略——中低频网格套利');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (173, 84, 'zh-TW', '簡單易實操的幣市絕對收益策略——中低頻網格套利', '<p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/fed1da6da79ca8f0cba2aa0c88e14d9e5f2182c6226b3.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"447\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p class=\"has-custom-size\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">套利交易簡介</span></font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\"></span></font></p><p class=\"has-custom-size\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">套利交易，又叫對沖交易，遵循“市場中性”原則，即同時進行兩筆行情相關、方向相反、數量相當、盈虧相抵的交易。最常見的套利交易發生在滿足條件一對標的上，交易時，買入認為被低估的標的，同時賣出被高估的標的，當差價恢復時，平倉出場。本質上，套利交易是交易者選擇兩個標的，構建投資組合，並以組合內兩個標的的差價，作為交易對象，如投資者認為價差較低時，買入/開多價差，價差上漲後平倉獲利。投資者關心的是組合內標價格的相互關係，而不是其絕對價格水平，通過其差價的波動來獲利，同時避免了價格直接波動的影響。</span></font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\"></span></font></p><p class=\"has-custom-size\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">套利交易的基本方法</span></font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\"></span></font></p><p class=\"has-custom-size\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">當我們選擇A,B兩個產品組成交易對時，我們定義組合的差價 diff = price_A - price_B。當認為diff處於低位時，我們開多diff，diff上漲到合適位置平倉。開多diff，即開多A，同時開空B；平多，即平多A，同時平多B。開空平空同理。下面我們具體舉例說明。</span></font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\"></span></font></p><p class=\"has-custom-size\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">如我們選擇</span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 86, 105); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">STAI</span><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">的BTC永續合約和BTC季度合約分別作為A和B，diff = 永續價格 - 季度價格。永續和季度合約各1個BTC保證金。</span></font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\"></span></font></p><p class=\"has-custom-size\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">操作：</span></font><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/02/27171.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7669\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">盈亏情况：</span></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://static.bafang.com/cdn/assets/academy/2020/02/27172.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_85/format,webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7671\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\"><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">經過上述開倉平倉操作，我們利用50USD的差價變化，賺取了價值約50USD的BTC。抽象來說，即我們在diff = -100USD/BTC時開多1BTC，在diff = -50USD/BTC時平倉，差價上漲了50USD/BTC，共通過做多差價賺取了diff上漲的50USD利潤。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">標的選擇</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">套利交易資產組合選擇的首要因素是，兩交易對價格的強相關性，如我們可以選擇</font><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 86, 105); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">STAI</span><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">不同期的合約，合約與現貨，或</font><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 86, 105); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">STAI</span><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">合約與OKCoin現貨等。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">另外需要考慮差價的波動範圍和平台手續費，一次完整的開倉和平倉，需要進行4筆交易，差價的波動需要足夠大以保證足夠大的利潤空間。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">還有，我們需要觀察差價的波動週期，確保交割週期內，差價客戶收斂，避免因為在差價回歸之前交割，造成虧損。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">根據這些要求，</font><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 86, 105); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">STAI</span><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">的BTC永續合約和BTC季度合約是一個很好的套利組合。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">網格交易法</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">所謂網格交易法（grid trading method），也稱魚網交易網，秉持的原則是“倉位策略比擇時策略更重要 \" 。其基本操作方式就是以某點為基點，每上漲或下跌一定點數掛一定數量空單或多單，設定盈利目標，但不設止損，當價格朝期望方向進展時獲利平倉，並在原點位掛同樣的買單或賣單。這樣布下的這些交易單形成了一張像魚網樣的陣列，在震蕩的市場中來回獲利。</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-e10f0e9d68ea70af224b1352b146b8ef_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">從上面簡單的原理描述中我們不難看出，網格交易法盈利的核心是“均值回歸”，在震盪行情中，網格策略會有非常好的表現。而套利交易目標交易對的差價，天然具有“必然回歸”的屬性，比如交割合約的價格最終必然回歸於現貨，永續合約與交割合約的價格同樣“必然回歸”。因此，網格交易法天然適合用於幣市的套利。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">中低頻網格套利策略</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">我們以</font><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 86, 105); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">STAI </span><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">&nbsp;BTC永續合約和BTC季度合約為例，我們定義diff = 永續價格- 季度價格，下圖為diff在2019.7.27-2019.8.27一個月的波動情況，可以看出，diff從+ 1%左右至-3%左右區間中震盪，中間幾次穿過0軸。</font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">網格的設置和執行：</span></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-84962a7deae68f5154207d4c19d16cd4_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以做多网格为例：</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-1381fed0367aa3255656f0942b44940b_hd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">隨著價格下跌，每跌至一個格子的價格，我們開一份多倉。隨著價格的下跌，我們依次開了買1，買2，買3三份多倉（即在圖中買1買2買3三個位置，分別在永續合約開多約30張，並在季度合約開等量空倉）；然後隨著價格的回升，我們依次平掉買3，買2，買1三部分倉位（即在圖中平買1平買2平買3三個位置，分別平掉永續約所開的30張多倉，並同時平掉季度合約當時所開張數空倉），獲利為三個格子的倉位*一個格子差價對應的利潤。做空網格同理。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">因為差價存在必然回歸到0值的基本假設，因此，差價小於0時，我們執行做多網格，差價大於0時，我們執行做空網格。且基於差價歸0假設，開倉後，我們不必做止損，等待價格回歸平倉即可。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">風險分析</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">理論上，在中低頻範疇內使用網格策略進行套利交易屬於一種絕對收益模型，中長期看來，可以保證本金完全無風險。但實際操作中，我們仍然需要考慮所選標的特點等實際問題帶來的潛在風險。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">單邊爆倉風險</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">套利交易每筆操作正常為對沖操作，持有等量多空倉位對沖價格波動，但仍可能出現由於價格巨幅波動造成的一邊倉位爆倉，爆倉後，另一邊持倉失去對沖的保護，會造成策略不可控的價格波動帶來的巨大風險。因此，首先要控制總槓桿倍數為相對低的程度，另外，一方虧損較大時，即使劃轉保證金保護其倉位安全。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">手續費和資金費率</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">由於套利交易是通過差價波動來盈利，因此單筆盈利較薄，我們通過中低頻操作，較大的格子，來保證每筆盈利足以覆蓋交易手續費和永續合約資金費率可能帶來的損失。</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">合約交割問題</font><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#4f5669\" face=\"SF Pro Text, SF Pro Icons, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">另外，合約交割時，可能出現差價不回歸的問題，因此臨近合約交割，我們只平倉不開倉，交割前，主動平掉兩邊所有倉位。</font></p>', '簡單易實操的幣市絕對收益策略——中低頻網格套利');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (174, 85, 'en', 'Bitcoin Back Above $11K as USDT Flows Continue and Futures Basis Surges — Crypto Market Daily', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">After a brief pullback, Bitcoin (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/index/btc-usd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">BTC</a>) saw a further appreciation in the last 24 hours, going up 1.12% to trade around $11,030, as per the STAI BTC Index price. The overall trend in Bitcoin remains strong, generally buoying the market and helping large-cap coins make important breakthroughs.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bitcoin Cash (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/index/bch-usd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">BCH</a>), for instance, surpassed its previous high of $280 and continued to move up quickly to its current level near $293, rising 7.54% in the last 24 hours. The BCH/BTC pair also reached two-month highs of 0.0269 last night. This breakout may attract more traders to join and thus keep the rally going. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/index/eos-usd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">EOS</a> and XRP, on the other hand, respectively surged 10.73% and 8.17%, and both have reached new highs since April 29. Ether (ETH), which broke out recently to cross the $300 level, currently stands at $321 — up a relatively modest 1.57% in the last 24 hours.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The rise in large-caps also drove up the total cryptocurrency market capitalization by 1.5% to $331 billion, while Bitcoin\'s dominance fell by 0.2% and is now at 61.4%, according to data from <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.coingecko.com/en\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">CoinGecko</a>. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Meanwhile, stock markets retreated on Tuesday, with the Nasdaq Composite Index down 1.27% and the S&P 500 down 0.65%. Gold futures prices rose for the second day in a row, however, hitting another record close and intraday high. Moreover, the Federal Reserve has been holding a two-day meeting that started Tuesday, with the results of the meeting to be announced on Wednesday.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21864c67e26.jpg\" alt=\"OKEx Token Index Board as of 8:00 am UTC on 7/29/20. Source: OKEx\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21864c67e26.jpg\"><br><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 86, 105); font-size: 16px; text-align: start;\">STAI</span> Token Index Board as of 8:00 am UTC on 7/29/20. Source: </em><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 86, 105); font-size: 16px; text-align: start;\">STAI</span></figcaption></figure><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A hint of risk in a lot of good numbers</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The amount of USDT flowing into exchanges recently spiked to a yearly high, according to on-chain data provider <a href=\"https://twitter.com/glassnode/status/1287805348389232640\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">Glassnode</a>, and Tether <a href=\"https://news.huoxing24.com/flash/20200729163235244589.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\">issued</a> another $300 million USDT around an hour ago today. This USDT issuance hints at increasing market demand and could potentially support further Bitcoin price appreciation.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21866271526.jpg\" alt=\"USDT Exchange Inflow. Source: Glassnode\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21866271526.jpg\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">USDT Exchange Inflow. Source: </em><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://twitter.com/glassnode/status/1287805348389232640\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">Glassnode</em></a></figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Looking at futures data, STAI one-month futures annualized basis surged to as high as 25.67% yesterday, its highest level since late February, as per data by skew. Values above 20% indicate that traders are paying a very high premium on spots and using high leverage. </p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f2186794fe6a.jpg\" alt=\"BTC Futures Annualized Rolling 1-Month Basis. Source: skew\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f2186794fe6a.jpg\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">BTC Futures Annualized Rolling 1-Month Basis. Source: </em><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://analytics.skew.com/dashboard/okex\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">skew</em></a></figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">At the same time, we note that funding rates for perpetual swaps have been at high levels since Monday. With most traders in profit due to the price increase, the higher funding rates can still be maintained for some time. However, highly leveraged traders may find it difficult to maintain their current positions for prolonged periods.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21868e1722a.jpg\" alt=\"Funding Rates. Data Collection Time: 7/27 0:00 am UTC to 7/29 8:00 am UTC\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21868e1722a.jpg\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">Funding Rates. Data Collection Time: 7/27 0:00 am UTC to 7/29 8:00 am UTC</em></figcaption></figure>', 'Bitcoin Back Above $11K as USDT Flows Continue and Futures Basis Surges — Crypto Market Daily');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (175, 85, 'zh-CN', '零基础学习币市分析| 4 看跌K线组合', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">涨跌有趋势，读懂价格语言；</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">买卖有信号，告别感觉交易。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">本节我们继续学习K线的组合应用——看跌组合。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">夕阳无限好，已是近黄昏。黄昏之星的出现，预示币价上涨行情告一段落，调整即将来临。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">什么样的K线组合是黄昏之星呢？如图红色画线处所示。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">标准的黄昏之星由三根K线组合而成，首先是一根较大的阳线，随后紧跟一根类似“十字”的星线，第三根K线是一根较大的阴线。黄昏之星是否成立，对第三根阴线的长度有着明确的要求，它的收盘价格一定要低于第一根阳线实体的50%。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">在确定黄昏之星有效以后，我们可以通过最后一根阴线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看跌力度强弱。如图，阴线收盘价格刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下的看跌力度比较弱。若后阴线收盘价格与前阳线开盘价格持平，则认为看跌力度较强。若后阴线收盘价格明显低于前阳线开盘价格，则认为看跌力度相当强劲。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">刚刚所讲是最标准的黄昏之星组合，但在实际走势中，黄昏之星会有一些变化。那么市场中真实的黄昏之星是怎样的呢？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">例如图示三种黄昏之星的样子，图一，中间由两根小K线组成。我们将它还原到实际走势图中。币价在大涨之后的高位区出现黄昏之星，后市币价出现大幅调整。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图二，中间K线并不是标准的十字星线，而是带有长上影线的小K线。截图来自STAI&nbsp;，BTC/USD 2小时图表，在高位出现黄昏之星后，币价滞涨回落</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图三，中间出现两根十字星，阴线力度明显大于阳线。币价在大涨后出现看跌力度强劲的黄昏之星，在高位震荡后最终出现大跌。有些时候黄昏之星会连续出现两个，甚至更多。BTC/USDT这段下跌走势途中，相隔不远的两个反弹高位都出现了黄昏之星，币价随后继续下跌。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">接下来我们学习第二种看跌K线组合--看跌吞没。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">首先，看一下看跌吞没的特征。后一根阴线实体，完全覆盖前一根阳线实体，如同阳线被阴线吞噬掉一般。说明空头力量正在大举反攻。因此得名看跌吞没。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">那么如何判断看跌力度呢？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图一，下跌阴线实体刚刚将阳线实体吞没，该种情况看跌力度较弱；图二，阴线实体收盘价明显低于阳线开盘价，阴线长度甚至达到阳线的两倍，该种情况看跌力度很强；图三，阴线实体一举将多根阳线吞没，该种情况看跌力度非常强劲。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">在市场中存在很多非标准的看跌吞没组合，那实际的看跌吞没组合是怎样的呢？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">例如图示的三种看跌吞没组合的变体。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图一，截图来自STAI&nbsp; LTC/USDT 日线图，币价大幅上涨后出现了一阴吞多阳的强劲看跌吞没组合后，币价出现连续下跌。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图二，截图来自STAI&nbsp; ETH/USDT&nbsp; 2小时图，在下跌行情的反弹高点，出现看跌吞没组合，币价结束反弹继续下行。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图三，截图来自STAI&nbsp; EOS/USDT&nbsp; 6小时图，币价在连续大涨后，出现看跌吞没组合，随后展开大幅下跌。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">第三种看跌K线组合：塔形顶</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">塔形顶，左边是一根中阳线或大阳线；中间由若干根小k线组成，通常在5根以上；右边是一根中阴线或大阴线。整体看上去就像一座宝塔，因此得名塔形顶。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">一个有效的塔形顶要满足：最后一根阴线的收盘价要低于前面大阴线实体的50%以下；塔形顶所展现的是：市场中做多力量逐步衰竭，多空达成平衡，最后到下跌力度增强的过程。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">在确定塔形顶有效后，我们可以通过最后一根阴线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看跌力度的强弱。如图，若阴线收盘价刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下看跌力度相对比较弱；若后阴线收盘价基本与前阳线开盘价持平，则认为看跌力度较强；若后阴线收盘价明显低于前阳线开盘价，则看跌力度相当强劲。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">当然，在实际走势中塔形顶并不像我们示意图中展示的这么完美。要活学活用。我们看一下市场实际中的塔形顶是怎样的。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">变化一，中间多根小K线带有长影线。截图来自STAI&nbsp; BTC/USDT&nbsp; 6小时图，在大幅度上涨后出现塔形顶组合，之后币价连续下跌，并跌穿前期低点。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">变化二，塔形顶中间部分并不都是非常小的K线构成，K线震荡幅度较大。截图来自STAI币币交易区AAC/USDT&nbsp; 12小时K线图，币价在一段反弹行情中出现塔形顶，随后继续大幅下跌。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">最后我们回顾一下本期内容：</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">三种典型的看跌组合。第一种，黄昏之星，预示黑暗即将降临；第二种，看跌吞没，空头力挽狂澜；第三种，塔形顶，多头逐步缴械投降。</p>', '零基础学习币市分析| 4 看跌K线组合');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (176, 85, 'zh-TW', '零基礎學習幣市分析| 4 看跌K線組合', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">涨跌有趋势，读懂价格语言；</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">买卖有信号，告别感觉交易。<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本节我们继续学习K线的组合应用——看跌组合。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">夕阳无限好，已是近黄昏。黄昏之星的出现，预示币价上涨行情告一段落，调整即将来临。<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">什么样的K线组合是黄昏之星呢？如图红色画线处所示。<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">标准的黄昏之星由三根K线组合而成，首先是一根较大的阳线，随后紧跟一根类似“十字”的星线，第三根K线是一根较大的阴线。黄昏之星是否成立，对第三根阴线的长度有着明确的要求，它的收盘价格一定要低于第一根阳线实体的50%。<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在确定黄昏之星有效以后，我们可以通过最后一根阴线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看跌力度强弱。如图，阴线收盘价格刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下的看跌力度比较弱。若后阴线收盘价格与前阳线开盘价格持平，则认为看跌力度较强。若后阴线收盘价格明显低于前阳线开盘价格，则认为看跌力度相当强劲。<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">刚刚所讲是最标准的黄昏之星组合，但在实际走势中，黄昏之星会有一些变化。那么市场中真实的黄昏之星是怎样的呢？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">例如图示三种黄昏之星的样子，图一，中间由两根小K线组成。我们将它还原到实际走势图中。币价在大涨之后的高位区出现黄昏之星，后市币价出现大幅调整。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">图二，中间K线并不是标准的十字星线，而是带有长上影线的小K线。在高位出现黄昏之星后，币价滞涨回落</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">图三，中间出现两根十字星，阴线力度明显大于阳线。币价在大涨后出现看跌力度强劲的黄昏之星，在高位震荡后最终出现大跌。有些时候黄昏之星会连续出现两个，甚至更多。BTC/USDT这段下跌走势途中，相隔不远的两个反弹高位都出现了黄昏之星，币价随后继续下跌。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">接下来我们学习第二种看跌K线组合--看跌吞没。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">首先，看一下看跌吞没的特征。后一根阴线实体，完全覆盖前一根阳线实体，如同阳线被阴线吞噬掉一般。说明空头力量正在大举反攻。因此得名看跌吞没。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">那么如何判断看跌力度呢？<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">图一，下跌阴线实体刚刚将阳线实体吞没，该种情况看跌力度较弱；图二，阴线实体收盘价明显低于阳线开盘价，阴线长度甚至达到阳线的两倍，该种情况看跌力度很强；图三，阴线实体一举将多根阳线吞没，该种情况看跌力度非常强劲。<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在市场中存在很多非标准的看跌吞没组合，那实际的看跌吞没组合是怎样的呢？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">例如三种看跌吞没组合的变体。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一，币价大幅上涨后出现了一阴吞多阳的强劲看跌吞没组合后，币价出现连续下跌。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">二，在下跌行情的反弹高点，出现看跌吞没组合，币价结束反弹继续下行。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">三，币价在连续大涨后，出现看跌吞没组合，随后展开大幅下跌。<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第三种看跌K线组合：塔形顶</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">塔形顶，左边是一根中阳线或大阳线；中间由若干根小k线组成，通常在5根以上；右边是一根中阴线或大阴线。整体看上去就像一座宝塔，因此得名塔形顶。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一个有效的塔形顶要满足：最后一根阴线的收盘价要低于前面大阴线实体的50%以下；塔形顶所展现的是：市场中做多力量逐步衰竭，多空达成平衡，最后到下跌力度增强的过程。<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;\"></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在确定塔形顶有效后，我们可以通过最后一根阴线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看跌力度的强弱。如图，若阴线收盘价刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下看跌力度相对比较弱；若后阴线收盘价基本与前阳线开盘价持平，则认为看跌力度较强；若后阴线收盘价明显低于前阳线开盘价，则看跌力度相当强劲。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当然，在实际走势中塔形顶并不像我们示意图中展示的这么完美。要活学活用。我们看一下市场实际中的塔形顶是怎样的。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">变化一，中间多根小K线带有长影线。在大幅度上涨后出现塔形顶组合，之后币价连续下跌，并跌穿前期低点。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">变化二，塔形顶中间部分并不都是非常小的K线构成，K线震荡幅度较大。币价在一段反弹行情中出现塔形顶，随后继续大幅下跌。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最后我们回顾一下本期内容：</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"SF Pro Text\", \"SF Pro Icons\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">三种典型的看跌组合。第一种，黄昏之星，预示黑暗即将降临；第二种，看跌吞没，空头力挽狂澜；第三种，塔形顶，多头逐步缴械投降。</p>', '零基礎學習幣市分析| 4 看跌K線組合');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (177, 86, 'en', 'Bitcoin Crosses $10K and ETH Posts 13-Month High Amid Crypto Market Rally — Market Watch Weekly', '<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b5f21888f9f5fe.jpg\" alt=\"Crypto Market Weekly\" class=\"wp-image-50468\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 450px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 450px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b5f21888f9f5fe.jpg\"></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><font color=\"#4f5669\">After a relatively long consolidation period, Bitcoin (BTC) finally opted for an upward breakout and spiked to $10,200 on Sunday, closing the week with gains of over 9.50%. Meanwhile, ether (ETH) set a 13-month high of $320, surging 31.56% last week, as per the STAI Spot Price.&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#4f5669\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><font color=\"#4f5669\">The usual large-capitalization cryptocurrencies also have risen in the last seven days, with Litecoin (LTC) and Bitcoin SV (BSV) surging 13.63% and 11.31%, respectively.&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#4f5669\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><font color=\"#4f5669\">DeFi tokens, however, retreated last week, with Chainlink (LINK) losing 8.26% and Kyber Network (KNC) plunging 13%. Previous high performers lost 20% or more, such as Synthetix (SNX) and Compound (COMP).</font><font color=\"#4f5669\"></font></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><font color=\"#4f5669\">It\'s also important to note that DeFi tokens fell sharply during ETH’s minor pullback after it hit $320 on Sunday, which shows a shift in the market trend.</font></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f21887ad6b8c.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 450px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 450px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f21887ad6b8c.jpg\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">Weekly returns of major cryptocurrencies 7/20–7/26. Source: TradingView</em></figcaption></figure><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\">Rapid rise in open interest</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">Bitcoin’s open interest in the STAI derivatives market has returned to above $1 billion, adding nearly 30% in the last seven days. Meanwhile, with the price of ETH setting a new high this year, ether’s OI has also reached an all-time high, jumping from last Monday’s $196 million to the current $290 million. The open interest on ETH options also rose on STAI, crossing $21 million — up 5x in the last month.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">The spike in open positions signals an increased probability of volatility returning to the market.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f218869718a9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 450px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 450px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f218869718a9.jpg\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\"></figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><font color=\"#4f5669\">Bitcoin’s short-term seven-day volatility (BVOL7D) finally picked up last week, rising to its current 4.43% from Tuesday’s 2.39%. But volatility remains low on a macro scale, as its 60-day volatility is down to 1.81%, the lowest level since November 2018.&nbsp;</font><br></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f218851662ef.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 450px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 450px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f218851662ef.jpg\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">Bitcoin’s 7D volatility (BVOL7D). Source: TradingView</em></figcaption></figure><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\">Technical analysis</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">On the daily chart, Bitcoin has been breaching its 2.5-year-long bearish trendline formed between December 2017 and June 2019 highs, as the price spiked above $10,000.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">However, traders have to wait to see if it’s a fake breakout, since the Tom Demark Sequential indicator just printed a sell “9” signal on the daily chart, along with a sell “13” signal on the two-day chart. Similar TD Sequential signals can be seen on the ETH charts as well.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">That being said, Bitcoin is still expected to continue to rise as long as it doesn\'t fall below the $9,800 support level. On the upside, traders should pay special attention to the resistance at $10,500.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">From a macro perspective, the gold price has already hit an all-time high this Monday, and the flood of liquidity has kept asset prices high across the market.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f21883ea4d78.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 450px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 450px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f21883ea4d78.jpg\"></figure><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\">Looking ahead this week&nbsp;</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">The market is expected to focus on whether the U.S. Congress can successfully pass a new trillion-dollar economic stimulus, which will affect the subsequent trend of financial assets. In addition, the U.S. Federal Reserve\'s next meeting will also be held on Wednesday of this week. The market believes the Fed will keep rates unchanged, but comments on the future direction of the economy from Fed Chairman Jerome Powell at the press conference will come under the spotlight.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">In the crypto space, Cardano is scheduled to finish its Shelley hard fork on July 29, and popular decentralized prediction market platform Augur is going to launch its version 2.0 soon.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">On the STAI exchange, in-demand DeFi tokens Balancer (bal) and Synthetix (SNX) have been made available for spot trading.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><br></p><hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: #1f2236;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: #1f2236;\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><br></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">Disclaimer: This material should not be taken as the basis for making investment decisions, nor be construed as a recommendation to engage in investment transactions. Trading digital assets involve significant risk and can result in the loss of your invested capital. You should ensure that you fully understand the risk involved and take into consideration your level of experience, investment objectives and seek independent financial advice if necessary.</em></p>', 'Bitcoin Crosses $10K and ETH Posts 13-Month High Amid Crypto Market Rally — Market Watch Weekly');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (178, 86, 'zh-CN', '零基础学币市分析|1 从价格到K线', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f218eb1e72d3.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"478\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f218eb1e72d3.jpg\"></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">涨跌有趋势，读懂价格语言；</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">买卖有信号，告别感觉交易。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">今天我们一起学习，技术分析中最基础的元素——K线。K线是当今最为普遍的价格标记法。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">先来看一下，一天中价格在市场中是如何运行的。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">在没有经过K线标记法处理时，某投资品的价格是这样的，无数的价格连在一起形成一条看起来毫无规律的曲线图。看起来有些乱是不是？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">下面，我们做一下简单的技术分析处理，标记一下其中重要的数据，</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">开盘价、收盘价、最高价、最低价。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">我们过滤掉其中繁乱的价格变化，将其绘制成折线图。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">如图所示，这样看起来是不是清晰很多？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">可不可以，用更简单的表示它呢？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">当然可以，K线图了解一下。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">如图这样处理，将开盘价、收盘价、最低价、最高价，平移到一条垂直线上。开盘价与收盘价之间构成K线实体，我们用较粗线条表示，实体到最高价和最低价之间我们用细线条表示，分别构成上影线和下影线。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">表示该时段价格下跌，通常称为阴线。收盘价高于开盘价的，我们用绿色标记实体，表示该时段价格上涨，通常称之为阳线。（当然部分市场会使用相反颜色标记K线涨跌。）</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">当我们把每一天的K线连在一起，就会出现我们常见的K线图样子。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图中每一根红色或绿色的K线都代表一天的价格变化数据。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">一天的价格走势可以用一根K线表示，那么一分钟、一个小时、一星期呢？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">根据统计价格变化的时间范围的不同，我们将K线分为不同的周期。这是多条一分钟K线连在一起的样子，这是多条“周K线”连在一起的样子。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">周期的划分非常灵活多样，几分钟、几小时、几天、几周或是几个月都可以。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">K线，在投资市场分析中有什么作用？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">特定的K线形态或特定的K线组合出现后，大概率会发生特定的价格走势。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">因为价格包含一切市场行为，历史会惊人的相似。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">后续我们再来分享，通过观察K线规律性排列，预判未来价格涨跌的方法。</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (179, 86, 'zh-TW', '零基礎學幣市分析|1 從價格到K線', '<p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f21893674d38.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b7235f21893674d38.jpg\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" data-mce-style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">漲跌有趨勢，讀懂價格語言；</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">買賣有信號，告別感覺交易。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">今天我們一起學習，技術分析中最基礎的元素——K線。 K線是當今最為普遍的價格標記法。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">先來看一下，一天中價格在市場中是如何運行的。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">在沒有經過K線標記法處理時，某投資品的價格是這樣的，無數的價格連在一起形成一條看起來毫無規律的曲線圖。看起來有些亂是不是？</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">下面，我們做一下簡單的技術分析處理，標記一下其中重要的數據，</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">開盤價、收盤價、最高價、最低價。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">我們過濾掉其中繁亂的價格變化，將其繪製成折線圖。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">如圖所示，這樣看起來是不是清晰很多？</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">可不可以，用更簡單的表示它呢？</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">當然可以，K線圖了解一下。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">如圖這樣處理，將開盤價、收盤價、最低價、最高價，平移到一條垂直線上。開盤價與收盤價之間構成K線實體，我們用較粗線條表示，實體到最高價和最低價之間我們用細線條表示，分別構成上影線和下影線。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">收盤價低於開盤價的，我們用紅色標記實體（答案在這裡哦），表示該時段價格下跌，通常稱為陰線。收盤價高於開盤價的，我們用綠色標記實體，表示該時段價格上漲，通常稱之為陽線。 （當然部分市場會使用相反顏色標記K線漲跌。）</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">當我們把每一天的K線連在一起，就會出現我們常見的K線圖樣子。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">圖中每一根紅色或綠色的K線都代表一天的價格變化數據。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">一天的價格走勢可以用一根K線表示，那麼一分鐘、一個小時、一星期呢？</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">根據統計價格變化的時間範圍的不同，我們將K線分為不同的周期。這是多條一分鐘K線連在一起的樣子，這是多條“週K線”連在一起的樣子。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">週期的劃分非常靈活多樣，幾分鐘、幾小時、幾天、幾週或是幾個月都可以。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">K線，在投資市場分析中有什麼作用？</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">特定的K線形態或特定的K線組合出現後，大概率會發生特定的價格走勢。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">因為價格包含一切市場行為，歷史會驚人的相似。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: left;\">後續我們再來分享，通過觀察K線規律性排列，預判未來價格漲跌的方法。</p>', '零基礎學幣市分析|1 從價格到K線');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (180, 87, 'en', 'What is KYC verification? How do I complete KYC validation?', NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (181, 87, 'zh-CN', '什么是KYC验证？如何完成KYC验证？', '<p>什么是KYC</p><p>KYC（Know your customer）政策（即充分了解你的客户）对账户持有人的强化审查，是反洗钱用于预防腐败的制度基础。</p><p>为什么做KYC</p><p>KYC政策不仅要求金融机构实行账户实名制，了解账户的实际控制人和交易的实际收益人，还要求对客户的身份、常住地址或企业所从事的业务进行充分的了解，并采取相应的措施。</p><p>如何进行KYC认证？</p><p>登录账户，点击小人头像选择身份认证。</p><p>根据步骤完成1级、2级、3级认证。</p><p>1级认证需要填写有效证件信息</p><p>2级认证需要上传有效证件正反面照片，完成后需要进行人脸识别，需要使用手机扫描页面二维码操作（需要手机端有支付宝）</p><p>3级认证需要通过手机APP进行认证，进行认证时需要口述文案。</p><p>手机APP与网页端一致。</p><p>认证须知：</p><p>1、请根据提示的内容，完成认证视频的录制。录制过程中会要求拍摄您的身份证或护照，请务必提前准备好您的证件。（国内用户只能使用身份证进行认证，不可以使用护照）</p><p>2、拍摄的每一步骤都会有文字提示，请按照文字提示进行操作。</p><p>3、每段视频拍摄好后，建议您都打开检查一下，如果拍摄效果不清晰的话需要您重新进行录制。否则很可能因为视频效果不清晰而审核不过。</p><p>4、视频上传对于流量和网速要求较高，视频上传预计占用您20M的流量，强烈建议您在WIFI环境下进行视频认证。 </p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (182, 87, 'zh-TW', '什麽是KYC驗證？如何完成KYC驗證？', '<p>什麽是KYC</p><p>KYC（Know your customer）政策（即充分了解你的客戶）對賬戶持有人的強化審查，是反洗錢用于預防腐敗的制度基礎。</p><p>爲什麽做KYC</p><p>KYC政策不僅要求金融機構實行賬戶實名制，了解賬戶的實際控制人和交易的實際收益人，還要求對客戶的身份、常住地址或企業所從事的業務進行充分的了解，並采取相應的措施。</p><p>如何進行KYC認證？</p><p><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/5632981376c2b118c3ccca25402008df5f218b9ce409f.png\" width=\"432\" height=\"79\" alt=\"\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p>登錄賬戶，點擊小人頭像選擇身份認證。</p><p>根據步驟完成1級、2級、3級認證。</p><p>1級認證需要填寫有效證件信息</p><p>2級認證需要上傳有效證件正反面照片，完成後需要進行人臉識別，需要使用手機掃描頁面二維碼操作（需要手機端有支付寶）</p><p>3級認證需要通過手機APP進行認證，進行認證時需要口述文案。</p><p>手機APP與網頁端一致。</p><p>認證須知：</p><p>1、請根據提示的內容，完成認證視頻的錄制。錄制過程中會要求拍攝您的身份證或護照，請務必提前准備好您的證件。（國內用戶只能使用身份證進行認證，不可以使用護照）</p><p>2、拍攝的每一步驟都會有文字提示，請按照文字提示進行操作。</p><p>3、每段視頻拍攝好後，建議您都打開檢查一下，如果拍攝效果不清晰的話需要您重新進行錄制。否則很可能因爲視頻效果不清晰而審核不過。</p><p>4、視頻上傳對于流量和網速要求較高，視頻上傳預計占用您20M的流量，強烈建議您在WIFI環境下進行視頻認證。</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (183, 88, 'en', 'What is Bitcoin?', '<p>What is bitcoin?</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Bitcoin is a consensus network, contributing to a new payment system and a fully digital currency. It is the first decentralized peer-to-peer payment network, which is controlled by its users without a central management organization or middleman. From the user\'s point of view, bitcoin is much like Internet cash. Bitcoin can also be regarded as the most outstanding three style bookkeeping system.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Who controls the bitcoin network?</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>No one owns the bitcoin network, just as no one owns the technology behind email. Bitcoin is controlled by all bitcoin users around the world. Developers can improve the software, but they can\'t change the rules of bitcoin protocol by force, because all users are free to choose the software they want to use. In order to keep compatibility with each other, all users need to choose software that follows the same rules. Only when all users reach a complete consensus can bitcoin work properly. Therefore, all users and developers are motivated to accept and protect this consensus.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>How does bitcoin work?</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>From the user\'s point of view, bitcoin is a mobile application or computer program, which can provide a personal bitcoin wallet with which users can pay and receive bitcoin. This is how bitcoin works for most users.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Behind the scenes, the entire bitcoin network shares a common ledger called \"blockchain.\". This general ledger contains every transaction processed, so that the user\'s computer can verify the validity of each transaction. The authenticity of each transaction is protected by the electronic signature corresponding to the sending address, which enables users to have complete control over the bitcoin transferred out from their own bitcoin address. In addition, anyone can use the computing power of specialized hardware to process transactions and get a bitcoin reward for it. This service is often referred to as \"mining.\". </p>', 'Bitcoin is a consensus network, contributing to a new payment system and a fully digital currency. It is the first decentralized peer-to-peer payment network, which is controlled by its users without a central management organization or middleman. From the user\'s point of view, bitcoin is much like Internet cash. Bitcoin can also be regarded as the most outstanding three style bookkeeping system.');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (184, 88, 'zh-CN', '什么是比特币？', '<p>什么是比特币？</p>\r\n<p>比特币是一个共识网络，促成了一个全新的支付系统和一种完全数字化的货币。它是第一个去中心化的对等支付网络，由其用户自己掌控而无须中央管理机构或中间人。从用户的角度来看，比特币很像互联网的现金。比特币也可以看作是目前最杰出的三式簿记系统。</p>\r\n<p>谁在控制比特币网络？</p>\r\n<p>没有谁拥有比特币网络，就像没有人拥有电子邮件背后的技术一样。比特币由世界各地所有的比特币用户控制。开发者可以改善软件，但他们不能强行改变比特币协议的规则，因为所有的用户都可以自由选择他们想用的软件。为了相互之间保持兼容性，所有用户也需要选择遵循相同规则的软件。只有所有用户达成完全一致的共识，比特币才能正常地工作。因此，所有的用户和开发者对接受和保护这一共识很有动力。</p>\r\n<p>比特币是如何运作的？</p>\r\n<p>从用户的角度来看，比特币就是一个手机应用或电脑程序，可以提供一个个人比特币钱包，用户可以用它支付和接收比特币。这就是比特币对于大多数用户的运作原理。</p>\r\n<p>在幕后，整个比特币网络共享一个称作“块链”的公共总帐。这份总帐包含了每一笔处理过的交易，使得用户的电脑可以核实每一笔交易的有效性。每一笔交易的真实性由发送地址对应的电子签名保护，这使得用户能够完全掌控从他们自己的比特币地址转出的比特币。另外，任何人都可以利用专门硬件的计算能力来处理交易并为此获得比特币奖励。这一服务经常被称作“挖矿”。</p>', '比特币是一个共识网络，促成了一个全新的支付系统和一种完全数字化的货币。它是第一个去中心化的对等支付网络，由其用户自己掌控而无须中央管理机构或中间人。从用户的角度来看，比特币很像互联网的现金。比特币也可以看作是目前最杰出的三式簿记系统。');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (185, 88, 'zh-TW', '什麽是比特幣？', '<p>什麼是比特幣？</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>比特幣是一個共識網絡，促成了一個全新的支付系統和一種完全數位化的貨幣。它是第一個去中心化的對等支付網絡，由其用戶自己掌控而無須中央管理機構或中間人。從用戶的角度來看，比特幣很像互聯網的現金。比特幣也可以看作是現時最傑出的三式簿記系統。</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>誰在控制比特幣網絡？</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>沒有誰擁有比特幣網絡，就像沒有人擁有電子郵件背後的科技一樣。比特幣由世界各地所有的比特幣用戶控制。開發者可以改善軟件，但他們不能强行改變比特幣協定的規則，因為所有的用戶都可以自由選擇他們想用的軟件。為了相互之間保持相容性，所有用戶也需要選擇遵循相同規則的軟件。只有所有用戶達成完全一致的共識，比特幣才能正常地工作。囙此，所有的用戶和開發者對接受和保護這一共識很有動力。</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>比特幣是如何運作的？</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>從用戶的角度來看，比特幣就是一個手機應用或電腦程式，可以提供一個個人比特幣錢包，用戶可以用它支付和接收比特幣。這就是比特幣對於大多數用戶的運作原理。</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>在幕後，整個比特幣網路共用一個稱作“塊鏈”的公共總帳。這份總帳包含了每一筆處理過的交易，使得用戶的電腦可以核實每一筆交易的有效性。每一筆交易的真實性由發送地址對應的電子簽名保護，這使得用戶能够完全掌控從他們自己的比特幣地址轉出的比特幣。另外，任何人都可以利用專門硬體的計算能力來處理交易並為此獲得比特幣獎勵。這一服務經常被稱作“挖礦”。</p>', '比特幣是一個共識網絡，促成了一個全新的支付系統和一種完全數位化的貨幣。它是第一個去中心化的對等支付網絡，由其用戶自己掌控而無須中央管理機構或中間人。從用戶的角度來看，比特幣很像互聯網的現金。比特幣也可以看作是現時最傑出的三式簿記系統。');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (186, 89, 'en', 'Bitcoin Breakout Fueling ‘Extreme Greed’ — Crypto Market Daily', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">Bitcoin (BTC) has finally made a major breakthrough. The cryptocurrency market leader surged 7% in the last 24 hours, rocketing past the $10,500 critical resistance level to $11,407 — its highest price since August 2018 — as per the STAI BTC Index price. Right now, the leading cryptocurrency is trading near $10,800. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">The bullish price action has been accompanied by an increase in trading volume — indicating that the positive momentum has a strong chance of continuing. Today\'s STAI BTCUSDT swap volume is likely to make a new high not seen since March 13.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">BTC fork Bitcoin Cash (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/index/bch-usd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/index/bch-usd\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\">BCH</a>) and its subsequent fork, Bitcoin SV (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/index/bsv-usd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/index/bsv-usd\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\">BSV</a>), followed the original Bitcoin’s trend and are up about 7%. Litecoin (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/index/ltc-usd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/index/ltc-usd\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\">LTC</a>) surged 10% and saw a huge increase in trading volume. On the other hand, ether (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/index/eth-usd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/index/eth-usd\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\">ETH</a>) saw a minor correction after seven straight days of gains. It is down 1.75%. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">In general, the total cryptocurrency market capitalization pumped another 3.9% to above $325 billion. Meanwhile, Bitcoin’s dominance climbed back to 61.6%, according to data from <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.coingecko.com/en\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.coingecko.com/en\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\">CoinGecko</a>. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">In the traditional market, we are also seeing price increases. The Nasdaq Composite Index added 1.6%, and the S&P 500 added 0.65%. Gold futures climbed past $1,900 per ounce on Monday. </p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg\" alt=\"OKEx Token Index Board as of 8:00 am UTC – 7/28/20. Source: OKEx\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\"><br></figcaption></figure><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\">The greediest moment of the year</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">The optimism of crypto market participants is apparent. The <a href=\"https://alternative.me/crypto/fear-and-greed-index/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\" data-mce-href=\"https://alternative.me/crypto/fear-and-greed-index/\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\">Crypto Fear and Greed Index</a> currently <a href=\"https://alternative.me/crypto/fear-and-greed-index/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\" data-mce-href=\"https://alternative.me/crypto/fear-and-greed-index/\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\">shows</a> a one-year peak of 76 — indicating a state of “extreme greed.” </p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg\" alt=\"Crypto Fear & Greed Index. Source: Alternative.me\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\"><br></figcaption></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">Meanwhile, the BTC long/short ratio has increased from 1.02 to 1.37 and the BTC margin lending ratio surged from 10.44 to 15.53 in the last 24 hours, according to STAI trading data. These two ratios are still running in the historically normal range. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">Due to higher funding rates, however, it is possible that bulls may close out their positions and create selling pressure.</p><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\">Top gainers and losers</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><br></p><ul style=\"padding: 0px 10px; margin: 0px 12px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: #214ded; line-height: 22px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px 10px; margin: 0px 12px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: #214ded; line-height: 22px;\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\">CTC/USDT +17.17%</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\">SNX/USDT +16.77%</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\">LRC/USDT +12.49%</li></ul><ul style=\"padding: 0px 10px; margin: 0px 12px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: #214ded; line-height: 22px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px 10px; margin: 0px 12px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; color: #214ded; line-height: 22px;\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\">HYC/USDT -9.26%</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\">LET/USDT -11.96%</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; list-style: disc; font-weight: 400; color: #4f5669; line-height: 19px;\">HDAO/USDT -12.30%</li></ul><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">As the market sentiment has turned toward Bitcoin, small-capitalization currencies are rising only modestly. Creditcoin (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/ctc-usdt\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/ctc-usdt\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\">CTC</a>) gained 17.17%. After a big pullback yesterday, Synthetic (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/snx-usdt\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/snx-usdt\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\">SNX</a>) bounced 16.77% today. Loopring (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/lrc-usdt\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/lrc-usdt\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\">LRC</a>) ranked third, gaining 12.49%. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">The biggest loser today is HyperDAO (<a href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/hdao-usdt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/hdao-usdt\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;\">HDAO</a>), which is down 12.30%.</p><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\">BTC technical analysis</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">Bitcoin is now starting a retracement phase after hitting prices above $11,000. Because the price has surpassed the critical $10,500 resistance level, we need to pay attention to the short-term threshold of $10,670. Midterm critical support is located at $10,280. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">The next price target for the first and foremost cryptocurrency is at $11,400 — but high funding rates remain a potential roadblock to price increases.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"425\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg\"><br></figure><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\">ETH technical analysis</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">The upward momentum has slowed for the price of ETH, but the bullish trend in the midterm remains intact. A continuation of the uptrend after a short-term correction is still promising. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">An intraday support level is around $299. As long as it holds this price, we may see another test of the previous high of $334. Because ETH has risen very quickly in the early going, profit-taking could impose a lot of pressure in the short-term. </p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg\" alt=\"OKEx ETH Perpetual Swap 1h chart – 7/28/20. Source: OKEx, TradingView\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" width=\"800\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg\"><figcaption style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;\"><br></figcaption></figure><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;\">LTC technical analysis</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">LTC has surged 10% in the last 24 hours as trading volumes have amplified. The intraday threshold is sitting around $52.50. Given the higher historical correlation between LTC and BTC, it is also important to be aware of Bitcoin\'s short-term movements when trading LTC.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"425\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg\"><br></figure><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><br></p><hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: #1f2236;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: #1f2236;\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><br></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;\">Disclaimer: This material should not be taken as the basis for making investment decisions, nor be construed as a recommendation to engage in investment transactions. Trading digital assets involve significant risk and can result in the loss of your invested capital. You should ensure that you fully understand the risk involved and take into consideration your level of experience, investment objectives and seek independent financial advice if necessary</em>.</p>', 'Bitcoin Breakout Fueling ‘Extreme Greed’ — Crypto Market Daily');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (187, 89, 'zh-CN', '零基础学币市分析|3 看涨K线组合', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218c95f12a3.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"425\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218c95f12a3.jpg\"></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">涨跌有趋势，读懂价格语言；</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">买卖有信号，告别感觉交易。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">本章我们一起学习K线组合的应用，今天分享K线的看涨组合。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">黑夜即将逝去，美好的一天就要开始，启明之星的出现，预示币价将迎来一轮上涨行情。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">什么样的K线组合是启明之星呢？如图红色画线处所示。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">标准的启明之星由三根K线组合而成，首先是一根较大的阴线，随后紧跟一根类似“十字”的星线，第三根K线是一根较大阳线。启明之星是否成立，对第三根阳线的长度有着明确的要求，它的收盘价格一定要高于第一根阴线实体的50%价位。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">在确定启明之星有效后，我们还可以通过第三根阳线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看涨力度强弱。如图，若阳线收盘价格刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下的看涨力度是比较弱势的。若后阳线收盘价格与前阴线开盘价格持平，则认为看涨力度较强。若后阳线收盘价明显高于前阴线开盘价，则看涨力度更强劲。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">刚刚所讲，是最标准的启明之星组合，但在实际的走势中，启明之星会有一些变化。那么市场中真实的启明之星是怎么样的呢？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">例如图示三种启明之星的样子，图一，中间并不是“十字”星，而更像是“T字”线。我们将它还原到真实的走势图中。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">币价大跌，出现启明之星，后市币价止跌反弹。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图二，中间由两根小K线组成。币价在上涨途中出现启明之星，后市币价继续上涨。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图三，由三根小K线或星线组成。币价大幅下跌，出现启明之星，随后币价止跌反转。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">接下来我们学习第二种看涨K线组合——看涨吞没。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">首先，看一下看涨吞没的特征。后一根阳线实体，完全覆盖前面阴线实体，如同阴线被阳线吞噬掉一般，表明多头力量正在大举反攻。因此得名看涨吞没。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">如何判断看涨力度呢？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图一，上涨阳线实体刚刚吞前面下跌阴线实体，该组合看涨力度最弱；图二，阳线实体明显高于前面阴线实体，甚至达到前阴线的两倍，该组合看涨力度很强；图三，阳线实体一举吞没前面多根阴线，该组合看涨力度最强。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">在市场中存在着很多非标准的看涨吞没组合，那实际的“看涨吞没”是怎样的呢？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">例如图示三种看涨吞没组合的样子，阳线并不需要完全吞没前面阴线的影线部分。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图一，币价大跌后出现看涨吞没组合，后市止跌并出现大幅反弹；</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图二，大阳线吞没两根小阴线，形成看涨吞没，随后展开一波上涨走势；</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">图三，阳线一举吞没三根阴线，后市出现大幅上涨。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">第三种看涨K线组合--塔形底。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">塔形底，左边是一根中阴线或大阴线；中间由若干根小K线组成，通常再5根以上；右边是一根中阳线或大阳线。整体看上去就像一个倒过来的宝塔，因此得名塔形底。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">一个有效塔形底要满足：最后一根阳线的收盘价格要超过前面大阴线实体的50%。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">塔形底展现的是：市场中做空力量逐渐减弱，至多空力量平衡，最后到上涨力度增强的过程。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">在确定塔型底有效后，我们还可以通过最后一根阳线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看涨力度强弱。如图，若阳线收盘价格刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下的看涨力度是比较弱势的。若后阳线收盘价格与前阴线开盘价格持平，则认为看涨力度较强。若后阳线收盘价明显高于前阴线开盘价，则看涨力度更强劲。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">当然，在实际走势中塔形底并不像我们示意图中展示的这么完美。所以要灵活变通。我们看一下市场中实际的“塔形底”是怎样的。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">变化一，实际样子非常接近塔形底的示意图。截图来自STAI币币交易区EOS/USDT的6小时K线图，塔形底出现在上涨趋势中，再次奠定了上涨优势，随后展开一轮伶俐的上涨行情。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">变化二，塔型底中间部分并不都是非常小的K线构成，K线震荡幅度较大。截图来自STAI币币交易区EOS/USDT的12小时K线图，币价大跌后形成塔型底，价格止跌，形成反转。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">最后我们回顾一下我们这一期的内容，</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\" data-mce-style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;\">三种典型的看涨K线组合。第一种，启明之星，预示着光明；第二种，看涨吞没，空方力量被多方快速绞杀；第三种，塔形底，看多力量的步步为营。<img src=\"涨跌有趋势，读懂价格语言；  买卖有信号，告别感觉交易。  本章我们一起学习K线组合的应用，今天分享K线的看涨组合。  黑夜即将逝去，美好的一天就要开始，启明之星的出现，预示币价将迎来一轮上涨行情。  什么样的K线组合是启明之星呢？如图红色画线处所示。  标准的启明之星由三根K线组合而成，首先是一根较大的阴线，随后紧跟一根类似“十字”的星线，第三根K线是一根较大阳线。启明之星是否成立，对第三根阳线的长度有着明确的要求，它的收盘价格一定要高于第一根阴线实体的50%价位。  在确定启明之星有效后，我们还可以通过第三根阳线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看涨力度强弱。如图，若阳线收盘价格刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下的看涨力度是比较弱势的。若后阳线收盘价格与前阴线开盘价格持平，则认为看涨力度较强。若后阳线收盘价明显高于前阴线开盘价，则看涨力度更强劲。  刚刚所讲，是最标准的启明之星组合，但在实际的走势中，启明之星会有一些变化。那么市场中真实的启明之星是怎么样的呢？  例如图示三种启明之星的样子，图一，中间并不是“十字”星，而更像是“T字”线。我们将它还原到真实的走势图中。  币价大跌，出现启明之星，后市币价止跌反弹。  图二，中间由两根小K线组成。币价在上涨途中出现启明之星，后市币价继续上涨。  图三，由三根小K线或星线组成。币价大幅下跌，出现启明之星，随后币价止跌反转。  接下来我们学习第二种看涨K线组合——看涨吞没。  首先，看一下看涨吞没的特征。后一根阳线实体，完全覆盖前面阴线实体，如同阴线被阳线吞噬掉一般，表明多头力量正在大举反攻。因此得名看涨吞没。  如何判断看涨力度呢？  图一，上涨阳线实体刚刚吞前面下跌阴线实体，该组合看涨力度最弱；图二，阳线实体明显高于前面阴线实体，甚至达到前阴线的两倍，该组合看涨力度很强；图三，阳线实体一举吞没前面多根阴线，该组合看涨力度最强。  在市场中存在着很多非标准的看涨吞没组合，那实际的“看涨吞没”是怎样的呢？  例如图示三种看涨吞没组合的样子，阳线并不需要完全吞没前面阴线的影线部分。  图一，币价大跌后出现看涨吞没组合，后市止跌并出现大幅反弹；  图二，大阳线吞没两根小阴线，形成看涨吞没，随后展开一波上涨走势；  图三，阳线一举吞没三根阴线，后市出现大幅上涨。  第三种看涨K线组合--塔形底。  塔形底，左边是一根中阴线或大阴线；中间由若干根小K线组成，通常再5根以上；右边是一根中阳线或大阳线。整体看上去就像一个倒过来的宝塔，因此得名塔形底。  一个有效塔形底要满足：最后一根阳线的收盘价格要超过前面大阴线实体的50%。  塔形底展现的是：市场中做空力量逐渐减弱，至多空力量平衡，最后到上涨力度增强的过程。  在确定塔型底有效后，我们还可以通过最后一根阳线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看涨力度强弱。如图，若阳线收盘价格刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下的看涨力度是比较弱势的。若后阳线收盘价格与前阴线开盘价格持平，则认为看涨力度较强。若后阳线收盘价明显高于前阴线开盘价，则看涨力度更强劲。  当然，在实际走势中塔形底并不像我们示意图中展示的这么完美。所以要灵活变通。我们看一下市场中实际的“塔形底”是怎样的。  变化一，实际样子非常接近塔形底的示意图。截图来自OKEX币币交易区EOS/USDT的6小时K线图，塔形底出现在上涨趋势中，再次奠定了上涨优势，随后展开一轮伶俐的上涨行情。  变化二，塔型底中间部分并不都是非常小的K线构成，K线震荡幅度较大。截图来自OKEX币币交易区EOS/USDT的12小时K线图，币价大跌后形成塔型底，价格止跌，形成反转。  最后我们回顾一下我们这一期的内容，  三种典型的看涨K线组合。第一种，启明之星，预示着光明；第二种，看涨吞没，空方力量被多方快速绞杀；第三种，塔形底，看多力量的步步为营。\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"涨跌有趋势，读懂价格语言；  买卖有信号，告别感觉交易。  本章我们一起学习K线组合的应用，今天分享K线的看涨组合。  黑夜即将逝去，美好的一天就要开始，启明之星的出现，预示币价将迎来一轮上涨行情。  什么样的K线组合是启明之星呢？如图红色画线处所示。  标准的启明之星由三根K线组合而成，首先是一根较大的阴线，随后紧跟一根类似“十字”的星线，第三根K线是一根较大阳线。启明之星是否成立，对第三根阳线的长度有着明确的要求，它的收盘价格一定要高于第一根阴线实体的50%价位。  在确定启明之星有效后，我们还可以通过第三根阳线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看涨力度强弱。如图，若阳线收盘价格刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下的看涨力度是比较弱势的。若后阳线收盘价格与前阴线开盘价格持平，则认为看涨力度较强。若后阳线收盘价明显高于前阴线开盘价，则看涨力度更强劲。  刚刚所讲，是最标准的启明之星组合，但在实际的走势中，启明之星会有一些变化。那么市场中真实的启明之星是怎么样的呢？  例如图示三种启明之星的样子，图一，中间并不是“十字”星，而更像是“T字”线。我们将它还原到真实的走势图中。  币价大跌，出现启明之星，后市币价止跌反弹。  图二，中间由两根小K线组成。币价在上涨途中出现启明之星，后市币价继续上涨。  图三，由三根小K线或星线组成。币价大幅下跌，出现启明之星，随后币价止跌反转。  接下来我们学习第二种看涨K线组合——看涨吞没。  首先，看一下看涨吞没的特征。后一根阳线实体，完全覆盖前面阴线实体，如同阴线被阳线吞噬掉一般，表明多头力量正在大举反攻。因此得名看涨吞没。  如何判断看涨力度呢？  图一，上涨阳线实体刚刚吞前面下跌阴线实体，该组合看涨力度最弱；图二，阳线实体明显高于前面阴线实体，甚至达到前阴线的两倍，该组合看涨力度很强；图三，阳线实体一举吞没前面多根阴线，该组合看涨力度最强。  在市场中存在着很多非标准的看涨吞没组合，那实际的“看涨吞没”是怎样的呢？  例如图示三种看涨吞没组合的样子，阳线并不需要完全吞没前面阴线的影线部分。  图一，币价大跌后出现看涨吞没组合，后市止跌并出现大幅反弹；  图二，大阳线吞没两根小阴线，形成看涨吞没，随后展开一波上涨走势；  图三，阳线一举吞没三根阴线，后市出现大幅上涨。  第三种看涨K线组合--塔形底。  塔形底，左边是一根中阴线或大阴线；中间由若干根小K线组成，通常再5根以上；右边是一根中阳线或大阳线。整体看上去就像一个倒过来的宝塔，因此得名塔形底。  一个有效塔形底要满足：最后一根阳线的收盘价格要超过前面大阴线实体的50%。  塔形底展现的是：市场中做空力量逐渐减弱，至多空力量平衡，最后到上涨力度增强的过程。  在确定塔型底有效后，我们还可以通过最后一根阳线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看涨力度强弱。如图，若阳线收盘价格刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下的看涨力度是比较弱势的。若后阳线收盘价格与前阴线开盘价格持平，则认为看涨力度较强。若后阳线收盘价明显高于前阴线开盘价，则看涨力度更强劲。  当然，在实际走势中塔形底并不像我们示意图中展示的这么完美。所以要灵活变通。我们看一下市场中实际的“塔形底”是怎样的。  变化一，实际样子非常接近塔形底的示意图。截图来自OKEX币币交易区EOS/USDT的6小时K线图，塔形底出现在上涨趋