STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"84\">As mentioned above, we may collect personal information of customers located in the European Economic Area. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"85\">In order to facilitate our services for customers located in the European Economic Area, we require explicit consent to transfer personal information from the European Economic Area to outside the area. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"86\">If you are an individual located in the European Economic Area and you refuse to agree to such transfer, you will no longer be able to use COINALL and our services. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"87\">You will be able to withdraw your digital assets; </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"88\">However, all other functions will be disabled. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"89\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"90\">V. How will we use your personal information </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"91\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"92\">COINALL uses personal information to communicate with you and manage, deliver, improve and personalize services. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"93\">COINALL may also generate general information from any personal information we collect and use it for our own purposes. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"94\">We may also use this information to communicate with you about other products or services provided by COINALL and/or its partners. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"95\">We will not share your personal data with third parties (except the partners who cooperate with COINALL), unless you have obtained your consent and further details below. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"96\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"97\">We may share your personal information with third parties: </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"98\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"99\">(a) If we think it is necessary to share it, implement the terms of service; </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"100\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"101\">(b) Abide by government agencies, including regulatory agencies, law enforcement and/or judicial departments; </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"102\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"103\">(c) A third party providing services to COINALL (such as management or technical services); </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"104\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"105\">(d) Sales or transfers involving our business or any part thereof. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"106\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"107\">In addition, we have implemented international standards to prevent money laundering, terrorist financing and avoid trade and economic sanctions, and will implement the final rules and regulations of virtual financial assets when effective, which may require us to conduct due diligence on customers. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"108\">This may include using third-party information and service providers that we will cross-reference with your personal information. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"109\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"110\">VI. Store your personal information </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"111\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"112\">The information we collect from you may be transferred and stored in destinations outside Malta. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"113\">This information may also be handled by employees working for us or our suppliers outside Malta. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"114\">Except for customers in the European Economic Area, when you submit your personal information, it means that you agree to the above transfer, storage or processing. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"115\">All the information you provide us is stored on our and/or third-party smart scan servers. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"116\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"117\">VII. access, modify and delete your personal information </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"118\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"119\">You have the right to request a copy of your personal information to make sure that the information we have about you is accurate and up-to-date. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"120\">If there is any inaccuracy in your personal information, you can request to update your information. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"121\">You can also request to delete your personal information, but we may refuse your request for specific reasons such as compliance or legal purposes. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"122\">If you want to check, modify and delete your personal information, please email to support@coinall.com with the theme of \"Information Inquiry\". </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"123\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"124\">In order to respond to data access, correction or deletion requests, we will verify the identity of the requester to ensure that he has the legal right to make such requests. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"125\">Although our goal is to reply to these requests free of charge, we reserve the right to charge you a reasonable fee if you repeat or make heavy requests. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"126\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"127\">VIII. Marketing and promotion </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"128\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"129\">We may inform you about the company\'s news promotion and information related to COINALL products and services. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"130\">We may share your personal information with third parties so that we can work on marketing and promotion projects or distribute marketing information. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"131\">When you use COINALL, you accept this privacy policy and agree to receive such marketing notices. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"132\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"133\">Customers can choose not to receive such marketing notices at any time. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"134\">If you don\'t want to receive such notification, please email to support@coinall.com. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"135\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"136\">You can\'t choose not to receive product-related notifications, such as policy/clause updates and operational notifications. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"137\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"138\">IX. Use of cookies </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"139\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"140\">When you visit COINALL, we may place a small amount of data for your browser Cookies according to industry practice. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"141\">This information can be placed on your computer or other devices used to access COINALL. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"142\">This information helps us identify you as a customer and collect information about your use of COINALL, so as to better customize our service and improve your experience. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"143\">We may also use the collected information to ensure that we comply with our compliance plan and that the security of your account will not be affected by the detection of irregular or suspicious account activities. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"144\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"145\">Most browsers are set to automatically accept Cookie. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"146\">Some Cookies will expire when you finish browsing, while others will remain on your computer or device until deleted or expired. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"147\">You can choose to refuse to use our Cookie, but this may affect the functionality of COINALL service or your user experience. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"148\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"149\">X. Information security </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"150\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"151\">We are committed to protecting COINALL and you from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure or destruction of personal information we collect and store. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"152\">We take various measures to ensure information security, including using SSL to encrypt all COINALL communications; </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"153\">All programs require two-factor authentication; </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"154\">Regularly review our personal information collection, storage and processing methods; </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"155\">And strictly restrict our employees and suppliers to access information only when necessary, and abide by strict contractual confidentiality obligations. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"156\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"157\">XI. contact COINALL about privacy issues or concerns. </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"158\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"159\">If you have any questions about this privacy policy or the use of personal information, please contact us at the following address in 08d2npc6@gmail.com with the theme of \"Privacy Requirements\". </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"160\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"161\">XII. Revision of our privacy policy </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"162\"> </span><span class=\"trans-sentence\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-index=\"163\">Any changes we make to our privacy policy in the future will be posted on this page, and if appropriate, we will inform you by email.</span></p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (201, 94, 'zh-CN', '比特币看起来超买，但分析师淡化了对下跌的恐惧', '<div id=\"node-0\"><p>随着本周比特币升至11个月来的最高水平，一些投资者开始担心该加密货币超买，并且可能由于价格大幅下跌而引起。 </p><p>但分析人士认为，这是一种过度反应。</p><p>根据CoinDesk的比特币价格指数，比特币的价格周一上涨至11,319美元，为2019年8月以来的最高水平。</p><p>在撰写本文时，该加密货币的交易价格接近11100美元，较一周前观察到的9400美元的低点上涨了18％。</p><p>突然的反弹将14天相对强度指数（RSI）推高至80.00以上。</p><p>超过70.00的度量被认为是超买，这意味着看涨移动现在已被过度拉伸。</p></div><div id=\"node-3\"><figure><div><div><picture data-image-id=\"499096\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png?format=webp 775w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png?format=jp2 775w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png 775w\" type=\"image/png\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png?format=webp 285w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png?format=jp2 285w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png 285w\" type=\"image/png\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png\" alt=\"第3天\" loading=\"lazy\" data-mce-src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png\"></picture></div></div><figcaption>比特币价格日线图</figcaption><figcaption>资料来源：TradingView</figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-4\"><p><span id=\"_mce_caret\" data-mce-bogus=\"1\" data-mce-type=\"format-caret\"></span>总部位于伦敦的Eterna Capital的首席首席投资官阿西姆·艾哈迈德（Asim Ahmad）表示，RSI高于70并不一定意味着即将出现的价格大幅下跌。<br></p><p>艾哈迈德说，这更有可能表明看涨行动过度，容易受到盘整或在最坏情况下的小幅回调。</p><p>Stack基金的研究主管Lennard Neo解释说，在一个强劲的趋势市场中，RSI可以在较长时期内保持通胀，并补充说其他指标显示出强劲的购买势头。</p><p>RSI基于价格，在之前的多头交易中保持较高水平。</p><p>巩固合并？</p></div><div id=\"node-6\"><figure><div><div><picture data-image-id=\"499099\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png?format=webp 775w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png?format=jp2 775w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png 775w\" type=\"image/png\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png?format=webp 285w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png?format=jp2 285w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png 285w\" type=\"image/png\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"349\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png\" alt=\"下载-6-43\" loading=\"lazy\" data-mce-src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png\"></picture></div></div><figcaption><small>2019年和2017年历史比特币日线图</small></figcaption><figcaption><small>资料来源：TradingView</small></figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-7\"><ul><li>尽管RSI在三个月期间多次多次印出高于70.00的高价，但比特币仍保持买价，并在2019年第二季度（左上）上涨了160％。</li><li>在2017年的牛市狂潮中观察到了类似的模式（右上）。</li><li>回到2020年夏季，RSI的超买指标可能会使加密货币在一段时间内徘徊在11,000美元左右。支撑位在10,500美元左右。</li><li>Neo表示，将资金从DeFi领域和传统市场转移到比特币将为加密货币创造动力。</li><li>如果美联储暗示对通货膨胀的容忍度更高，那么短期内价格可能会迅速升至12,000美元。这可能会使美元再次遭到抛售，并使黄金价格突破2,000美元大关。</li><li>LMAX Digital的货币策略师乔尔·克鲁格（Joel Kruger）表示，比特币仍然容易受到股票抛售的影响，正如三月份大盘崩盘时所看到的那样。</li></ul></div>', '随着本周比特币升至11个月来的最高水平，一些投资者开始担心该加密货币超买，并且可能由于价格大幅下跌而引起。');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (202, 94, 'en', 'Bitcoin Looks Overbought but Analysts Play Down Drop Fears', '<div id=\"node-0\"><p>With bitcoin rising to its highest level in 11 months this week, some investors are beginning to worry that the cryptocurrency is overbought and may be due for notable price drop. <br></p></div><div id=\"node-1\"><p>But analysts suggest that’s an overreaction.</p></div><div id=\"node-2\"><ul><li><li>Bitcoin’s price rose to $11,319 on Monday, the highest level since August 2019, according to CoinDesk’s Bitcoin Price Index.</li><li>At time of writing, the cryptocurrency is trading near $11,100, representing a 18% gain from lows near $9,400 observed a week ago.</li><li>The sudden rally has pushed the 14-day relative strength index (RSI) above 80.00.</li><li>A measurement of over 70.00 is considered overbought, meaning the bullish move is now overstretched.</li></li></ul></div><div id=\"node-3\"><figure><div><div><picture data-image-id=\"499096\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png?format=webp 775w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png?format=jp2 775w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png 775w\" type=\"image/png\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png?format=webp 285w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png?format=jp2 285w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png 285w\" type=\"image/png\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png\" alt=\"dailies-3\" loading=\"lazy\" data-mce-src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png\"></picture></div></div><figcaption><small>Daily chart of bitcoin\'s price</small></figcaption><figcaption><small>Source: TradingView</small></figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-4\"><ul><li><br></li><li>Asim Ahmad, co-chief investment officer at London-based Eterna Capital, said that an above-70 RSI does not necessarily imply an impending major price slide.</li><li>More likely it indicates that the bullish move is overstretched and vulnerable to consolidation or a minor retracement at worst, Ahmad said.</li><li>Lennard Neo, head of research at Stack funds, explained the RSI can stay inflated for longer periods in a strongly trending market, adding that other indicators are showing strong buying momentum.</li><li>The RSI is based on price and remained elevated during the previous bulls runs.</li></ul></div><div id=\"node-5\"><h2>Consolidation ahead?</h2></div><div id=\"node-6\"><figure><div><div><picture data-image-id=\"499099\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png?format=webp 775w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png?format=jp2 775w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png 775w\" type=\"image/png\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png?format=webp 285w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png?format=jp2 285w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png 285w\" type=\"image/png\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"349\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png\" alt=\"download-6-43\" loading=\"lazy\" data-mce-src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png\"></picture></div></div><figcaption><small>Historical bitcoin daily charts for 2019 and 2017</small></figcaption><figcaption><small>Source: TradingView</small></figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-7\"><ul><li>Bitcoin remained bid and rose 160% in the second quarter of 2019 (above left) despite the RSI printing highs above 70.00 several times during the three-month period.</li><li>A similar pattern was observed during the bull market frenzy of 2017 (above right).</li><li>Back to summer 2020 and the overbought measurement on the RSI may keep the cryptocurrency hovering around $11,000 for some time. Support is seen around $10,500.</li><li>Rotation of money out of the DeFi space and traditional markets and into bitcoin would create momentum for the cryptocurrency, said Neo.</li><li>Prices could rise quickly toward $12,000 in the short-term if the U.S. Federal Reserve signals higher tolerance for inflation. That could yield another sell-off for the greenback and send gold above the $2,000 mark.</li><li>Bitcoin still remains vulnerable to a sell-off in equities, as was seen during the wider markets crash in March, according to Joel Kruger, a currency strategist at LMAX Digital.</li></ul></div>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (203, 94, 'zh-TW', '比特幣看起來超買，但分析師淡化了對下跌的恐懼', '<div id=\"node-0\"><p>隨著本周比特幣升至11個月來的最高水准，一些投資者開始擔心該加密貨幣超買，並且可能由於價格大幅下跌而引起。</p><p>但分析人士認為，這是一種過度反應。</p><p>根據CoinDesk的比特幣價格指數，比特幣的價格週一上漲至11319美元，為2019年8月以來的最高水准。</p><p>在撰寫本文時，該加密貨幣的交易價格接近11100美元，較一周前觀察到的9400美元的低點上漲了18%。</p><p>突然的反彈將14天相對强度指數（RSI）推高至80.00以上。</p><p>超過70.00的度量被認為是超買，這意味著看漲移動現在已被過度拉伸。</p></div><div id=\"node-3\"><figure><div><div><picture data-image-id=\"499096\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png?format=webp 775w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png?format=jp2 775w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png 775w\" type=\"image/png\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png?format=webp 285w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png?format=jp2 285w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png 285w\" type=\"image/png\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png\" alt=\"第3天\" loading=\"lazy\" data-mce-src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png\"></picture></div></div><figcaption><small>比特币价格日线图</small></figcaption><figcaption><small>资料来源：TradingView</small></figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-4\"><ul><li><br></li><li>總部位於倫敦的Eterna Capital的首席首席投資官阿西姆·艾哈邁德（Asim Ahmad）表示，RSI高於70並不一定意味著即將出現的價格大幅下跌。<br></li><li>艾哈邁德說，這更有可能表明看漲行動過度，容易受到盤整或在最壞情况下的小幅回檔。<br></li><li>Stack基金的研究首長Lennard Neo解釋說，在一個強勁的趨勢市場中，RSI可以在較長時期內保持通脹，並補充說其他名額顯示出強勁的購買勢頭。<br></li><li>RSI基於價格，在之前的多頭交易中保持較高水準。</li></ul></div><div id=\"node-5\"><h2>巩固合并？</h2></div><div id=\"node-6\"><figure><div><div><picture data-image-id=\"499099\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png?format=webp 775w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png?format=jp2 775w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png 775w\" type=\"image/png\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png?format=webp 285w\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png?format=jp2 285w\" type=\"image/jp2\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png 285w\" type=\"image/png\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"349\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png\" alt=\"下载-6-43\" loading=\"lazy\" data-mce-src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png\"></picture></div></div><figcaption><small>2019年和2017年历史比特币日线图</small></figcaption><figcaption><small>资料来源：TradingView</small></figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-7\"><ul><li>儘管RSI在三個月期間多次多次印出高於70.00的高價，但比特幣仍保持買價，並在2019年第二季度（左上）上漲了160%。<br></li><li>在2017年的牛市狂潮中觀察到了類似的模式（右上）。<br></li><li>回2020年夏季，RSI的超買名額可能會使加密貨幣在一段時間內徘徊在11000美元左右。支撐比特在10500美元左右。<br></li><li>Neo表示，將資金從DeFi領域和傳統市場轉移到比特幣將為加密貨幣創造動力。<br></li><li>如果美聯儲暗示對通貨膨脹的容忍度更高，那麼短期內價格可能會迅速升至12000美元。這可能會使美元再次遭到拋售，並使黃金價格突破2000美元大關。<br></li><li>LMAX Digital的貨幣策略師喬爾·克魯格（Joel Kruger）表示，比特幣仍然容易受到股票拋售的影響，正如三月份大盤崩盤時所看到的那樣。</li></ul></div>', '隨著本周比特幣升至11個月來的最高水准，一些投資者開始擔心該加密貨幣超買，並且可能由於價格大幅下跌而引起。');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (204, 95, 'zh-CN', '预期进一步的比特币收益将使期货合约清算蒙上阴影', '<div id=\"node-0\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 41px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.42;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">尽管领先的加密货币</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">周一</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">的每日涨幅</font></font><a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/gold-reaches-all-time-high-as-bitcoin-breaks-above-11k\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">超过10％，</a><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">但已结算的比特币期货合约仍保持在相对较低的水平，</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">因为一些交易员预计价格会上涨。</font></font></p></div><div id=\"node-1\" class=\"article-list\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 42px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><ul style=\"margin: 24px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style-type: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\"><a href=\"https://qa.coindesk.com/price/bitcoin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">比特币</a><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">以上$ 11,400飙升，周一，但这种波动只能引发破产现价仅售$ 133万美元的比特币BitMEX期货合约的，领先的比特币衍生产品交易所，根据</font><a href=\"http://skew.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">偏移</a><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">。</font></li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">自从2019年9月以来，比特币一直保持在该价格以下，对于许多交易员来说，突破10500美元是一个关键的看涨市场信号。</font></li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">周一的清算还不到5月10日清算所关闭的合约数量的一半，当时比特币从每日开盘价9,500美元短暂下跌了15％，至8,100美元。</font></li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">显着的比特币价格变动通常会达到随着时间的推移积累或以过度杠杆交易的市场流动性，触发数亿期货合约的清算。</font></li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">加密货币交易公司Zorax Capital的执行合伙人Zoran Scekic说：“每个人都知道情况会加剧。”他补充说，他认为目前零售交易员并没有过度利用杠杆空头，这可能是相对较低的原因清算期货合约的水平。</font></li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">Scekic预计，由于市场情绪转为看涨，因此在首次适度的价格修正时会出现“大量清算”。</font></li></ul></div><div id=\"node-2\" class=\"inline-image-v2 default\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; justify-content: center; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 775px; width: max-content;\"><div class=\"image-lightbox-wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; cursor: zoom-in;\"><span class=\"expand-lightbox-icon-holder\" style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; z-index: 1; position: absolute; bottom: 10px; right: 10px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease 0s; cursor: pointer; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; width: 40px; height: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\"><svg class=\"svg-icon\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path d=\"M19.5,-3.55271368e-15 L20,-3.55271368e-15 L20,0.5 L20,7.5 L19,7.5 L19,1.827 L11.8427091,8.38850444 L11.1572909,7.66035488 L18.42,1 L11.5,1 L11.5,-3.55271368e-15 L19.5,-3.55271368e-15 Z M0.5,20 L-1.13686838e-13,20 L-1.13686838e-13,19.5 L-1.13686838e-13,12.5 L1,12.5 L1,18.173 L8.15729086,11.6114956 L8.84270914,12.3396451 L1.58,19 L8.5,19 L8.5,20 L0.5,20 Z\" id=\"Expand\" fill=\"#FCC117\" fill-rule=\"nonzero\"></path></g></svg></span><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><picture data-image-id=\"498643\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-775x495.png?format=webp 775w\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-775x495.png?format=jp2 775w\" type=\"image/jp2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-775x495.png 775w\" type=\"image/png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-855x546.png?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-570x364.png?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-285x182.png?format=webp 285w\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-855x546.png?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-570x364.png?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-285x182.png?format=jp2 285w\" type=\"image/jp2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-855x546.png 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-570x364.png 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-285x182.png 285w\" type=\"image/png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"495\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-775x495.png\" alt=\"btc-liqs-2020\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></picture></div></div><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 775px;\"><br></figcaption></figure></div>', '比特币以上$ 11,400飙升，周一，但这种波动只能引发破产现价仅售$ 133万美元的比特币BitMEX期货合约的，领先的比特币衍生产品交易所，根据偏移。\r\n自从2019年9月以来，比特币一直保持在该价格以下，对于许多交易员来说，突破10500美元是一个关键的看涨市场信号。');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (205, 96, 'zh-CN', '市场裹足：比特币的价格和以太的主导地位坐在2020年的高点', '<div id=\"node-0\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 41px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.42;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">随着波动性反弹，比特币的价格处于11个月高位。</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">同时，由于去中心化金融（DeFi）的持续增长，以太的主导地位已达到峰值。</font></font></p></div><div id=\"node-1\" class=\"article-list\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 42px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><ul style=\"margin: 24px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style-type: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\"><a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/price/bitcoin\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"></font></a><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">截至20:00 UTC（美国东部时间下午4点），</font><a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/price/bitcoin\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">比特币</font></a><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">（BTC）交易价格约为10,998美元。</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">在之前的24小时内增长了2.1％。</font></font></li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">比特币的24小时范围：10,573美元至11,422美元</font></li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">BTC高于10天和50天移动平均线，这对市场技术人员是一个看涨信号。</font></li></ul></div><div id=\"node-2\" class=\"inline-image-v2 default\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; justify-content: center; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inhe