x; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></picture></div></div><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 775px;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">自7月26日起在Coinbase上进行比特币交易。</font></font></small></figcaption><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">资料来源：</font></font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">TradingView</font></font></small></figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-3\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">周二，比特币的价格再创2020年的新高，在像Coinbase这样的现货交易所达到11422美元。</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">世界上最古老的加密货币的价格最后一次在Coinbase上达到该水平是2019年8月12日。</font></font><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"> </em></p></div><div id=\"node-4\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\">阅读更多：</em></span><a href=\"http://coindesk.com/bitcoin-futures-volume-price\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\">价格达到$ 11K时，比特币期货交易量增长186％</em></span></a></p></div><div id=\"node-5\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">Fairlead Strategies的分析师凯蒂·斯托克顿（Katie Stockton）表示：“比特币不仅在决定性的阻力位上突破了10,000美元的心理阻力位，而且还突破了10,055美元的关键水平。” </font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">但是，她对此表示怀疑，价格是否会保持在$ 11,000以上。 </font></font></p></div><div id=\"node-6\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">“这种上涨有一些上行疲惫的迹象，因此我们一定要等待突破确认，然后再向比特币添加风险敞口。</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">这将在每周收盘价超过10,055美元时发生。”她补充道。 </font></font></p></div><div id=\"node-7\" class=\"inline-image-v2 default\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; justify-content: center; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 775px; width: max-content;\"><div class=\"image-ligh