/div><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 775px;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">过去一年Coinbase上的比特币现货价格。</font></font></small></figcaption><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">资料来源：</font></font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">TradingView</font></font></small></figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-8\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">BitBull Capital加密货币基金的Konstatine Kogan指出：</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">“ </font></font><a href=\"https://alternative.me/crypto/fear-and-greed-index/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">恐惧与贪婪指数处于\'极端贪婪\'区域</a><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">，正在朝超买水平发展。” </font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">“第一个支撑位是10,000美元。</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">如果比特币跌破这一水平，那么就有可能随后下跌。”他补充说。 </font></font></p></div><div id=\"node-9\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">并非所有利益相关者都对比特币市场的价格上涨感到怀疑。</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">根据聚合商CryptoCompare的数据，对交易者来说，一个积极的因素是波动性正在卷土重来。</font></font></p></div>', '随着波动性反弹，比特币的价格处于11个月高位。同时，由于去中心化金融（DeFi）的持续增长，以太的主导地位已达到峰值。');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (206, 96, 'zh-TW', NULL, '<p>隨著波動性反彈，比特幣的價格處於11個月高位。同時，由於去中心化金融（DeFi）的持續增長，乙太的主導地位已達到峰值。</p><p>截至20:00 UTC（美國東部時間下午4點），比特幣（BTC）交易價格約為10998美元。在之前的24小時內增長了2.1%。</p><p>比特幣的24小時範圍：10573美元至11422美元</p><p>BTC高於10天和50天移動平均線，這對市場科技人員是一個看漲訊號。</p><div id=\"node-2\" class=\"inline-image-v2 default\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; justify-content: center; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 775px; width: max-content;\"><div class=\"image-lightbox-wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; cursor: zoom-in;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><picture data-image-id=\"498958\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"316\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-775x316.jpg\" alt=\"btcjul28\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></picture></div></div><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 775px;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">自7月26日起在Coinbase上进行比特币交易。</font></font></small></figcaption><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">资料来源：</font></font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">TradingView</font></font></small></figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-3\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 1.56;\"><font color=\"#161f36\" face=\"acumin-pro, sans-serif\">週二，比特幣的價格再創2020年的新高，在像Coinbase這樣的現貨交易所達到11422美元。世界上最古老的加密貨幣的價格最後一次在Coinbase上達到該水准是2019年8月12日。</font></p><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 1.56;\"><font color=\"#161f36\" face=\"acumin-pro, sans-serif\">閱讀更多：價格達到$ 11K時，比特幣期貨交易量增長186%</font></p><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 1.56;\"><font color=\"#161f36\" face=\"acumin-pro, sans-serif\">Fairlead Strategies的分析師凱蒂·斯托克頓（Katie Stockton）表示：“比特幣不僅在决定性的阻力位上突破了10000美元的心理阻力位，而且還突破了10055美元的關鍵水准。”但是，她對此表示懷疑，價格是否會保持在$ 11000以上。</font></p><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 1.56;\"><font color=\"#161f36\" face=\"acumin-pro, sans-serif\">“這種上漲有一些上行疲憊的迹象，囙此我們一定要等待突破確認，然後再向比特幣添加風險敞口。這將在每週收盤價超過10055美元時發生。”她補充道。</font></p></div><div id=\"node-7\" class=\"inline-image-v2 default\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; justify-content: center; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 775px; width: max-content;\"><div class=\"image-lightbox-wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; cursor: zoom-in;\"><span class=\"expand-lightbox-icon-holder\" style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; z-index: 1; position: absolute; bottom: 10px; right: 10px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease 0s; cursor: pointer; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; width: 40px; height: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\"><svg class=\"svg-icon\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path d=\"M19.5,-3.55271368e-15 L20,-3.55271368e-15 L20,0.5 L20,7.5 L19,7.5 L19,1.827 L11.8427091,8.38850444 L11.1572909,7.66035488 L18.42,1 L11.5,1 L11.5,-3.55271368e-15 L19.5,-3.55271368e-15 Z M0.5,20 L-1.13686838e-13,20 L-1.13686838e-13,19.5 L-1.13686838e-13,12.5 L1,12.5 L1,18.173 L8.15729086,11.6114956 L8.84270914,12.3396451 L1.58,19 L8.5,19 L8.5,20 L0.5,20 Z\" id=\"Expand\" fill=\"#FCC117\" fill-rule=\"nonzero\"></path></g></svg></span><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><picture data-image-id=\"498956\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-775x328.jpg?format=webp 775w\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-775x328.jpg?format=jp2 775w\" type=\"image/jp2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-775x328.jpg 775w\" type=\"image/jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-855x362.jpg?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-570x241.jpg?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-285x121.jpg?format=webp 285w\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-855x362.jpg?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-570x241.jpg?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-285x121.jpg?format=jp2 285w\" type=\"image/jp2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-855x362.jpg 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-570x241.jpg 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-285x121.jpg 285w\" type=\"image/jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"328\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-775x328.jpg\" alt=\"btcyear\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></picture></div></div><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 775px;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">过去一年Coinbase上的比特币现货价格。</font></font></small></figcaption><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">资料来源：</font></font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;\">TradingView</font></font></small></figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-8\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 1.56;\"><font color=\"#161f36\" face=\"acumin-pro, sans-serif\">BitBull Capital加密貨幣基金的Konstatine Kogan指出：“恐懼與貪婪指數處於\'極端貪婪\'區域，正在朝超買水准發展。”“第一個支撐比特是10000美元。如果比特幣跌破這一水准，那麼就有可能隨後下跌。”他補充說。</font></p><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 1.56;\"><font color=\"#161f36\" face=\"acumin-pro, sans-serif\">並非所有利益相關者都對比特幣市場的價格上漲感到懷疑。根據聚合商CryptoCompare的數據，對交易者來說，一個積極的因素是波動性正在捲土重來。</font></p></div>', '隨著波動性反彈，比特幣的價格處於11個月高位。同時，由於去中心化金融（DeFi）的持續增長，乙太的主導地位已達到峰值。');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (207, 96, 'en', 'Market Wrap: Bitcoin’s Price and Ether’s Dominance Sit at 2020 Highs', '<div id=\"node-0\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 41px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.42;\">Bitcoin’s price is at its 11-month high as volatility bounces back up. Meanwhile, ether’s dominance has spiked on continued growth in decentralized finance (DeFi).</p></div><div id=\"node-1\" class=\"article-list\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 42px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><ul style=\"margin: 24px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style-type: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\"><a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/price/bitcoin\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">Bitcoin</a> (BTC) trading around $10,998 as of 20:00 UTC (4 p.m. ET). Gaining 2.1% over the previous 24 hours.</li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">Bitcoin’s 24-hour range: $10,573-$11,422</li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">BTC above 10-day and 50-day moving averages, a bullish signal for market technicians.</li></ul></div><div id=\"node-2\" class=\"inline-image-v2 default\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; justify-content: center; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 775px; width: max-content;\"><div class=\"image-lightbox-wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; cursor: zoom-in;\"><span class=\"expand-lightbox-icon-holder\" style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; z-index: 1; position: absolute; bottom: 10px; right: 10px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease 0s; cursor: pointer; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; width: 40px; height: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\"><svg class=\"svg-icon\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path d=\"M19.5,-3.55271368e-15 L20,-3.55271368e-15 L20,0.5 L20,7.5 L19,7.5 L19,1.827 L11.8427091,8.38850444 L11.1572909,7.66035488 L18.42,1 L11.5,1 L11.5,-3.55271368e-15 L19.5,-3.55271368e-15 Z M0.5,20 L-1.13686838e-13,20 L-1.13686838e-13,19.5 L-1.13686838e-13,12.5 L1,12.5 L1,18.173 L8.15729086,11.6114956 L8.84270914,12.3396451 L1.58,19 L8.5,19 L8.5,20 L0.5,20 Z\" id=\"Expand\" fill=\"#FCC117\" fill-rule=\"nonzero\"></path></g></svg></span><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><picture data-image-id=\"498958\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-775x316.jpg?format=webp 775w\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-775x316.jpg?format=jp2 775w\" type=\"image/jp2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-775x316.jpg 775w\" type=\"image/jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-855x349.jpg?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-570x232.jpg?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-285x116.jpg?format=webp 285w\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-855x349.jpg?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-570x232.jpg?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-285x116.jpg?format=jp2 285w\" type=\"image/jp2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-855x349.jpg 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-570x232.jpg 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-285x116.jpg 285w\" type=\"image/jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"316\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcjul28-775x316.jpg\" alt=\"btcjul28\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></picture></div></div><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 775px;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\">Bitcoin trading on Coinbase since July 26.</small></figcaption><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\">Source: TradingView</small></figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-3\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\">The price of bitcoin hit another 2020 high Tuesday, reaching $11,422 on spot exchanges like Coinbase. The last time the price of the world’s oldest cryptocurrency hit that level on Coinbase was Aug. 12, 2019.<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"> </em></p></div><div id=\"node-4\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\">Read More: </em></span><a href=\"http://coindesk.com/bitcoin-futures-volume-price\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\">Bitcoin Futures Volume Surges 186% as Price Hits $11K</em></span></a></p></div><div id=\"node-5\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\">“Bitcoin has pushed decisively through not only psychological resistance of $10,000 but also a key level near $10,055,” said Katie Stockton, an analyst at Fairlead Strategies. However, she is skeptical the price can stay over $11,000. </p></div><div id=\"node-6\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\">“There are some signs of upside exhaustion on this push higher, so we would be sure to await confirmation of the breakout before adding exposure to bitcoin. This would occur on consecutive weekly closes above $10,055,” she added. </p></div><div id=\"node-7\" class=\"inline-image-v2 default\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; justify-content: center; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 775px; width: max-content;\"><div class=\"image-lightbox-wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; cursor: zoom-in;\"><span class=\"expand-lightbox-icon-holder\" style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; z-index: 1; position: absolute; bottom: 10px; right: 10px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease 0s; cursor: pointer; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; width: 40px; height: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\"><svg class=\"svg-icon\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path d=\"M19.5,-3.55271368e-15 L20,-3.55271368e-15 L20,0.5 L20,7.5 L19,7.5 L19,1.827 L11.8427091,8.38850444 L11.1572909,7.66035488 L18.42,1 L11.5,1 L11.5,-3.55271368e-15 L19.5,-3.55271368e-15 Z M0.5,20 L-1.13686838e-13,20 L-1.13686838e-13,19.5 L-1.13686838e-13,12.5 L1,12.5 L1,18.173 L8.15729086,11.6114956 L8.84270914,12.3396451 L1.58,19 L8.5,19 L8.5,20 L0.5,20 Z\" id=\"Expand\" fill=\"#FCC117\" fill-rule=\"nonzero\"></path></g></svg></span><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><picture data-image-id=\"498956\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-775x328.jpg?format=webp 775w\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-775x328.jpg?format=jp2 775w\" type=\"image/jp2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-775x328.jpg 775w\" type=\"image/jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-855x362.jpg?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-570x241.jpg?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-285x121.jpg?format=webp 285w\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-855x362.jpg?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-570x241.jpg?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-285x121.jpg?format=jp2 285w\" type=\"image/jp2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-855x362.jpg 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-570x241.jpg 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-285x121.jpg 285w\" type=\"image/jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"328\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btcyear-775x328.jpg\" alt=\"btcyear\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></picture></div></div><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 775px;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\">Bitcoin spot price on Coinbase the past year.</small></figcaption><figcaption style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><small style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2em; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\">Source: TradingView</small></figcaption></figure></div><div id=\"node-8\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\">“The <a href=\"https://alternative.me/crypto/fear-and-greed-index/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">Fear and Greed Index is in the ‘extreme greed’ zone</a>, moving towards the overbought level,” noted Konstatine Kogan of cryptocurrency fund of funds BitBull Capital. “The first support is located at the level of $10,000. If bitcoin falls below this mark, then there is a possibility of a subsequent decline,” he added. </p></div><div id=\"node-9\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\">Not all stakeholders are suspicious of the bitcoin market’s price run-up. One positive for traders is that volatility is making a comeback, according to data from aggregator CryptoCompare. </p></div><div id=\"node-10\" class=\"inline-image-v2 default\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; justify-content: center; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-wid