ww.coindesk.com/price/tezos\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">tezos</a> (XTZ) - 0.43%</li></ul></div><div id=\"node-26\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\">Read More: </em></span><a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/tetras-capital-shuts-down-crypto-hedge-fund-after-75-loss\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\">Tetras Capital Shuts Down Crypto Hedge Fund After 75% Loss</em></span></a></p></div><div id=\"node-27\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\">Equities:</p></div><div id=\"node-28\" class=\"article-list\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 42px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><ul style=\"margin: 24px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style-type: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">In Asia the Nikkei 225 closed in the red 0.26%, <a href=\"https://www.investing.com/news/stock-market-news/japan-stocks-lower-at-close-of-trade-nikkei-225-down-026-2242954\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">dragged down by losses in the transportation and construction sectors</a>.</li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">In Europe The FTSE 100 ended the day in the green 0.40% <a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/07/28/europe-markets-us-stimulus-hopes-rising-coronavirus-cases-in-focus.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">on hopes of fresh U.S. government stimulus boosting the global economy</a>.</li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">In the United States the S&P 500 slipped 0.70%, <a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/07/27/stock-market-futures-open-to-close-news.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">dragged lower by tech stocks despite plans for a new relief package for jobless Americans</a>.</li></ul></div><div id=\"node-29\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\">Read More: </em></span><a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/ethereum-defi-platforms-eth-history\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\">One Billion, Two Billion, Three Billion, Four? DeFi Knocking on TradFi’s Door</em></span></a></p></div><div id=\"node-30\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;\">Commodities:</p></div><div id=\"node-31\" class=\"article-list\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 42px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><ul style=\"margin: 24px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style-type: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">Gold is up 0.75% at $1,956 as of press time after hitting an intraday high of $1,980.</li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">Oil is down 1.7%. Price per barrel of West Texas Intermediate crude: $40.94</li></ul></div>', 'Bitcoin’s price is at its 11-month high as volatility bounces back up. Meanwhile, ether’s dominance has spiked on continued growth in decentralized finance (DeFi).');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (208, 95, 'en', 'Expectations for Even Further Bitcoin Gains Keep Lid on Futures Contracts Liquidations', '<div id=\"node-0\" class=\"article-pharagraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;\"><p class=\"text \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 41px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.42;\">Liquidated bitcoin futures contracts stay at relatively low levels despite the bellwether cryptocurrency’s daily gain of <a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/gold-reaches-all-time-high-as-bitcoin-breaks-above-11k\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">more than 10%</a> Monday as some traders expect higher price movements.</p></div><div id=\"node-1\" class=\"article-list\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 42px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><ul style=\"margin: 24px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style-type: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\"><a href=\"https://qa.coindesk.com/price/bitcoin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">Bitcoin</a> soared above $11,400 on Monday, but this volatility only triggered the bankruptcy price for only $133 million worth of bitcoin futures contracts on BitMEX, the leading bitcoin derivatives exchange, according to <a href=\"http://skew.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-reactroot=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;\">Skew</a>.</li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">Breaking above $10,500 was a critical bullish market signal for many traders since bitcoin had stayed below that price since September 2019.</li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">Monday’s liquidations are less than half the amount of contracts closed by liquidation on May 10, when bitcoin briefly dropped 15% to $8,100 from a daily open of $9,500.</li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">Significant bitcoin price movements generally trigger the liquidation of hundreds of millions in futures contracts by reaching pockets of market liquidity that has accumulated over time or are traded with excessive leverage.</li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">“Everyone knows this is going up,” said Zoran Scekic, managing partner at cryptocurrency trading firm Zorax Capital, adding that he doesn’t think retail traders are in over-leveraged short positions at this point, which could be the reason behind relatively low levels of liquidated futures contracts.</li><li style=\"margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;\">Scekic expects an “abundance of liquidations” at the first moderate price correction, however, given the market\'s sentiment shift to bullishness.</li></ul></div><div id=\"node-2\" class=\"inline-image-v2 default\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; justify-content: center; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 775px; width: max-content;\"><div class=\"image-lightbox-wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; cursor: zoom-in;\"><span class=\"expand-lightbox-icon-holder\" style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; z-index: 1; position: absolute; bottom: 10px; right: 10px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease 0s; cursor: pointer; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; width: 40px; height: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\"><svg class=\"svg-icon\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path d=\"M19.5,-3.55271368e-15 L20,-3.55271368e-15 L20,0.5 L20,7.5 L19,7.5 L19,1.827 L11.8427091,8.38850444 L11.1572909,7.66035488 L18.42,1 L11.5,1 L11.5,-3.55271368e-15 L19.5,-3.55271368e-15 Z M0.5,20 L-1.13686838e-13,20 L-1.13686838e-13,19.5 L-1.13686838e-13,12.5 L1,12.5 L1,18.173 L8.15729086,11.6114956 L8.84270914,12.3396451 L1.58,19 L8.5,19 L8.5,20 L0.5,20 Z\" id=\"Expand\" fill=\"#FCC117\" fill-rule=\"nonzero\"></path></g></svg></span><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><picture data-image-id=\"498643\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-775x495.png?format=webp 775w\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-775x495.png?format=jp2 775w\" type=\"image/jp2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 415px)\" sizes=\"(min-width: 415px) 775px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-775x495.png 775w\" type=\"image/png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-855x546.png?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-570x364.png?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-285x182.png?format=webp 285w\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-855x546.png?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-570x364.png?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-285x182.png?format=jp2 285w\" type=\"image/jp2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 414px)\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 285px\" srcset=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-855x546.png 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-570x364.png 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-285x182.png 285w\" type=\"image/png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img width=\"775\" height=\"495\" src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-775x495.png\" alt=\"btc-liqs-2020\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></picture></div></div></figure></div>', 'Bitcoin soared above $11,400 on Monday, but this volatility only triggered the bankruptcy price for only $133 million worth of bitcoin futures contracts on BitMEX, the leading bitcoin derivatives exchange, according to Skew.');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (209, 95, 'zh-TW', '預期進壹步的比特幣收益將使期貨合約清算蒙上陰影', '<p>盡管領先的加密貨幣周壹的每日漲幅超過10％，但已結算的比特幣期貨合約仍保持在相對較低的水平，因為壹些交易員預計價格會上漲。</p><p>比特幣以上$ 11,400飆升，周壹，但這種波動只能引發破產現價僅售$ 133萬美元的比特幣BitMEX期貨合約的，領先的比特幣衍生產品交易所，根據偏移。</p><p>自從2019年9月以來，比特幣壹直保持在該價格以下，對於許多交易員來說，突破10500美元是壹個關鍵的看漲市場信號。</p><p>周壹的清算還不到5月10日清算所關閉的合約數量的壹半，當時比特幣從每日開盤價9,500美元短暫下跌了15％，至8,100美元。</p><p>顯著的比特幣價格變動通常會達到隨著時間的推移積累或以過度杠桿交易的市場流動性，觸發數億期貨合約的清算。</p><p>加密貨幣交易公司Zorax Capital的執行合夥人Zoran Scekic說：“每個人都知道情況會加劇。”他補充說，他認為目前零售交易員並沒有過度利用杠桿空頭，這可能是相對較低的原因清算期貨合約的水平。</p><p>Scekic預計，由於市場情緒轉為看漲，因此在首次適度的價格修正時會出現“大量清算”。</p><p><img src=\"https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/btc-liqs-2020-775x495.png\" alt=\"btc-liqs-2020\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p>', '盡管領先的加密貨幣周壹的每日漲幅超過10％，但已結算的比特幣期貨合約仍保持在相對較低的水平，因為壹些交易員預計價格會上漲。\r\n\r\n比特幣以上$ 11,400飆升，周壹，但這種波動只能引發破產現價僅售$ 133萬美元的比特幣BitMEX期貨合約的，領先的比特幣衍生產品交易所，根據偏移。');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (210, 97, 'zh-CN', '黄金达到历史新高，因为比特币突破$ 11k', '<p>黄金价格周一达到新的历史高点1,942美元，延续了自2019年开始的涨势。</p><p>自一月份以来，黄金价格上涨了约28％，创历史新高。</p><p>黄金在2011年9月6日达到历史最高纪录1,924美元。</p><p>比特币通常被视为数字黄金，由于这种坚守的加密货币与黄金并驾齐驱，因此飙升至11,400美元。 </p><p>根据OnChainFX的说法，比特币在过去24小时内上涨了13％以上。 </p>', '黄金价格周一达到新的历史高点1,942美元，延续了自2019年开始的涨势。');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (211, 97, 'zh-TW', '黃金達到歷史新高，因為比特幣突破$ 11k', '<p>黃金價格週一達到新的歷史高點1942美元，延續了自2019年開始的漲勢。</p><p>自一月份以來，黃金價格上漲了約28%，創歷史新高。</p><p>黃金在2011年9月6日達到歷史最高紀錄1924美元。</p><p>比特幣通常被視為數位黃金，由於這種堅守的加密貨幣與黃金並駕齊驅，囙此飆升至11400美元。</p><p>根據OnChainFX的說法，比特幣在過去24小時內上漲了13%以上。</p>', '黃金價格週一達到新的歷史高點1942美元，延續了自2019年開始的漲勢。');
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (212, 97, 'en', 'Gold Reaches All-Time High as Bitcoin Breaks Above $11k', '<p>The price of gold reached a new all-time intraday high of $1,942 Monday, extending a rally that started in 2019.</p><p>A record high for the yellow metal comes during an approximately 28% rally since January.</p><p>Gold’s previous record high of $1,924 was reached on Sept. 6, 2011.</p><p>Bitcoin, often viewed as digital gold, soared to $11,400 as the stalwart cryptocurrency keeps pace with gold. </p><p>Bitcoin gained more than 13% over the past 24 hours, according to OnChainFX. </p>', 'The price of gold reached a new all-time intraday high of $1,942 Monday, extending a rally that started in 2019.');
