 6000 AETC tokens</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">2: 30% reward for purchasing 40,000 AETC tokens</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">3: 45% reward for purchasing 100,000 AETC tokens</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">4: 60% reward for purchasing 200,000 AETC tokens</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">5: 100% reward for purchasing 500,000 AETC tokens</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Example :(purchasing for 6000 AETC tokens will reward 960 AETC tokens)</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Terms &amp; Conditions:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Rewards will be issued within 24 hours after the end of the event.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">PCICOIN reserves the right of final interpretation of this activity.</span></p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (446, 166, 'kor', 'AETC 캠페인 행사', '<p>모든 AETC 팬을 불러주세요: 100,000 AETC 토큰을 획득할 수 있습니다!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>행사기간 : 2021-07-01 00:00:00 AM(UTC) - 2021-07-10 11:59:59 PM(UTC).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>모든 AETC 팬분들께 감사드리기 위해 지금 AETC 나눔행사에 모든 팬을 초대합니다.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>이벤트 기간 동안 해당 수량의 AETC를 구매하면 20~100%의 해당 보상이 주어진다.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>보상은 다음과 같습니다.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1: AETC 토큰 6000개를 구매하면 16% 보상을 받을 수 있다.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2: AETC 토큰 4만 개 구매 시 30% 보상을 받을 수 있다.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>3: AETC 토큰 10만 개 구매 45% 보상.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>4: AETC 토큰 20만 개 구매 시 60% 보상을 받을 수 있다.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>5: AETC 토큰 50만 개 구매 시 100% 보상을 받을 수 있다.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>예: (AETC 토큰 6000개 구매 시 AETC 토큰 960개 보상).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>약관 및 세부 사항:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>리워드는 이벤트 종료 후 24시간 이내에 지급된다.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>pcicion은 이 행사의 최종 해석권을 유지합니다.</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (447, 166, 'jp', 'AETCキャンペーン', '<p>すべてのAETCファンに呼びかけ：1000，000 AETCトークンが勝つ！</p>\r\n<p>活動時間：2021-07-01 00：00：00 AM(UTC)-2021-07-10 11：59 PM(UTC)。</p>\r\n<p>すべてのAETCファンに感謝するために、私たちは今すべてのファンをAETC共有イベントに招待しています。</p>\r\n<p>キャンペーン中に対応する数のAETCを購入すると、20%~100%の対応する報酬が得られます。</p>\r\n<p>ご褒美は以下の通りです。</p>\r\n<p>1：AETCトークン6000枚を購入すると16%の奨励が受けられます。</p>\r\n<p>2：AETCトークン4万枚を購入すると30%の奨励が得られる。</p>\r\n<p>3：AETCトークン10万枚購入45%奨励。</p>\r\n<p>4：AETCトークン20万枚を購入すると60%の奨励が得られる。</p>\r\n<p>5：AETCトークン50万枚を購入すると100%の奨励が得られる。</p>\r\n<p>例：(AETCトークン6000個を購入すると960個のAETCトークンが奨励されます)。</p>\r\n<p>条項と細則：</p>\r\n<p>奨励金は活動終了後24時間以内に支給されます。</p>\r\n<p>pcicionは今回の活動の最終解釈権を保持する。</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (448, 166, 'de', NULL, '<p><span class=\"text-dst\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #ffffff; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif;\">Rufen Sie alle AETC-Fans an: 100.000 AETC-Tokens k&ouml;nnen gewonnen werden!</span><br style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span class=\"text-dst hl\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #ffff00; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif;\">Aktivit&auml;tszeit: 01. Juli 2021 00: 00: 00 (Weltzeit) -10 vom Juli 2021 um 23: 59: 59 Uhr (GMT).</span><br style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span class=\"text-dst\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #ffffff; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif;\">Um uns bei allen AETC-Fans zu bedanken, laden wir jetzt alle Fans zur Teilnahme an der AETC-Sharing ein.</span><br style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span class=\"text-dst\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #ffffff; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif;\">F&uuml;r den Kauf einer angemessenen Anzahl von AETC w&auml;hrend der Veranstaltung wird eine entsprechende Belohnung von 20% Murray 100% erhalten.</span><br style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span class=\"text-dst\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #ffffff; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif;\">Die Auszeichnungen lauten wie folgt:</span><br style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span class=\"text-dst\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #ffffff; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'\\微软雅黑\', sans-serif;\">1: der Kauf von 6.000 AETC-Tokens kann eine Belohnung von 16% erhalten.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Microsoft Yahei, \\\\5FAE软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2: 30% Pr&auml;mie f&uuml;r den Kauf von 40.000 AETC-Tokens.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Microsoft Yahei, \\\\5FAE软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3: 45% Vorschuss f&uuml;r den Kauf von 100.000 AETC-Tokens.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Microsoft Yahei, \\\\5FAE软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4: 60% Pr&auml;mie f&uuml;r den Kauf von 200.000 AETC-Tokens.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Microsoft Yahei, \\\\5FAE软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5: 500.000 AETC-Tokens werden belohnt.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Microsoft Yahei, \\\\5FAE软雅黑, sans-serif;\">Beispiel: (der Kauf von 6.000 AETC-Tokens belohnt 960 AETC-Tokens).&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Microsoft Yahei, \\\\5FAE软雅黑, sans-serif;\">Allgemeine Gesch&auml;ftsbedingungen:&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Microsoft Yahei, \\\\5FAE软雅黑, sans-serif;\">Die Preisverleihung findet innerhalb von 24 Stunden nach dem Ende der Veranstaltung statt.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Microsoft Yahei, \\\\5FAE软雅黑, sans-serif;\">Bkcion beh&auml;lt sich das Recht vor, diese Veranstaltung endg&uuml;ltig zu interpretieren.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (449, 166, 'it', NULL, '<p>Chiamate tutti i fan AETC: 1000000 gettoni AETC possono essere vinti!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Tempo di attivit&agrave;: 2021 - 07 - 01 00: 00 AM (UTC) - 2021 - 07 - 10 11: 59: 59 PM (UTC).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Per ringraziare tutti i fan dell\'AETC, invitiamo ora tutti i fan a partecipare alle attivit&agrave; di condivisione AETC.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>L\'acquisto del numero appropriato di AETC durante l\'evento ricever&agrave; una corrispondente ricompensa del 20% Murray 100%.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I premi sono i seguenti:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1: &Egrave; possibile ottenere una ricompensa del 16% per l\'acquisto di 6000 gettoni AETC.</p>\r\n<p>2: 30% bonus per l\'acquisto di 40, 000 gettoni AETC.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>3: 45% bonus per l\'acquisto di 100000 gettoni AETC.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>4: 60% bonus per l\'acquisto di 200000 gettoni AETC.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>5: 500000 I gettoni AETC saranno ricompensati.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Esempio: (Acquistando 6000 gettoni AETC ricompenser&agrave; 960 gettoni AETC).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Termini e condizioni:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I premi saranno assegnati entro 24 ore dalla fine dell\'evento.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>pcicion si riserva il diritto di interpretazione finale di questo evento.</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (450, 166, 'spa', NULL, '<p>Llama a todos los fans de AETC: &iexcl;Se pueden ganar 1000000 fichas AETC!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Hora de actividad: 2021 - 07 - 01 00:00:00 (UTC) - 2021 - 07 - 10 11:59:59 (UTC).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Con el fin de dar las gracias a todos los fans de AETC, ahora invitamos a todos los aficionados a participar en las actividades de intercambio de AETC.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>La compra del n&uacute;mero apropiado de AETC durante el evento recibir&aacute; una recompensa correspondiente del 20% Murray 100%.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Los premios son los siguientes:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1: Usted puede obtener una recompensa del 16% por comprar 6000 fichas AETC.</p>\r\n<p>2:30 % de bonificaci&oacute;n por la compra de 40.000 fichas AETC.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>3:45 % de bonificaci&oacute;n por comprar 100000 fichas AETC.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>4:60 % de bonificaci&oacute;n para comprar 200000 fichas AETC.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>5:500000 fichas AETC ser&aacute;n recompensadas.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Ejemplo: (Comprar 6000 fichas AETC recompensar&aacute; 960 fichas AETC).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>T&eacute;rminos y condiciones:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Los premios se otorgar&aacute;n dentro de las 24 horas siguientes al final del evento.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>pcicion se reserva el derecho de interpretaci&oacute;n final de este evento.</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (451, 166, 'tr', NULL, '<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">T&uuml;m AETC hayranlarına &ccedil;ağrı: 1000.000 AETC jetonu kazanın!</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Etkinlik saati: 2021-07-01 00:00:00 (UTC)-2021-07-10 11:59:59 PM (UTC).</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">T&uuml;m AETC hayranlarına teşekk&uuml;r etmek i&ccedil;in, şimdi t&uuml;m hayranları AETC paylaşım etkinliğine katılmaya davet ediyoruz.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Etkinlik sırasında uygun miktarda AETC satın alınması% 20-% 100 karşılık gelen bir &ouml;d&uuml;lle &ouml;d&uuml;llendirilecektir.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&Ouml;d&uuml;ller aşağıdaki gibidir:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">1: 6000 AETC jetonu satın alın ve% 16 &ouml;d&uuml;l kazanın.</span><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">2: %30 bonus karşılığında 40.000 AETC jetonu satın alın.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">3: %45 &ouml;d&uuml;l karşılığında 100.000 AETC jetonu satın alın.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">4: 200.000 AETC jetonu satın almak i&ccedil;in% 60 &ouml;d&uuml;l.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">5: %100 &ouml;d&uuml;lle 500.000 AETC jetonu satın alın.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&Ouml;rnek: (6000 AETC belirteci satın almak 960 AETC belirteci &ouml;d&uuml;llendirir).</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Hatalar ve kurallar:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&Ouml;d&uuml;ller Temmuz ayından sonraki 24 saat i&ccedil;inde verilecektir.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">pcicion sonunda bu olayı yorumlama hakkını saklı tutar.</span></p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article_translations` VALUES (452, 166, 'pt', NULL, '<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Chame todos os f&atilde;s da AETC: 1000.000 tokens AETC para ganhar!</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Hor&aacute;rio do evento: 2021-07-01 00:00:00 (UTC)-2021-07-10 11:59:59 PM (UTC).</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Para agradecer a todos os f&atilde;s da AETC, agora convidamos todos os f&atilde;s a participar do evento de compartilhamento da AETC.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">As compras da quantidade apropriada de AETCs durante o evento ser&atilde;o recompensadas com uma recompensa correspondente de 20%-100%.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">As recompensas s&atilde;o as seguintes:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">1: Compre 6000 tokens AETC e obtenha uma recompensa de 16%.</span><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">2: Compre 40.000 tokens AETC por um b&ocirc;nus de 30%.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">3: Compre 100.000 tokens AETC para uma recompensa de 45%.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">4: recompensa de 60% por comprar 200.000 tokens AETC.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">5: Compre 500.000 tokens AETC com uma recompensa de 100%.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Exemplo: (Comprar 6000 tokens AETC recompensar&aacute; 960 tokens AETC).</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Erros e regras:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">As recompensas ser&atilde;o emitidas dentro de 24 horas a partir de julho.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, system-ui, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">pcicion reserva-se o direito de finalmente interpretar este evento.</span></p>', NULL);
